    {2069,"Recklessness",132109,2,0,2,{"wago"},"The Enforcer becomes immune to fear effects and his or her chance to deal a critical is increased by $90929s1% for $90929d., but the Enforcer's armor is also reduced by $90929s2%.\n\n\n\nThe Enforcer can use this ability if his or her remaining health is below 20%.",14,0,0,0,95,0,10,2066,0},
