    {2108,"Stay of Execution",135917,2,0,0,{"wago"},"After Baron Ashbury finishes casting Asphyxiate, he immediately casts Stay of Execution. This spell heals all players to 50% of their maximum health.$[!2,4\n\n\n\nIn Heroic Difficulty, instead of healing players at the end of the cast, Baron Ashbury channels Stay of Execution until interrupted. Players are healed every second for $93706s1% of their maximum health, but Baron Ashbury is also healed for $93706s2% of his maximum health.$]",-1,0,0,96,96,2109,2,0,0},
