    {2137,"Malefic Strike",237530,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Commander Springvale slashes at his main target, instantly dealing $93685s1% of his normal Physical melee damage and generating a charge of Unholy Power he can then use for other abilities.",-1,0,0,0,98,2138,1,0,0},
    {2138,"Shield of the Perfidious",132390,2,0,0,{"wago"},"When Commander Springvale has three charges of Unholy Power, he consumes the charges and unleashes the power from his shield. Shield of the Perfidious deals $93722s1 Shadow damage every $93693t1 seconds in a narrow 25 degree cone in front of Springvale for $93693d. $[!2,4\n\n\n\nIn Heroic Difficulty, the cone expands to 150 degrees.$]",-1,0,0,0,98,2139,2,0,0},
    {2139,"Desecration",136199,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Commander Springvale desecrates the ground in a $93691A1 yard radius under a random player. All players standing in this defiled ground have their movement speed decreased by $93691s1% and take $93691s2 Shadow damage every $93690t1 seconds.",-1,0,0,0,98,2140,3,0,0},
    {2140,"Word of Shame",237555,2,0,2,{"wago"},"When Commander Springvale has three charges of Unholy Power, he can consume the charges and cast this spell on a random enemy player. Word of Shame deals $93852s1% of a player's maximum health as Shadow damage every $93852t1 seconds. The effect lasts until either the targeted player or Commander Springvale dies.",2,0,0,8,98,2142,4,0,0},
