    {2157,"Conjure Poisonous Mixture",136242,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Lord Walden conjures a bottle of poisonous mixture then throws it at the location of a random player. When the bottle lands on the ground it erupts. \n\n\n\nThe poison immediately inflicts $93697s1 Nature damage to players within $93697A1 yards, and continues to inflict $93697s2 Nature damage every $93697t2 seconds while decreasing the movement speed of players by $93697s3% for $93697d.",1,0,0,0,99,2392,2,0,0},
