    {2444,"Dust Flail",132846,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Lockmaw begins to whip his tail up and down for $81643d. Lockmaw deals $81644s1 Nature damage every second to players behind him and their chance to hit is reduced by $81673s1% for $81673d. The damage dealt by Dust Flail increases by $81644s3% for each second Lockmaw whips his tail.",-1,0,0,0,118,2445,3,2442,0},
    {2445,"Venomous Rage",136224,2,0,0,{"wago"},"When Lockmaw's remaining health reaches 30%, he enters a Venomous Rage. This increases his damage dealt by $81706s1%.",-1,0,0,2048,118,2446,4,2442,0},
    {2446,"Scent of Blood",237515,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Lockmaw causes a random player to bleed, inflicting $81690s1 Physical damage every $81690t1 seconds for $81690d. The scent of the blood causes Frenzied Crocolisks to attack the affected player.",-1,0,0,0,118,2447,5,2442,0},
    {2447,"Frenzied Crocolisk",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"These vicious crocolisks periodically join the fight from the nearby riverbeds. They try to attack any player who has the Scent of Blood effect on them.",-1,2448,33451,0,118,0,6,2442,0},
    {2448,"Vicious Bite",132141,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Frenzied Crocolisks bite their current enemy target, inflicting Physical damage equal to $81677s1% of a normal melee attack and additionally inflicting $81677s2 Physical damage every $81677t2 seconds for $81677d. The Vicious Bite stacks up to 3 times.",-1,0,0,0,118,0,7,2447,0},
    {2449,"Augh",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"While Lockmaw is alive, Augh is immune to damage and will periodically enter the fight stealthed then use his Paralytic Blow Dart, Whirlwind, or Smoke bomb abilities before retreating.$[!2,4\n\n\n\nAfter Lockmaw dies in Heroic Difficulty, Augh steals Lockmaw's loot and becomes attackable.$]",-1,2450,0,0,118,0,8,0,0},
    {2450,"Paralytic Blow Dart",132273,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Augh shoots a Paralytic Blow Dart at a random player, immediately inflicting $84799s1 Nature damage, reducing melee, ranged, and spell casting speeds by $84799s3%, and additionally inflicting $84799s2 Nature damage every $84799t2 seconds for $84799d.",-1,0,0,512,118,2451,9,2449,0},
    {2451,"Whirlwind",132369,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Augh spins around like mad towards a random player for $84784d, inflicting $84785s1 Physical damage every second to surrounding enemies within $84785A1 yards.",-1,0,0,0,118,2452,10,2449,0},
    {2452,"Smoke Bomb",132156,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Augh explodes a Smoke Bomb at his feet, stunning any enemy target within $84768A1 yards for $84768d.",-1,0,0,0,118,2453,11,2449,0},
    {2453,"Frenzy",136224,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Augh enters a Frenzy, increasing his attack speed by $91415s1% and damage dealt by $91415s3%.",14,0,0,8,118,2454,12,2449,0},
    {2454,"Dragon's Breath",134153,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Augh breathes fire in a $83776a1 yard long 60 degree frontal cone, inflicting $83776s1 Fire damage to every enemy target within the cone and disorienting them for $83776d.",14,0,0,136,118,0,13,2449,0},
    {2455,"Stage One: Begone Infidels!",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,2456,0,0,119,2462,1,0,0},
