    {2457,"Plague of Ages",136157,2,0,0,{"wago"},"High Prophet Barim hurls a bolt of cursed blight that targets a random player then jumps to hit two more random players. The bolt inflicts $82622s1 Nature damage and an additional $82622s2 Nature damage every $82622t2 seconds for $82622d.",-1,0,0,1024,119,2458,3,2455,0},
