    {2466,"Merged Souls",237557,2,0,0,{"wago"},"If a Soul Fragment reaches the Harbinger of Darkness, the Soul Fragment will heal the Harbinger for $82263s1 and increase the size and damage dealt by the Harbinger by $82263s3%. After casting this spell, the Soul Fragment disappears.",-1,0,0,0,119,0,13,2473,0},
