    {4202,"The Skyfire",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"Sky Captain Swayze helms this massive gunship equipped with numerous cannons and a pair of harpoon guns for its defense. The gunship is sturdy but not indestructible, and if it sustains too much damage the pursuit of Deathwing will come to an untimely end.",-1,4205,0,0,332,4203,2,4027,0},
