    {4208,"Twilight Flames",425955,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Goriona launches a blast of dark energy at the location of a random player, inflicting $%108051s1 Shadow damage on impact to players in a $108051A1 yard radius. Twilight Flames lingers on the deck of the Skyfire, inflicting $%108076s1 Shadow damage to players within $108076A1 yards every $108053t1 sec for $108053d.",-1,0,0,0,332,4354,26,4206,0},
