    {6310,"The Night",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"Tsulong struggles at Night with the Sha's corrupting influence. Bringing Tsulong's remaining health to zero while at Night permanently destroys the Sha's influence over him. When he reaches 100 energy, he temporarily purges the Sha's influence and radiant sunlight turns Night into Day.",-1,6311,0,0,742,6315,1,0,0},
