    {6323,"Sun Breath",535045,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Tsulong breathes out solar energy in a 60-degree cone in front of him, inflicting $122855s1 Nature damage to Sha within $122855A1 yards and stunning them for $122855d. The breath also places the Bathed in Light effect on players within its area.",-1,6324,0,0,742,6551,15,6315,0},
