    {6325,"Dissonance Field",237546,2,0,0,{"wago"},"The Empress creates a dissonance field which disrupts the sound associated with magic. The dissonance field absorbs nearby magical effects until it runs out of resonance. Once its resonance depletes, the field erupts in a Sonic Discharge.\n\n\n\nPlayers casting magical effects inside the dissonance field also deplete it of resonance.",-1,6326,0,0,743,6337,2,6336,0},
