    {6877,"Windstorm",236154,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Quet'zal pulls all players into the eye of a rushing windstorm. Players suffer $136577s1 Nature damage every $136577t1 sec until they are able to exit the storm. Damage, healing, and absorption effects cast while inside the windstorm are decreased by $136577s2%.\n\n\n\nOnce the storm is over, some rushing winds will linger.",-1,6878,0,0,817,6913,16,6866,0},
