    {7077,"Shatter",236316,2,0,0,{"wago"},"When a Molten Golem reaches 1% health remaining it becomes cooled and brittle, rendering it inactive. When Volkhan uses Shattering Stomp, all Cooled Golems will Shatter, inflicting $52429s1 Physical damage to all players within $52429A1 yards.",-1,0,0,16,598,30062,7,7045,0},
