    {7181,"Decapitate",839975,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Lei Shen throws his axe with supernatural force, inflicting $134916s1 Physical damage and inflicting Decapitate, increasing Physical damage taken by $134916s2% for $134916d. The damage inflicted decreases the farther away the target is from Lei Shen.",-1,0,0,17,832,7182,10,7178,0},
    {7182,"Thunderstruck",839983,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Lei Shen winds up to hurl his axe at a target location, inflicting $135096s1 Nature damage to nearby enemies. The damage inflicted decreases the farther away an enemy is from the impact point.",-1,0,0,16,832,7245,11,7178,0},
    {7186,"Intermission: Supercharge Conduits!",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"When he has 65% health remaining, Lei Shen casts Supercharge Conduits, becoming invulnerable and activating all four Conduits at once, supercharging them and increasing their level by one. Lei Shen can only maintain Supercharge Conduits for 45 seconds.",-1,7191,0,0,832,7192,13,0,0},
    {7191,"Overloaded Circuits",136111,2,0,0,{"wago"},"The Conduit with the highest charge after Supercharge Conduits expires becomes Overloaded, disabling the Conduit. An Overloaded Conduit inflicts $137176s1 Nature damage every $137176t1 sec to that quadrant of the room.\n\n$[!5,6\n\nIn Heroic difficulty, instead of the Overloaded Conduit becoming disabled, it remains active for the remainder of the fight, granting Lei Shen that ability.$]",-1,0,0,0,832,7814,14,7186,0},
    {7192,"Stage Two: Lightning Will End You!",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"Lei Shen equips his Polearm, Lightning, allowing him to call lightning from the sky. Lei Shen will charge any Conduit that he is near.",-1,7193,0,0,832,7202,16,0,0},
    {7193,"Discharged Energy",136075,2,0,0,{"wago"},"If Lei Shen is not charging a Conduit, he will Discharge electricity, inflicting increasing Nature damage every $134821t1 sec.",-1,0,0,32,832,7195,17,7192,0},
