    {7247,"Ball Lightning",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"The Ball Lightning periodically rushes towards a random player, inflicting $136620s2 Nature damage to that target.\n\n\n\n$[!5,6\n\nIn Heroic difficulty, Ball Lightning inflicts damage to enemies within $136620A2 yards.$]",-1,0,47569,0,832,0,20,7196,0},
