    {7249,"Violent Gale Winds",236154,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Lei Shen causes the walls of his chamber to open, unleashing the force of Violent Gale Winds. The winds push players in a direction, inflicting $136889s1 Nature damage every $136889t1 sec and causing Windburn.",-1,7871,0,0,832,7212,28,7209,0},
