    {7348,"Ji-Kun's Flock",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"Ji-Kun's young are located throughout the roost and progress through different stages of life. After a period of incubation Young Eggs of Ji-Kun will hatch into Hatchlings. When fed by Ji-Kun, the Hatchlings then mature into Fledglings. Both Fledgling Eggs and Mature Eggs will hatch into Juveniles.",-1,7349,0,32,828,7856,1,0,0},
