    {7357,"Caw",132158,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Ji-Kun cries out at 1 random player, sending piercing sound waves at their location. When the waves reach their destination they inflict $134375s1 Physical damage to all targets within $134375A1 yards of the impact.",5,0,0,32,828,7358,22,0,0},
