    {7682,"Poison Breath",136006,2,0,0,{"wago"},"The Massive Jormungar breathes poison on all players in front of it, inflicting Nature damage and additional Nature damage every $48133t3 sec., for $48133d.",-1,0,0,512,642,7683,12,7673,0},
