    {7691,"Stage 1: Grauf",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"Skadi the Ruthless starts the fight by mounting his drake, Grauf. While mounted, Skadi will fly overhead and order Grauf to breathe freezing clouds onto players below.\n\n\n\nSkadi remains mounted until players fire three harpoons at Grauf by using the Harpoon Launcher.",-1,7692,0,0,643,7704,1,0,0},
