    {7832,"Mutate Primordius (Volatile)",838812,2,0,0,{"wago"},"When Primordius steps on a Volatile Pool, it is absorbed, increasing Primordius' current mutation level to its maximum and healing Primordius for $140509s3% of his maximum health.",-1,0,0,0,820,7833,26,7831,0},
