    {7872,"Ancient Miasma",571320,2,0,1,{"wago"},"An Ancient Miasma fills the room, absorbing all healing received but creating an Ancient Barrier that absorbs damage equal to the amount of healing absorbed, up to a cap of 100% of maximum health. In addition, the Miasma inflicts $142906s1 Shadow damage every $142906t1 sec.",-1,7873,0,36,846,7874,5,0,0},
