    {7874,"Endless Rage",132344,2,0,1,{"wago"},"Malkorok gains Rage over time whenever he is not in a Blood Rage.\n\n\n\nWhen Malkorok reaches 100 Rage, he absorbs the Ancient Miasma and enters a Blood Rage.",-1,7875,0,0,846,7896,8,0,0},
