    {7948,"Shoot",133580,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Shoots a player, inflicting $143884s1% weapon damage.",-1,0,0,0,850,7949,38,7946,0},
    {7949,"Multi-Shot",236182,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Fire a volley of arrows, inflicting $143887s1 Physical damage to enemies within a $143887A1-yard cone.",-1,0,0,0,850,0,39,7946,0},
    {7950,"Essence of Y'Shaarj",236296,2,0,2,{"wago"},"The Ancient Miasma forms orbs of corruption every $143846t1 seconds, which persist for the remainder of the fight. \n\n\n\nIf a player comes into contact with an orb, it is consumed, removing Ancient Barrier and inflicting $143857s1 Shadow damage to them.",0,0,0,4096,846,0,7,7872,0},
    {7951,"Eradicate",607852,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Malkorok kills all players if he is not defeated within $143916s1 minutes.",-1,0,0,16,846,0,20,7896,0},
    {7952,"Living Corruption",0,1,0,3,{"wago"},"Seismic Slam causes Living Corruption to ooze out of the ground and attack players.",0,7953,49124,4096,846,0,15,7884,0},
    {7953,"Languish",460857,2,0,3,{"wago"},"Living Corruption weakens all players within 8 yards of them, reducing movement speed and spell casting speed by $143919s1%.",0,0,0,0,846,0,16,7952,0},
    {7954,"Dark Meditation",236170,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Sun Tenderheart enters a Dark Meditation, inflicting Shadow damage to all enemies every half second. Players take $143564s1% less damage from Dark Meditation when inside her Meditative Field.",-1,0,0,4,849,7943,32,7942,0},
    {7956,"Desperate Measures",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"Upon reaching 66% or 33% health remaining, Rook Stonetoe manifests evil forms of his closest friends, making Embodied Misery, Embodied Sorrow, and Embodied Gloom.\n\n\n\nOnce all three spirits are defeated, Rook Stonetoe resumes fighting players.",-1,8395,0,0,849,8145,7,7885,0},
    {7957,"Corruption Shock",136050,2,0,1,{"wago"},"Embodied Gloom hurls a bolt of corrupted lightning at several locations, inflicting $144018s1 Nature damage to all enemies within $144018A1 yards.",-1,0,0,64,849,8330,13,8397,0},
    {7958,"Defiled Ground",463566,2,0,1,{"wago"},"Embodied Misery smashes the ground with fervor, inflicting $143961s1 Physical damage to her current target, knocking them back. This force burns into the ground, inflicting $144357s1 Shadow damage every second.",-1,0,0,0,849,0,9,8395,0},
    {7959,"Inferno Strike",132863,2,0,1,{"wago"},"Embodied Sorrow casts a massive Fire damage spell at a random target. Inferno Strike divides ${$143962m2*$143962m1} Fire damage among all targets within $143962A2 yards.",-1,0,0,32,849,0,11,8396,0},
    {7960,"Stage 1: A Cry in the Darkness",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,7962,0,0,851,7961,5,0,0},
    {7961,"Stage 2: Frenzy for Blood!",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"The excessive scent of blood sends Thok into a frenzy for blood!\n\n\n\n$[!17 In Raid Finder difficulty, this occurs when Thok reaches 80%, 55%, and 30% health. $]",-1,7981,0,0,851,7969,11,0,0},
    {7962,"Fearsome Roar",237567,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Thok's bellowing roar inflicts $143426s1 Physical damage in a frontal cone. The roar incites terror in players' hearts, causing them to take $143766s1% more damage per stack.",-1,0,0,1,851,7963,6,7960,0},
    {7963,"Deafening Screech",252188,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Upon reaching full energy, Thok lets loose a shrill cry, inflicting $143343s1 Physical damage to all enemies and interrupting spellcasts. Every time Thok Screeches, the rate of his energy regeneration is increased.",-1,0,0,32,851,7964,7,7960,0},
    {7964,"Tail Lash",132109,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Thok's mighty tail whips about, striking all enemies behind the caster, inflicting $143428s1 Physical damage and stunning them for $143428d.",-1,0,0,0,851,7965,8,7960,0},
    {7965,"Shock Blast",839974,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Electricity arcs and snaps around Thok's shock collar, inflicting $143707s1 Nature damage to random enemies.",-1,0,0,0,851,7967,9,7960,0},
    {7966,"Shadow Weakness",651086,2,0,0,{"wago"},"When Embodied Anguish strikes targets, he applies Shadow Weakness, increasing damage taken by Mark of Anguish. Additionally, passing the Mark of Anguish applies one Shadow Weakness to all players. This effect stacks.",-1,0,0,0,849,8415,23,7940,0},
    {7967,"Bloodied",236305,2,0,2,{"wago"},"When players fall beneath 50% health, Thok the Bloodthirsty can smell their blood. If at least half the players in the raid are within 10 yards of one another while Bloodied, the scent of blood becomes overwhelming and Thok enters a Blood Frenzy.",0,0,0,0,851,0,10,7960,0},
    {7968,"Kor'kron Jailer",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Thok's mighty roar when he enters a Blood Frenzy attracts the attention of a nearby jailer. Upon defeating him, you may obtain a prison key that can unlock one of the nearby cells containing Garrosh's prisoners.",-1,0,49082,0,851,8581,14,7961,0},
    {7969,"Prisoners of War",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"Garrosh has taken prisoners during his Pandaria campaign, and they remain trapped in cages alongside the beasts, hoping for freedom.",-1,8283,0,0,851,0,20,0,0},
    {7973,"An Infusion of Acid",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"Once Akolik draws Thok's attention, the mighty dinosaur will devour him and absorb the acidic powers of the saurok. This will end Thok's Blood Frenzy.",-1,7977,0,0,851,0,22,8283,0},
    {7974,"An Infusion of Frost",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"Once Gorai draws Thok's attention, the mighty dinosaur will devour him and absorb the watery powers of the jinyu. This will end Thok's Blood Frenzy.",-1,7978,0,0,851,0,26,8284,0},
    {7975,"An Infusion of Flame",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"Once Montak draws Thok's attention, the mighty dinosaur will devour him and absorb the fiery powers of the yaungol. This will end Thok's Blood Frenzy.",-1,7982,0,0,851,0,30,8285,0},
    {7976,"Corrosive Blood",538440,2,0,0,{"wago"},"A corrosive poison seeps from every one of Thok's pores. This toxin hits random players, inflicting $143791s1 Nature damage initially, and then $143791s2 Nature damage every $143791t2 sec for $143791d.",-1,0,0,0,851,0,24,7973,0},
    {7977,"Acid Breath",132107,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Thok's Fearsome Roar is replaced by Acid Breath. Acid Breath inflicts $143780s1 Nature damage in a frontal cone. The acid coats the armor of affected players, reducing its effectiveness by $143780s2% per stack.",-1,0,0,1,851,7976,23,7973,0},
    {7978,"Freezing Breath",135844,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Thok's Fearsome Roar is replaced by Freezing Breath. Freezing Breath inflicts $143426s1 Frost damage in a frontal cone and coats players in frost. After 5 stacks, the target will be frozen in a tomb of ice.",-1,0,0,1,851,7979,27,7974,0},
    {7979,"Icy Blood",464484,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Thok's skin freezes and cracks, spurting plumes of ice from within. Icy Blood inflicts $143800s1 Frost damage to random enemies and coats enemies in ice for $143800d. This ice inflicts $143773s3 damage every $143773t3 seconds.  Upon reaching 5 stacks of the debuff, a player becomes frozen in a tomb of ice.",-1,0,0,0,851,0,28,7974,0},
    {7980,"Fixate",236188,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Thok becomes unable to be tanked, and will fixate on random distant players.",-1,0,0,16,851,7968,13,7961,0},
    {7981,"Blood Frenzy",132334,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Thok roars in hunger, knocking away front enemies and going into a frenzy for blood. Any enemies who are caught within reach of Thok's terrible maw are devoured instantly. \n\n\n\nThok gradually gains speed during Blood Frenzy. He is also immune to taunt during Blood Frenzy.",-1,0,0,0,851,7980,12,7961,0},
    {7982,"Scorching Breath",135809,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Thok's Fearsome Roar is replaced by Scorching Breath. Scorching Breath inflicts $143426s1 Fire damage in a frontal cone. The flames sear enemy flesh, causing $143767s2 Fire damage every $143767t2 seconds.",-1,0,0,1,851,7983,31,7975,0},
    {7983,"Burning Blood",132847,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Thok's skin becomes coated in a sheen of incendiary oil, inflicting $143783s1 Fire damage to random enemies and leaving a puddle of flame beneath their feet.",-1,0,0,0,851,0,32,7975,0},
    {7984,"Tears of the Vale",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"As a water elemental, Immerseus attacks players directly.",-1,7985,0,0,852,7992,5,0,0},
    {7985,"Sha Bolt",651091,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Immerseus fires a Sha Bolt at every enemy, inflicting $143295s1 Shadow damage to enemies within $143295A1 yards, and forming a Sha Pool at the targeted location. Sha Pools inflict $143297s1 Shadow damage every second.",-1,0,0,0,852,7987,6,7984,0},
    {7987,"Swirl",135861,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Immerseus causes torrents of Sha-corrupted water to burst from beneath the cracks in the ground. Players that come into contact with the tainted waters will suffer $143413s1 Shadow damage and be knocked away.",-1,0,0,32,852,7988,7,7984,0},
    {7988,"Corrosive Blast",236302,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Immerseus inflicts $143436s1 Shadow damage in a cone aimed at his primary target, increasing Shadow damage taken by $143436s2% for $143436d. Stacks.",-1,0,0,1,852,7991,8,7984,0},
    {7989,"Swelling Corruption",656551,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Immerseus surges with power, gaining stacks of Swelling Corruption proportional to his current Corruption level. This power lashes out at players who strike Immerseus with single target abilities, coalescing into a Congealed Sha creature as well as inflicting Sha Corruption upon the attacker, which deals at least $143579s1 Shadow damage every $143579t1 sec for $143579d, increasing in damage rapidly with each additional stack.",0,0,0,4128,852,0,10,7984,0},
    {7991,"Seeping Sha",651087,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Coming into contact with the Seeping Sha that surrounds Immerseus inflicts $143286s1 Shadow damage and knocks players back.",-1,0,0,0,852,7989,9,7984,0},
    {7992,"Split",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"Upon reaching zero health, Immerseus becomes unstable and bursts into a shower of Sha Puddles and Contaminated Puddles, which will attempt to reform in the pool at the center of the chamber. \n\n\n\nFor each Sha Puddle killed and each Contaminated Puddle healed to full, Immerseus's Corruption is reduced by one.",-1,7993,0,0,852,0,11,0,0},
    {7993,"Sha Puddle",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"When destablized, Immerseus forms one Sha Puddle for every four units of Corruption he has. Destroying a Sha Puddle before it merges back into the central pool will remove one unit of Corruption.",-1,7994,49121,2,852,7995,12,7992,0},
    {7994,"Sha Residue",651095,2,0,0,{"wago"},"When a Sha Puddle is destroyed, it triggers Sha Residue, applying Sha Residue to enemies within $143459A1 yards and increasing damage dealt to other Sha Puddles by $143459s2%. This effect stacks.",-1,0,0,0,852,0,13,7993,0},
    {7995,"Contaminated Puddle",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"When destablized, Immerseus forms one Contaminated Puddle for every four units of Corruption that have previously been removed. Healing a Contaminated Puddle to full health before it merges back into the central pool will cause it to become Purified, and remove one unit of Corruption upon reaching Immerseus.",-1,7996,33112,4,852,7998,14,7992,0},
    {7996,"Congealing",237012,2,0,0,{"wago"},"The speed of the Contaminated Puddle wanes as it increases in health.",-1,0,0,128,852,7997,15,7995,0},
    {7997,"Purified Residue",136037,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Upon reaching full health, a Contaminated Puddle releases Purified Residue, restoring $143524s1% mana to allies within $143524A1 yards and increasing healing done by $143524s2%. This effect stacks.",-1,0,0,128,852,0,16,7995,0},
    {7998,"Erupting Sha",651084,2,0,0,{"wago"},"When any Puddle reaches Immerseus, it triggers an eruption, inflicting $143498s1 Shadow damage to all players for a Sha or Contaminated Puddle, or $145377s1 Frost damage for a Purified Puddle.",-1,0,0,0,852,7999,17,7992,0},
    {7999,"Sha Pool",651093,2,0,2,{"wago"},"The Sha Pool grows over time, inflicting at least $119941s1 Shadow damage over $119941t1 sec to enemies who touch it, stacking and increasing rapidly in damage proportional to the number of stacks. Touching the Sha Pool causes it to shrink, whereas it will expand whenever any Puddle reaches it.",0,0,0,4128,852,8000,18,7992,0},
    {8000,"Seeping Sha",651085,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Coming into contact with the Seeping Sha that surrounds Immerseus inflicts $143286s1 Shadow damage and knocks players back.",0,0,0,0,852,0,19,7992,0},
    {8001,"Paragons of the Klaxxi",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,8002,0,0,853,8014,5,0,0},
    {8002,"Paragon's Purpose",646377,2,0,2,{"wago"},"Whenever a Klaxxi Paragon is defeated, all other active Klaxxi Paragons heal to full and gain a $143482s1% damage bonus.",0,0,0,0,853,8576,6,8001,0},
    {8003,"Ready to Fight",236641,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Klaxxi Paragons with this aura on them will be the next to join the fight. \n\n\n\nBefore the fight begins, three Klaxxi Paragons will have this aura. When the encounter begins all three of these Paragons join the encounter and one other Paragon will gain this aura to indicate that they will join the fight next.\n\n\n\nEverytime a new Klaxxi Paragon joins the fight, one of the inactive Klaxxi Paragons will gain this aura.",-1,0,0,32,853,8074,8,8001,0},
    {8004,"Kil'ruk the Wind-Reaver",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,8005,48682,1,853,0,71,0,0},
    {8005,"Exposed Veins",457636,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Kil'ruk the Wind-Reaver's sharp blades expose the blood vessels of his victims, making them more susceptible to the attacks of Xaril the Poisoned Mind.\n\n\n\nAll damage taken from Xaril the Poisoned Mind is increased 10% for each application of Exposed Veins.",-1,0,0,1,853,8006,72,8004,0},
    {8006,"Gouge",132155,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Kil'ruk the Wind-Reaver incapacitates his current tank target.  This attack is followed immediately by Mutilate.",-1,8007,0,37,853,8008,73,8004,0},
    {8007,"Mutilate",135358,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Kil'ruk the Wind-Reaver lashes out with both of his weapons for a devastating attack.",-1,0,0,21,853,0,74,8006,0},
    {8008,"Death from Above",878215,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Kil'ruk the Wind-Reaver leaps into the air over a random player and then crashes down. Kil'ruk inflicts Physical damage to all enemies within $142232A1 yards upon landing.",-1,0,0,0,853,8475,75,8004,0},
