    {8549,"Poison-Tipped Blades",136067,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Korgra's poison-tipped dagger inflicts $146902s1 Nature damage every $146902t1 sec.  to her primary target. This effect stacks.",-1,0,0,0,881,8550,17,8548,0},
    {8550,"Poison Cloud",840198,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Korgra shatters a vial of poison, causing a smoky poison cloud to coalesce at her feet. This poison cloud inflicts $147705s1 Nature damage every $147705t1 second to players standing within.",-1,0,0,0,881,8551,18,8548,0},
    {8551,"Curse of Venom",458736,2,0,0,{"wago"},"When her health falls low, Korgra's Curse of Venom takes effect. She will take the form of a snake, casting a deadly poison bolt volley until she is defeated.",-1,0,0,0,881,8552,19,8548,0},
    {8552,"Dragonmaw Ebon Stalker",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Upon Korgra's command, these stealthed units will emerge from the shadows behind a random target, stabbing wildly. Any victims standing within range of the blows will suffer critical Physical damage.",-1,0,50975,0,881,0,20,8548,0},
    {8553,"Foot Soldiers",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,8554,0,0,881,8563,21,8537,0},
    {8554,"Dragonmaw Bonecrusher",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"These deadly warriors will charge to a distant faction leader, stunning them. While stunned, they will perform a barrage of deadly attacks to the victim.",-1,8555,50968,33,881,8556,22,8553,0},
    {8555,"Fracture",132152,2,0,0,{"wago"},"The Dragonmaw Bonecrusher charges to a distant Faction Leader, stunning them and inflicting $146901s1% of the leader's health every $t1 sec.",-1,0,0,33,881,0,23,8554,0},
    {8556,"Dragonmaw Tidal Shaman",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"The Dragonmaw Tidal Shaman cast healing spells on their allies, and summon violent Tidal waves to damage their enemies.",-1,8557,50988,96,881,8558,24,8553,0},
    {8557,"Healing Tide Totem",538569,2,0,0,{"wago"},"The Dragonmaw Tidal Shaman summons a totem at the Shaman's feet that heals nearby allies for $146755s1% of their total health every $146754t1 seconds for $146754d.",-1,0,0,32,881,0,25,8556,0},
    {8558,"Dragonmaw Flameslinger",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"These deadly archers shoot fire-tipped arrows at random players. The effect inflicts Fire damage on impact, and then burns the ground and any players standing within.",-1,0,50970,0,881,8559,26,8553,0},
    {8559,"Dragonmaw Grunt",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Dragonmaw Grunts wade into battle, crushing their enemies with devistating blows. They will also hurl a mighty axe at distant enemies.",-1,0,50984,0,881,8587,27,8553,0},
    {8561,"Dragonmaw Flagbearer",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Dragonmaw Flagbearers inspire those around them, dropping a banner that increases melee, ranged, and spell casting speed by $146735s1%. It also increases damage dealt by $146735s3% for all friendly targets within 15 yards for $146735d.",-1,0,50979,0,881,8562,29,8553,0},
