    {9377,"Overview",0,3,0,1,{"wago"},"Kargath's Berserker Rush cannot be stopped until he either kills his target, or finds something else to take his anger out on.\n\n\n\nAs the fight progresses, Iron Bombers and Drunken Bileslingers rain destruction from the arena stands. Players can dispatch these creatures after being tossed into the crowd by Kargath's Chain Hurl.$[!16\n\n\n\nIn Mythic difficulty, the raid must perform well to gain favor that is tracked by Roar of the Crowd. If the raid gains enough favor from Roar of the Crowd, the raid is granted increased damage dealing.$]",-1,9378,0,0,1128,10404,1,0,0},
    {9378,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Iron Bombers and Drunken Bileslingers will continue to harass the raid from the stands until they are killed.",-1,0,0,2,1128,9379,2,9377,0},
    {9379,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Kargath inflicts massive damage to the tank with his |cFF2959D3|Hspell:159113|h[Impale]|h|r ability.\n\n$bullet;Iron Bombers inflict raidwide damage until they are killed.",-1,0,0,4,1128,9380,3,9377,0},
    {9380,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Kargath's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:159113|h[Impale]|h|r leaves |cFF2959D3|Hspell:159178|h[Open Wounds]|h|r on his target that increases the damage of consecutive Impales.",-1,0,0,1,1128,0,4,9377,0},
    {9382,"Kargath Bladefist",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,9383,54674,0,1128,9387,6,0,0},
    {9383,"Impale",236276,2,159113,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,1,1128,9384,7,9382,0},
    {9384,"Blade Dance",236303,2,159250,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,1128,9385,8,9382,0},
    {9385,"Berserker Rush",841383,2,158986,0,{"wago"},"$[!16\n\n\n\nIn Mythic difficulty, the raid gains favor for Roar of the Crowd the longer Kargath stays in Berserker Rush. However, if Kargath's fixate target dies, the raid loses a big chunk of favor.$]",-1,0,0,16,1128,9386,9,9382,0},
    {9386,"Chain Hurl",463560,2,159947,0,{"wago"},"$[!17\n\n\n\nIn Looking for Raid difficulty, Kargath automatically tosses the tank with the highest amount of Open Wounds stacks, one random healer, and three random DPS into the crowd.$]",-1,10679,0,32,1128,0,10,9382,0},
    {9387,"Drunken Bileslinger",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Drunken Bileslingers appear in the stands and throw Mauling Brew into the arena.",-1,9388,54795,0,1128,9390,12,0,0},
    {9388,"Mauling Brew",236271,2,159410,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,1128,9389,13,9387,0},
