    {9393,"Iron Grunt",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"A seemingly endless throng of rowdy orcs.$[!16\n\n\n\nIn Mythic difficulty, killing Iron Grunts grants favor for Roar of the Crowd.$]",-1,9743,54869,0,1128,9394,20,0,0},
