    {9657,"Slag Elemental",0,1,0,2,{"wago"},"Slag Elementals will go Dormant and remove the Damage Shield of any nearby Primal Elementalist when they are reduced to 1 hitpoint.  While Dormant, the Fury's Blasts will restore $155239s1 Energy. When the Slag Elemental reaches 100 Energy they will revive.",0,9658,53481,32,1154,9648,37,10801,0},
