    {9849,"Pumped Up",236310,2,0,0,{"wago"},"When Hans'gar or Franzok take damage, they gain increasing amounts of Rage.\n\n\n\nAs their Rage increases, Pumped Up increases in power and they inflict more melee damage, increase the hammers thrown by Skullcracker, reduce the cast time of Disrupting Roar, and increase the number of jumps performed during Body Slam.",-1,0,0,32,1155,9859,17,9857,0},
