    {9900,"Arcane Wrath: Displacement",1041234,2,0,0,{"wago"},"In addition to Arcane Wrath's normal effects, Branded Players are unable to move more than 10 yards from the location they were marked. Attempting to leave the marked area will teleport the player back to the location they were originally marked.",-1,0,0,0,1197,9901,14,9890,0},
    {9901,"Destructive Resonance: Displacement",1041232,2,0,0,{"wago"},"In addition to Destructive Resonance's normal effects, it grows to twice its original size over 30 seconds.",-1,0,0,0,1197,9946,15,9890,0},
    {9902,"Mark of Chaos: Displacement",135739,2,0,0,{"wago"},"In addition to Mark of Chaos' normal effects, the target is teleported to a random location.",-1,0,0,1,1197,9903,18,9890,0},
    {9903,"Force Nova: Displacement",1041235,2,0,0,{"wago"},"In addition to Force Nova's normal effects, it now also pushes players away as the nova moves outwards.",-1,0,0,0,1197,0,19,9890,0},
    {9905,"Arcane Wrath: Fortification",1041234,2,0,0,{"wago"},"In addition to Arcane Wrath's normal effect, the jump range of Arcane Wrath is only decreased by 25% with each jump.",-1,0,0,0,1197,9906,30,9892,0},
    {9906,"Destructive Resonance: Fortification",1041232,2,0,0,{"wago"},"In addition to Destructive Resonance's normal effects, it persists for 2 minutes.",-1,0,0,0,1197,9947,31,9892,0},
    {9907,"Mark of Chaos: Fortification",135739,2,0,0,{"wago"},"In addition to Mark of Chaos' normal effects, the target is rooted in place.",-1,0,0,1,1197,9908,34,9892,0},
    {9908,"Force Nova: Fortification",1041235,2,0,0,{"wago"},"In addition to Force Nova's normal effects, an additional nova is released every $157323t1 sec,. for $157323d.",-1,0,0,0,1197,0,35,9892,0},
    {9910,"Arcane Wrath: Replication",1041234,2,0,0,{"wago"},"In addition to Arcane Wrath's normal effects, a second player will be Branded the first time Arcane Wrath jumps.",-1,0,0,0,1197,9911,50,9894,0},
    {9911,"Destructive Resonance: Replication",1041232,2,0,0,{"wago"},"In addition to Destructive Resonance's normal effects, two additional Destructive Resonances are created nearby when it detonates or expires.",-1,0,0,0,1197,9948,51,9894,0},
    {9912,"Mark of Chaos: Replication",135739,2,0,0,{"wago"},"In addition to Mark of Chaos' normal effects, 8 Orbs of Chaos are conjured when Mark of Chaos expires. Each orb flies out from the wearer and inflicts $158648s1 Arcane damage to all players that they move through.",-1,0,0,1,1197,9913,54,9894,0},
