    {10169,"Stage Two: Devoured Souls",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"At 75% health, Teron'gor twists and devours one of the ancient souls of Auchindoun, gaining malevolent powers directly opposed to the good deeds the Draenei heroes stood for in life.$[!8,23\n\n\n\nIn Challenge Mode and Mythic difficulty, Teron'gor siphons all three spirits and gains a combination of their powers.$]",-1,10170,0,0,1225,0,13,0,0},
    {10170,"Mender Elum",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"Teron'gor corrupts the healing powers of Mender Elum, gaining powers of Affliction.",-1,10191,0,0,1225,10177,14,10169,0},
