    {10285,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Ragewing rises from the depths of the Spire to ambush players on a narrow bridge. She mainly attacks with breaths and blasts of flame, but once badly injured she will alight on the ground to assault her foes directly.",-1,10286,0,0,1229,10289,1,0,0},
    {10286,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Destroy Ragewing Whelps as quickly as possible.\n\n$bullet;Standing towards the middle of the bridge will make it easier to avoid |cFF2959D3|Hspell:155031|h[Engulfing Fire]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Spreading out will decrease the chance of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:155053|h[Magma Spit]|h|r affecting more than one person.",-1,0,0,2,1229,10288,2,10285,0},
