    {10307,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Zaela begins by engaging players on foot, but once sufficiently injured will retreat to a flying proto-drake for a time. For the remainder of the fight, the party must deal with Zaela and swooping flame breath attacks from her drakes.",-1,10308,0,0,1234,10312,1,0,0},
