    {10405,"Overview",0,3,0,1,{"wago"},"This trio of forest protectors complement each other to overcome their foes. Life Warden Gola heals his allies with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:168082|h[Revitalize]|h|r, while Earthshaper Telu stuns players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:427459|h[Toxic Bloom]|h|r, and Dulhu threatens players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:427512|h[Noxious Charge]|h|r.",-1,10552,0,0,1207,10409,1,0,0},
