    {10656,"Rumbling Goren",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},"Frenzied Goren will emerge from the ground, inflicting $175835s2 Nature damage on impact. They will roll around in a frenzy, inflicting $175920s2 Physical damage on contact and knocking players away. After Call of Earth is over these Goren will submerge back into the ground, re-emerging at will.",-1,10657,60733,1,1291,0,8,10655,0},
