    {11401,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Players attempt to turn the massive Hellfire Cannons in the Citadel's courtyard against the mighty gate of the Citadel, while fending off Siegemaster Mar'tak and her militarized force.\n\n\n\nThroughout the encounter, waves of enemies rush at the players, periodically accompanied by huge siege weapons that seek to destroy the Cannons and the players defending them. Destroying these siege weapons allows players to salvage Felfire Munitions, which may be brought to the Hellfire Cannon, allowing it to  continuously fire Hellfire Rounds at the Reinforced Hellfire Door.\n\n\n\nOnce players successfully breach the Reinforced Hellfire Door, Siegemaster Mar'tak's forces retreat into the Citadel.",-1,11404,0,0,1426,11846,1,0,0},
    {11402,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Be ready to grab the attention of any Hellfire Reinforcements.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:184243|h[Slam]|h|r stacks increase Physical damage taken, so be wary when tanking multiple enemies and a Hulking Berserker.",-1,0,0,1,1426,0,4,11401,0},
    {11403,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:183449|h[Felfire Volley]|h|r inflicts high raid-wide damage after |cFF2959D3|Hspell:181968|h[Metamorphosis]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,1426,11402,3,11401,0},
    {11404,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Quickly defeat Gorebound Felcasters after they use |cFF2959D3|Hspell:181968|h[Metamorphosis]|h|r to become a Gorebound Terror.\n\n$bullet;Defeat Fel-Infused Siege Weapons to keep the Hellfire Cannons alive.",-1,0,0,2,1426,11403,2,11401,0},
    {11406,"Hellfire Reinforcements",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,11407,0,0,1426,11428,11,0,0},
    {11407,"Iron Dragoon",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"This hardened melee enemy wields a sharpened polearm and is at the beck and call of Siegemaster Mar'tak.",-1,0,56414,0,1426,11425,12,11406,0},
