    {12007,"Overview",0,3,0,1,{"wago"},"Players initially face Serpentrix alone. However when the beast reaches 66% and 33% health it will |cFF2959D3|Hspell:191873|h[Submerge]|h|r and re-emerge at a distant location, summoning two Hydra Spawns nearby.",-1,12008,0,0,1479,12011,1,0,0},
    {12008,"Damage Dealer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;When Serpentrix uses |cFF2959D3|Hspell:191855|h[Toxic Wound]|h|r, keep moving to avoid taking damage from the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:191858|h[Toxic Puddle]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Avoid damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192050|h[Poison Spit]|h|r by staying downwind of Serpentrix during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:191797|h[Violent Winds]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;When Serpentrix uses |cFF2959D3|Hspell:191873|h[Submerge]|h|r at 33% and 66% health, interrupt it to prevent damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:191848|h[Rampage]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,1479,12009,2,12007,0},
    {12009,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;When Serpentrix uses |cFF2959D3|Hspell:191855|h[Toxic Wound]|h|r, keep moving to avoid taking damage from the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:191858|h[Toxic Puddle]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Avoid damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192050|h[Poison Spit]|h|r by staying downwind of Serpentrix during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:191797|h[Violent Winds]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,1479,12010,3,12007,0},
    {12010,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192050|h[Poison Spit]|h|r by staying downwind of Serpentrix during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:191797|h[Violent Winds]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;When Serpentrix uses |cFF2959D3|Hspell:191873|h[Submerge]|h|r at 33% and 66% health, interrupt it to prevent damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:191848|h[Rampage]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,1479,0,4,12007,0},
