    {12020,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Warlord Parjesh calls in reinforcements to assist him in combat and hurls an |cFF2959D3|Hspell:191977|h[Impaling Spear]|h|r, striking the first target in a line and inflicting massive damage.",-1,12021,0,0,1480,12024,1,0,0},
    {12021,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Position yourself behind naga reinforcements when |cFF2959D3|Hspell:191977|h[Impaling Spear]|h|r is being thrown to avoid being pinned.\n\n$bullet;Kill enemy naga summoned by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192072|h[Call Reinforcements]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,1480,12022,2,12020,0},
    {12022,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Position yourself behind naga reinforcements when |cFF2959D3|Hspell:191977|h[Impaling Spear]|h|r is being thrown to avoid being pinned.\n\n$bullet;If an ally is struck by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:191977|h[Impaling Spear]|h|r, that player will require increased healing.",-1,0,0,4,1480,12023,3,12020,0},
    {12023,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Position yourself behind naga reinforcements when |cFF2959D3|Hspell:191977|h[Impaling Spear]|h|r is being thrown to avoid being pinned.\n\n$bullet;Gain threat on Hatecoil Shellbreakers when |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192072|h[Call Reinforcements]|h|r is cast.",-1,0,0,1,1480,0,4,12020,0},
    {12024,"Crashing Wave",135861,2,191919,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,12025,0,0,1480,12026,5,0,0},
