    {12030,"Hatecoil Crestrider",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Hurls lightning bolts at random targets.",-1,12031,60790,0,1480,0,18,12027,0},
    {12031,"Section 11",0,2,192138,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,64,1480,12421,19,12030,0},
    {12044,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Hyrja becomes empowered by Olmyr the Enlightened and Solsten depending upon which mystic she is closest to. As she becomes empowered she is granted particular abilities that grow in power over time. Moving Hyrja out of range of a mystic slowly reduces that mystic's empowerment.",-1,12045,0,0,1486,12052,1,0,0},
    {12045,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Move away from other players when affected with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192048|h[Expel Light]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;While Hyrja has |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192132|h[Mystic Empowerement: Thunder]|h|r be prepared to run to safety during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192305|h[Eye of the Storm]|h|r\n\n$bullet;While Hyrja has |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192133|h[Mystic Empowerement: Holy]|h|r avoid the orbs of light during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192307|h[Sanctify]|h|r",-1,0,0,2,1486,12046,2,12044,0},
    {12046,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Move away from other players when affected with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192048|h[Expel Light]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;While Hyrja has |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192132|h[Mystic Empowerement: Thunder]|h|r be prepared to run to safety during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192305|h[Eye of the Storm]|h|r\n\n$bullet;While Hyrja has |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192133|h[Mystic Empowerement: Holy]|h|r avoid the orbs of light during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192307|h[Sanctify]|h|r",-1,0,0,4,1486,12047,3,12044,0},
    {12047,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Move Hyrja between Olmyr and Solsten to manage how many stacks of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192132|h[Mystic Empowerement: Thunder]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192133|h[Mystic Empowerement: Holy]|h|r she has.\n\n$bullet;While Hyrja has |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192132|h[Mystic Empowerement: Thunder]|h|r be prepared to run to safety during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192305|h[Eye of the Storm]|h|r\n\n$bullet;While Hyrja has |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192133|h[Mystic Empowerement: Holy]|h|r avoid the orbs of light during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192307|h[Sanctify]|h|r",-1,0,0,1,1486,0,4,12044,0},
    {12048,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Lady Hatecoil assaults her enemies with raging storms and lightning strikes, using conductivity to her advantage. \n\n\n\n|cFF2959D3|Hspell:193597|h[Static Nova]|h|r strikes all players touching the water and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193611|h[Focused Lightning]|h|r can blow away sand dunes.",-1,12061,0,0,1490,12086,1,0,0},
    {12049,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"King Deepbeard attacks with an array of avoidable abilities. Normally, evade the damage, but if you are afflicted with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193018|h[Gaseous Bubbles]|h|r, seek out damaging effects to avoid triggering a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193047|h[Gaseous Explosion]|h|r.",-1,12058,0,0,1491,12087,1,0,0},
    {12051,"Section 6",0,2,192048,0,{"wago"},"$[!2,8,23\n\n\n\nIn this difficulty, after Expel Light bursts, the effect bounces to another player.$]",-1,0,0,0,1486,0,11,12053,0},
    {12052,"Section 7",0,2,192018,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,1486,12055,5,0,0},
    {12053,"Section 8",0,2,192133,1,{"wago"},"$[!2,8,23\n\n\n\nIn this difficulty, stacks of Mystic Empowerment: Holy slowly fade away while Hyrja is not being actively empowered by Olmyr the Enlightened.$]",-1,12054,0,0,1486,0,9,0,0},
    {12054,"Section 9",0,2,192307,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,1486,12051,10,12053,0},
    {12055,"Section 10",0,2,192132,1,{"wago"},"$[!2,8,23\n\n\n\nIn this difficulty, stacks of Mystic Empowerment: Thunder slowly fade away while Hyrja is not being actively empowered by Solsten.$]",-1,13650,0,0,1486,12053,6,0,0},
    {12056,"Section 11",0,2,191976,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,1486,0,8,12055,0},
    {12057,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The Wrath of Azshara crushes Queen Azshara's enemies with fierce storms and arcane energy, seeking to wash away her foes. Avoid the dangerous weather hazards and watch out when the storm intensifies!",-1,12064,0,0,1492,12085,1,0,0},
    {12058,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid taking damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193051|h[Call the Seas]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Move to avoid damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193171|h[Aftershock]|h|r after King Deepbeard casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193152|h[Quake]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,1491,12059,2,12049,0},
    {12059,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid damage when King Deepbeard casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193051|h[Call the Seas]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Move to avoid damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193171|h[Aftershock]|h|r after King Deepbeard casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193152|h[Quake]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,1491,12060,3,12049,0},
    {12060,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid damage when King Deepbeard casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193051|h[Call the Seas]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Move to avoid damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193171|h[Aftershock]|h|r after King Deepbeard casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193152|h[Quake]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;When King Deepbeard casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193093|h[Ground Slam]|h|r move to avoid damage!",-1,0,0,1,1491,0,4,12049,0},
    {12061,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Move on top of a sand dune to avoid damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193597|h[Static Nova]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Move away from sand dunes when |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193611|h[Focused Lightning]|h|r strikes to prevent it from destroying them.",-1,0,0,2,1490,12062,2,12048,0},
    {12062,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Move on top of a sand dune to avoid damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193597|h[Static Nova]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Move away from sand dunes when |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193611|h[Focused Lightning]|h|r strikes to prevent it from destroying them.",-1,0,0,4,1490,12063,3,12048,0},
    {12063,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Move on top of a sand dune to avoid damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193597|h[Static Nova]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Move away from sand dunes when |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193611|h[Focused Lightning]|h|r strikes to prevent it from destroying them.\n\n$bullet;Gain threat on loose Saltsea Globules when Lady Hatecoil casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193682|h[Beckon Storm]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,1490,0,4,12048,0},
    {12064,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid being sucked into the air by moving away from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192675|h[Mystic Tornado]|h|r when it spawns.\n\n$bullet;Move out of the detonation area of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192708|h[Arcane Bomb]|h|r once it has been dispelled.",-1,0,0,2,1492,12065,2,12057,0},
    {12065,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid being sucked into the air by moving away from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192675|h[Mystic Tornado]|h|r when it spawns.\n\n$bullet;Dispel |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192708|h[Arcane Bomb]|h|r from players so they can avoid its detonation.",-1,0,0,4,1492,12066,3,12057,0},
    {12066,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Remain within melee range of the Wrath of Azshara to prevent it from using |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192696|h[Raging Storms]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Avoid being sucked into the air by moving away from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192675|h[Mystic Tornado]|h|r when it spawns.\n\n$bullet;Move out of the area while |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192619|h[Massive Deluge]|h|r is being cast.",-1,0,0,1,1492,0,4,12057,0},
    {12067,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Tirathon begins the fight in his blood elf form, but uses Metamorphosis halfway through the encounter. Tirathon changes to one of two demonic forms at this time and uses new and altered abilities. The form that Tirathon chooses changes from week to week.",-1,12068,0,0,1467,12071,1,0,0},
    {12068,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;If Tirathon metamorphoses into a Vengeance demon he casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:202913|h[Fel Mortar]|h|r instead of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:191823|h[Furious Blast]|h|r. This will greatly increase the number of Furious Flames zones in the arena.\n\n$bullet;If Tirathon metamorphoses into a Havoc demon, use your damage reduction abilities to survive.",-1,0,0,2,1467,12069,2,12067,0},
    {12069,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:191823|h[Furious Blast]|h|r damages the entire party if Tirathon's cast is successful.\n\n$bullet;If Tirathon metamorphoses into a Havoc demon the entire party will take significant damage as the fight continues.",-1,0,0,4,1467,12070,3,12067,0},
    {12070,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:191941|h[Darkstrikes]|h|r inflicts substantial Shadow damage while active.\n\n$bullet;If Tirathon enters Vengeance form, reposition him to avoid his whirling Glaives.",-1,0,0,1,1467,0,4,12067,0},
    {12071,"Tirathon, Fallen Hunter",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,12072,0,0,1467,12075,5,0,0},
