    {12095,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Ash'golm gradually fills the chamber with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243622|h[Volcanic Eruption]|h|rs and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243632|h[Burning Embers]|h|r until he is frozen by the Warden's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244257|h[Deepfreeze Containment]|h|r. \n\n\n\nOnce frozen, Ash'golm and all Living Embers becomes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244248|h[Brittle]|h|r until he reheats and begins to fill the chamber with flame again.",-1,12096,0,0,1468,33224,1,0,0},
    {12096,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Activating |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244257|h[Deepfreeze Containment]|h|r removes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243566|h[Searing Mountain]|h|r from Ash'golm and causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243622s|h[Volcanic Eruption]|h|r to subside.",-1,0,0,1,1468,12097,2,12095,0},
    {12097,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;When |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243630|h[Burning Ember]|h|r expires, it spawns a Living Ember at the target's location.\n\n$bullet;Activating |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244257|h[Deepfreeze Containment]|h|r removes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243566|h[Searing Mountain]|h|r from Ash'golm and causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243622s|h[Volcanic Eruption]|h|r to subside.",-1,0,0,4,1468,12098,3,12095,0},
    {12098,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Activating |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244257|h[Deepfreeze Containment]|h|r causes Ash'golm and Living Embers to become |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244248|h[Brittle]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;When |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243632|h[Burning Ember]|h|r expires, it spawns a Living Ember at the target's location.",-1,0,0,2,1468,0,4,12095,0},
    {12104,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Hymdall uses his Horn of Valor to call in Storm Drakes to breathe lightning on the platform. As the fight progresses, the number of drakes called by the Horn of Valor increases.",-1,12105,0,0,1485,12110,1,0,0},
    {12105,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid standing near |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193235|h[Dancing Blade]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Do not be in front of Hymdall as he can cast |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193083|h[Bloodletting Sweep]|h|r without warning.\n\n$bullet;Beware the skies, as Storm Drakes strafe across the platform, leaving a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193260|h[Static Field]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,1485,12106,2,12104,0},
    {12106,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid standing near |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193235|h[Dancing Blade]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Do not be in front of Hymdall as he can cast |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193083|h[Bloodletting Sweep]|h|r without warning.\n\n$bullet;Beware the skies, as Storm Drakes strafe across the platform, leaving a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193260|h[Static Field]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,1485,12107,3,12104,0},
    {12107,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid standing near |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193235|h[Dancing Blade]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Face Hymdall away from other players as he can cast |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193083|h[Bloodletting Sweep]|h|r without warning.\n\n$bullet;Beware the skies, as Storm Drakes strafe across the platform, leaving a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193260|h[Static Field]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,1485,0,4,12104,0},
