    {12131,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Active Mitigation can be used to reduce the damage of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193668|h[Savage Blade]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Rely on the protective shield of the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193765|h[Aegis of Aggramar]|h|r to survive |cFF2959D3|Hspell:193827|h[Ragnarok]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,1488,0,4,12128,0},
