    {12341,"Overview",0,3,0,1,{"wago"},"Rokmora sheds Blightshard Skitters as he receives damage. These skitters leave behind |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192800|h[Choking Dust]|h|r when killed, damaging everyone nearby.$[!2,23\n\n\n\nOn Heroic difficulty, Any Blightshard Skitters that are alive when Rokmora uses Shatter are destroyed and inflict damage to the party with Rupturing Skitter.\n\n\n\nRokmora also creates Crystalline Ground that damages the party as they move across it.$]",-1,12342,0,0,1662,12348,1,0,0},
    {12342,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Kill Blightshard Skitters before they are destroyed by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:188114|h[Shatter]|h|r.",1,0,0,2,1662,13907,2,12341,0},
    {12343,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Rokmora inflicts massive damage with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:188114|h[Shatter]|h|r.",1,0,0,4,1662,13908,4,12341,0},
    {12344,"Tanks",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Face Rokomora away from the party to protect them from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:188169|h[Razor Shards]|h|r.",1,0,0,1,1662,13909,6,12341,0},
