    {12386,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Glazer releases chaotic orbs from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243769|h[Ocular Blast]|h|r that bounce around the arena.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, Glazer begins casting |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245312|h[Focused Beam]|h|r that can only be interrupted by reflecting it back at him.",-1,13899,0,0,1469,33413,1,0,0},
    {12389,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Lens' can reflect Glazer's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245312|h[Focused Beam]|h|r back at him, interrupting him.",-1,0,0,2,1469,0,4,12386,0},
    {12395,"Section 7",0,2,196376,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,4,1654,0,9,12298,0},
    {12396,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Using Elune's Light to properly counter Cordana's abilities is key to successfully defeating her.",-1,12397,0,0,1470,12414,1,0,0},
    {12397,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:197513|h[Detonating Moonglaive]|h|r causes you to take increased Physical damage.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:213576|h[Deepening Shadows]|h|r continue to spread across the platform unless destroyed by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192656|h[Elune's Light]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:197422|h[Creeping Doom's]|h|r spirits are invisible unless revealed by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192656|h[Elune's Light]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Quickly gain threat on Avatars of Vengeance that are revealed by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192656|h[Elune's Light]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,1470,12398,2,12396,0},
    {12398,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:197513|h[Detonating Moonglaive]|h|r causes victims caught in its blast to take increased Physical damage.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:213576|h[Deepening Shadows]|h|r continue to spread across the platform unless destroyed by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192656|h[Elune's Light]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:197422|h[Creeping Doom's]|h|r spirits are invisible unless revealed by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192656|h[Elune's Light]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Avatars of Vengeance continually target members of your party at random with their damaging abilities.",-1,0,0,4,1470,12399,3,12396,0},
    {12399,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Enemies revealed by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192656|h[Elune's Light]|h|r take $192752s1% more damage.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:213576|h[Deepening Shadows]|h|r continue to spread across the platform unless destroyed by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192656|h[Elune's Light]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:197422|h[Creeping Doom's]|h|r spirits are invisible unless revealed by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192656|h[Elune's Light]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Avatars of Vengeance must be revealed by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:192656|h[Elune's Light]|h|r, turning them into dangerous melee attackers.",-1,0,0,2,1470,0,4,12396,0},
