    {12414,"Elune's Light",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"Elune's Light can be acquired from the Glowing Sentry on Illidan's platform, and can be picked up during the encounter when it is removed by Cordana's various abilities.",-1,12400,0,32,1470,13402,5,0,0},
