    {12513,"Section 15",0,2,201733,2,{"wago"},nil,2,0,0,8,1672,12514,14,12512,0},
    {12514,"Section 16",0,2,199143,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,128,1672,12515,15,12512,0},
    {12515,"Section 17",0,2,199193,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,12964,0,0,1672,12653,16,12512,0},
    {12516,"Section 7",0,2,199345,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,1656,12517,7,12311,0},
    {12517,"Section 8",0,2,199389,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,1656,0,8,12311,0},
    {12518,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Naraxas emerges from a deep burrow to feed, drawing players towards her maw with her |cFF2959D3|Hspell:199176|h[Spiked Tongue]|h|r. As the fight progresses, additional drogbar jump into the area and run towards Naraxas as sacrifices, granting her stacks of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:199246|h[Ravenous]|h|r.$[!2,23\n\n\n\nOn Heroic difficulty, the crowd in the stands begins Hurling Rocks, doing continuous damage to the party.$]",-1,12519,0,0,1673,12522,1,0,0},
    {12519,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Kill drogbar before they can be devoured by Naraxas.\n\n$bullet;Avoid standing in pools of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:210150|h[Toxic Retch]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,1673,12520,2,12518,0},
    {12520,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Heal allies hit by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:188492|h[Rancid Maw]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Allies consumed by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:199176|h[Spiked Tongue]|h|r take massive damage.",1,0,0,4,1673,13910,3,12518,0},
    {12521,"Tanks",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;If Naraxas is not engaged in melee combat, she damages the entire party with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:198963|h[Putrid Skies]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Run away from Naraxas when she starts to cast |cFF2959D3|Hspell:199176|h[Spiked Tongue]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;At 20% health, Naraxas goes into a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:199775|h[Frenzy]|h|r.",1,0,0,1,1673,13911,5,12518,0},
