    {12817,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Skorpyron's lair is a constantly spawning chamber of scorpids that join the battle following |cFF2959D3|Hspell:204371|h[Call of the Scorpid]|h|r, but which also attack if any player strays too close.",-1,12818,0,0,1706,12825,1,0,0},
