    {13554,"The Nightborne",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"When Tichondrius exits the Illusionary Night for the first time, he begins to call the Nightborne to aid him.",-1,13515,0,0,1762,13555,20,0,0},
    {13555,"The Legion",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"When Tichondrius exits the Illusionary Night for the second time, he begins to call the Legion to aid him.",-1,13522,0,0,1762,0,28,0,0},
    {13556,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Levantus uses a variety of attacks that are very difficult to dodge when swimming through water. Remember to use |cFF2959D3|Hspell:217206|h[Gust of Wind]|h|r often to avoid damage!",-1,13557,0,0,1769,13560,1,0,0},
    {13557,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Grab the water walking ability from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:217206|h[Gust of Wind]|h|r to maintain your mobility while fighting Levantus.\n\n$bullet;Run around Levantus while she casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:217277|h[Massive Spout]|h|r to avoid taking massive damage.",-1,0,0,2,1769,13558,2,13556,0},
    {13558,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Grab the water walking ability from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:217206|h[Gust of Wind]|h|r to maintain your mobility while fighting Levantus.\n\n$bullet;Run around Levantus while she casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:217277|h[Massive Spout]|h|r to avoid taking massive damage.",-1,0,0,4,1769,13559,3,13556,0},
    {13559,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Swim around Levantus while she casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:217277|h[Massive Spout]|h|r to avoid taking massive damage.\n\n$bullet;Try to stay in melee range as often as possible to prevent Levantus from using |cFF2959D3|Hspell:217229|h[Rampaging Torrent]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,1769,0,4,13556,0},
