    {13699,"Parasitic Lasher",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},"Pursues the closest player and attempts to jump into them and afflict them with Parasitic Fetter. Once Parasitic Fetter is dispelled again, the parasite is recreated at the same health it had when it afflicted the target with Parasitic Fetter.",-1,13702,67025,0,1761,0,9,13686,0},
    {13700,"Parasitic Lasher",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Pursues the closest player and attempts to jump into them and afflict them with Parasitic Fetter. Once Parasitic Fetter is dispelled again, the parasite is recreated at the same health it had when it afflicted the target with Parasitic Fetter.",-1,13703,67025,0,1761,0,23,13693,0},
    {13702,"Section 27",0,2,219248,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,1761,0,10,13699,0},
    {13703,"Section 28",0,2,219248,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,1761,0,24,13700,0},
    {13704,"Overview",0,3,0,1,{"wago"},"During the fight, Na'zak the Fiend shakes Ley-Infused Rubble loose from the ceiling, and begins to absorb its energy with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:219813|h[Absorb Leystones]|h|r. For each Leystone still on the ground when he finishes casting, Na'zak gains a charge of  |cFF2959D3|Hspell:219836|h[Ley Infusion]|h|r.",-1,13705,0,0,1783,13708,1,0,0},
    {13705,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,1,{"wago"},"$bullet;Do not stand in front of the boss during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:219349|h[Corroding Spray]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Collect Ley-Infused Rubble before Na'zak absorbs their energy.\n\n$bullet;Attack allies encased by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:219861|h[Web Wrap]|h|r to free them.",-1,0,0,2,1783,13706,2,13704,0},
    {13706,"Tanks",0,3,0,1,{"wago"},"$bullet;Face Na'zak the Fiend away from allies to avoid hitting them with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:219349|h[Corroding Spray]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,1783,13707,3,13704,0},
    {13707,"Healers",0,3,0,1,{"wago"},"$bullet;Do not stand in front of the boss during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:219349|h[Corroding Spray]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Collect Ley-Infused Rubble before Na'zak absorbs their energy.\n\n$bullet;Allies take massive damage during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:219836|h[Ley Infusion]|h|r",-1,0,0,4,1783,0,4,13704,0},
    {13708,"Section 1",0,2,219349,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,1783,13732,5,0,0},
    {13709,"Section 10",0,2,219498,2,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,4096,1718,13067,6,0,0},
    {13722,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"As the fight progresses, Drugon hurls |cFF2959D3|Hspell:219542|h[Avalanche]|h|r at random enemy target destinations. Targets hit by this ability become |cFF2959D3|Hspell:219812|h[Frozen]|h|r and take increased damage from following attacks.",-1,13723,0,0,1789,13727,1,0,0},
    {13723,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid standing in front of Drugon during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:219602|h[Snow Plow]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Avoid getting hit with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:219542|h[Avalanche]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,1789,13724,2,13722,0},
    {13724,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Allies affected by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:219812|h[Frozen]|h|r take increased damage from all attacks.\n\n$bullet;Heal allies being gripped by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:219610|h[Snow Plow]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Avoid getting hit by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:219542|h[Avalanche]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,1789,13725,3,13722,0},
    {13725,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Face Drugon away from allies to avoid hitting them with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:219493|h[Snow Crash]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Avoid standing in front of Drugon during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:219602|h[Snow Plow]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,1789,0,4,13722,0},
