    {13824,"Stage One: Division of Power",0,0,0,3,{"wago"},"On Mythic difficutly, High Botanist Tel'arn starts the fight in his three pure forms and no longer shares health between the forms. Whenever a form dies, the remaining are healed to full health and gain additional effects on their abilities.",0,13825,0,4096,1761,14467,29,0,0},
