    {14409,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;During the initial phase, lead the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:229242|h[Fel Beam]|h|r away from your allies.\n\n$bullet;Avoid taking damage from the Legion Command Ship's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:229284|h[Bombardment]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;While on a Legion Command Ship, avoid being knocked off by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:229151|h[Disintegrate]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,1838,14411,3,14408,0},
    {14410,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;During the initial phase, lead the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:229242|h[Fel Beam]|h|r away from your allies.\n\n$bullet;Avoid taking damage from the Legion Command Ship's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:229284|h[Bombardment]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;While on a Legion Command Ship, avoid being knocked off by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:229151|h[Disintegrate]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;In the final phase, prevent |cFF2959D3|Hspell:230084|h[Stabilize Rift]|h|r from completing.",-1,0,0,2,1838,14409,2,14408,0},
    {14411,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid taking damage from the Legion Command Ship's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:229284|h[Bombardment]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;While on a Legion Command Ship, avoid being knocked off by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:229151|h[Disintegrate]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;In the final phase prevent |cFF2959D3|Hspell:230084|h[Stabilize Rift]|h|r from completing.",-1,0,0,1,1838,0,4,14408,0},
