    {14590,"Tanks",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;When afflicted with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:230201|h[Burden of Pain]|h|r, attempt to minimize Physical damage taken.\n\n$bullet;Avoid being struck by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:232722|h[Slicing Tornado]|h|r to prevent unnecessary damage.",0,0,0,1,1861,0,7,14587,0},
