    {14970,"Tormented Souls",0,0,0,3,{"wago"},"Upon reaching 30% health, the Engine of Souls draws forth a vast number of tormented spirits to form the Desolate Host.$[!16\n\n\n\nIn Mythic difficulty, this begins a chain reaction that destroys the Spiritual Fonts.$]",0,14971,0,0,1896,0,38,0,0},
