    {15550,"Tormented Soul",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"A massive soul has coalesced within Belac's cage, trapped and tormented for thousands of years.  While on the surface it is no more than a mass of ill will and pain, remnants of hope from long-forgotten prisoners remain trapped inside.",-1,15551,75615,0,1867,15307,20,0,0},
