    {15628,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Teron Gorefiend periodically marks a player with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:40251|h[Shadow of Death]|h|r, killing them instantly. The slain player then returns as a Vengeful Spirit, with the unique ability to hinder and destroy Shadowy Constructs that will otherwise decimate other players.",-1,15629,0,0,1585,15632,1,0,0},
