    {15630,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Be prepared to become a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:40251|h[Shadow of Death].|h|r\n\n$bullet;Be quick to dispel |cFF2959D3|Hspell:40239|h[Incinerate]|h|r to avoid damage.\n\n$bullet;Targets afflicted by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:40243|h[Crushing Shadows]|h|r are especially susceptible to Shadow damage.",-1,0,0,4,1585,15631,3,15628,0},
    {15631,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Hold the attention of Teron Gorefiend.",-1,0,0,1,1585,0,4,15628,0},
