    {15861,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Zuraal uses the void to empower himself and injure his opponents. |cFF2959D3|Hspell:244579|h[Decimate]|h|r creates pools of damaging void energy, while |cFF2959D3|Hspell:244602|h[Coalesced Void]|h|r triggers a devastating |cFF2959D3|Hspell:244599|h[Dark Expulsion]|h|r when it reaches Zuraal.",-1,15862,0,0,1979,34292,1,0,0},
    {15862,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263399|h[Oozing Slam]|h|r causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:244602|h[Coalesced Void]|h|r to spawn, which erupts in a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:244599|h[Dark Expulsion]|h|r when they reach Zuraal.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:244579|h[Decimate]|h|r leaves behind |cFF2959D3|Hspell:244588|h[Void Sludge]|h|r in its impact area.",-1,0,0,2,1979,15863,2,15861,0},
    {15863,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263399|h[Oozing Slam]|h|r causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:244602|h[Coalesced Void]|h|r to spawn, which erupts in a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:244599|h[Dark Expulsion]|h|r when they reach Zuraal.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:244579|h[Decimate]|h|r leaves behind |cFF2959D3|Hspell:244588|h[Void Sludge]|h|r in its impact area.",-1,0,0,4,1979,15864,3,15861,0},
    {15864,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263440|h[Void Slash]|h|r inflicts heavy Physical and Shadow damage.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263399|h[Oozing Slam]|h|r causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:244602|h[Coalesced Void]|h|r to spawn, which erupts in a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:244599|h[Dark Expulsion]|h|r when they reach Zuraal.",-1,0,0,1,1979,0,4,15861,0},
