    {15919,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Viceroy Nezhar creates a ring of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263529|h[Collapsing Void]|h|r that becomes a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263532|h[Void Storm]|h|r. Nezhar also blasts players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263542|h[Mass Void Infusion]|h|r that leaves behind void energy.\n\n\n\nUmbral Tentacles answer the viceroy's call and attacks players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1268733|h[Mind Flay]|h|r.",-1,15920,0,0,1981,34302,1,0,0},
    {15920,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265030|h[Void Storm]|h|r inflicts heavy Shadow damage to players caught within it.\n\n$bullet;Umbral Tentacles channel |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1268733|h[Mind Flay]|h|r on a random player.",-1,0,0,2,1981,15921,2,15919,0},
    {15921,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265030|h[Void Storm]|h|r inflicts heavy Shadow damage to players caught within it.\n\n$bullet;Umbral Tentacles channel |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1268733|h[Mind Flay]|h|r on a random player.",-1,0,0,4,1981,15922,3,15919,0},
    {15922,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265030|h[Void Storm]|h|r inflicts heavy Shadow damage to players caught within it.\n\n$bullet;Viceroy Nezhar demolishes his current target with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:244750|h[Mind Blast]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,1981,0,4,15919,0},
