    {15970,"Tanks",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Position the Maiden of Valor in |cFF2959D3|Hspell:233556|h[Corrupted Matrix]|h|r to prevent the Fallen Avatar from gaining energy.\n\n$bullet;Take turns tanking the Fallen Avatar to manage the application of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:236494|h[Desolate]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Move away from the Fallen Avatar while he casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:239132|h[Rupture Realities]|h|r.",0,0,0,1,1873,15971,4,14705,0},
    {15971,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Help soak the effects of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:239739|h[Dark Mark]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Avoid |cFF2959D3|Hspell:234059|h[Unbound Chaos]|h|r and the targets of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:236604|h[Shadowy Blades]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Move away from the Fallen Avatar while he casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:239132|h[Rupture Realities]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Focus damage on the Maiden of Valor while she is casting |cFF2959D3|Hspell:233856|h[Cleansing Protocol]|h|r to trigger a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:233739|h[Malfunction]|h|r.",0,0,0,2,1873,14707,5,14705,0},
