    {15982,"Ember of Taeshalach",0,1,0,2,{"wago"},"These fragments of Taeshalach's essence move towards Aggramar.  Upon reaching him they recombine with Taeshalach, causing a Blazing Eruption.",0,16190,1070,0,1984,16197,71,16053,0},
    {15983,"Section 45",0,2,244912,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,1984,16696,73,15982,0},
    {15996,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"L'ura summons |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265419|h[Notes of Despair]|h|r that continue to play |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265421|h[Dirge of Despair]|h|r until they are destroyed. L'ura occasionally targets players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265464|h[Discordant Beam]|h|r that inflicts heavy Shadow damage and also silences any |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265419|h[Notes of Despair]|h|r it hits.\n\n\n\nWhen all the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265419|h[Notes of Despair]|h|r are silenced, Alleria destroys them with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1266643|h[Shattering Shot]|h|r.",-1,15997,0,0,1982,16000,1,0,0},
    {15997,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265464|h[Discordant Beam]|h|r inflicts heavy Shadow damage to each targeted player and silences any |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265419|h[Notes of Despair]|h|r it hits.\n\n$bullet; Alleria's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265999|h[Siphon Void]|h|r causes L'ura to take massively increased damage.",-1,0,0,2,1982,15998,2,15996,0},
    {15998,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265421|h[Dirge of Despair]|h|r continues to damage all players until all |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265419|h[Notes of Despair]|h|r are silenced.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265464|h[Discordant Beam]|h|r inflicts heavy Shadow damage to each targeted player and silences any |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265419|h[Notes of Despair]|h|r it hits.",-1,0,0,4,1982,15999,3,15996,0},
    {15999,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Each |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1267207|h[Abyssal Lance]|h|r inflicts Shadow damage to the target player.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265464|h[Discordant Beam]|h|r inflicts heavy Shadow damage to each targeted player and silences any |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265419|h[Notes of Despair]|h|r it hits.",-1,0,0,1,1982,0,4,15996,0},
