    {16421,"The Unmaking of Creation",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The Speaker has heard the anguished whispers of the Unmaker, an emerald star calling out from the darkness. Little is known of him, only that his once-noble soul has been twisted by ages of endless torment.",-1,16932,0,0,2031,16931,1,0,0},
