    {16457,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Vol'kaal is empowered by Yazma's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:250192|h[Bad Voodoo]|h|r until all of the Reanimation Totems are destroyed. Once all of the totems are destroyed, Vol'kaal begins to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:250241|h[Rapid Decay]|h|r.",-1,16458,0,0,2036,16462,1,0,0},
