    {16966,"Section 28",0,2,255200,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,1,2031,0,29,16964,0},
    {16971,"Stage Three: The Arcane Masters",0,0,0,2,{"wago"},"When Argus reaches 40% health, he is sufficiently weakened such that Aman'Thul is able to subdue him with a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:257645|h[Temporal Blast]|h|r. \n\n\n\nOr, so it seems...",0,0,0,0,2031,16989,44,0,0},
    {16987,"Section 27",0,2,257296,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2031,16955,11,16931,0},
    {16989,"Stage Four: The Gift of Life, The Forge of Loss",0,0,0,2,{"wago"},"His Constellar Designates buying him the time to regain his strength, Argus kills the players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:256542|h[Reap Soul]|h|r. All hope would be lost, were it not for the titans...",0,17117,0,0,2031,0,45,0,0},
    {16990,"Section 50",0,2,258039,2,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,1,2031,16992,51,16989,0},
    {16991,"Section 53",0,2,257299,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2031,16965,47,16989,0},
    {16992,"Reorigination Modules",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Reorigination Modules will begin an Initialization Sequence when created.\n\n\n\nWhen their health is consumed, they will cast Reorigination Pulse.",-1,16993,81327,0,2031,17000,52,16989,0},
    {16993,"Section 55",0,2,256388,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2031,16995,53,16992,0},
    {16995,"Section 56",0,2,256393,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2031,0,54,16992,0},
    {16996,"Eonar's Aid",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,17050,0,0,2031,17002,59,16989,0},
    {16999,"Section 61",0,2,256399,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2031,0,62,17051,0},
    {17000,"The Spirit World",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,17001,0,0,2031,16996,55,16989,0},
    {17001,"Hungering Souls",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Hungering Souls stalk the spirit world, released by Argus' wrath. If they come into contact with any ghosts they will burst, applying Soul Detonation to any nearby ghosts.",-1,17004,51658,0,2031,17005,56,17000,0},
    {17002,"Khaz'goroth's Aid",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"When Khaz'goroth has at least 20 Titanic Essence, he will begin to channel Titanforging.\n\n\n\nPlayers can collect Motes of Titanic Power within the Spirit World to grant Khaz'goroth Titanic Energy.",-1,17003,0,0,2031,0,63,16989,0},
    {17003,"Section 63",0,2,257214,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,17006,0,0,2031,0,64,17002,0},
    {17004,"Section 66",0,2,256899,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2031,0,57,17001,0},
    {17005,"Motes of Titanic Power",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"When Reorigination Modules complete a Reorigination Pulse, their Titanic energy is released into the Spirit World as Motes of Titanic Power. Players can walk into these to collect them, granting Khaz'goroth Titanic Essence that he can use to fuel his Titanforging ability.",-1,0,0,0,2031,0,58,17000,0},
    {17006,"Section 68",0,2,257215,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2031,0,65,17003,0},
    {17007,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The Coin-Operated Puemmler becomes empowered when it consumes nearby coin piles with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:271903|h[Coin Magnet]|h|r, gaining stacks of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:271867|h[Pay To Win]|h|r .",-1,31416,0,0,2109,31432,1,0,0},
    {17008,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid the Pummeler's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:257337|h[Shocking Claw]|h|r.",3,0,0,2,2109,31415,3,17007,0},
    {17009,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:262347|h[Static Pulse]|h|r leaves lingering electricity on players that damages them.",3,0,0,4,2109,31414,5,17007,0},
    {17010,"Tanks",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;The Pummeler becomes empowered for each stack of coin it consumes from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:271903|h[Coin Magnet]|h|r \n\n$bullet;Keep the Pummeler stationary to enable allies to accurately |cFF2959D3|Hspell:255996|h[Punt]|h|r Azerite footbombs.",0,0,0,1,2109,0,7,17007,0},
    {17011,"Pursuite",0,2,257407,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,16835,0,16,2083,16837,7,0,0},
    {17012,"Section 10",0,2,257402,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,32,2095,17015,6,17013,0},
    {17013,"Loaded Dice",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"Harlan Sweete rolls his magically loaded dice at 60% and 30% health remaining, gaining an advantage in combat.",-1,17012,0,0,2095,16942,5,0,0},
    {17015,"Section 12",0,2,257458,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,1,2095,0,7,17013,0},
    {17016,"Section 56",0,2,257485,3,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,0,1987,16719,23,16717,0},
    {17017,"Section 55",0,2,257238,2,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,32,1987,16720,37,15836,0},
    {17018,"Section 54",0,2,257484,3,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,0,1987,0,40,16720,0},
    {17019,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The three leaders of Freehold's crews enter combat together. Joining one of the Captains and his or her crew prior to engaging with the Council will earn you an ally, drastically improving your chances and negating the effects of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:257821|h[Under One Banner]|h|r.",-1,17020,0,0,2093,17024,1,0,0},
    {17020,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Free allies disoriented by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:258337|h[Blackout Barrel]|h|r by destroying the barrels.",-1,0,0,2,2093,17021,2,17019,0},
    {17021,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Keep allies at maximum health as |cFF2959D3|Hspell:256979|h[Powder Shot]|h|r deals significant damage to random players.",-1,0,0,4,2093,17022,3,17019,0},
    {17022,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Free allies disoriented by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:258337|h[Blackout Barrel]|h|r by destroying the barrels.",-1,0,0,1,2093,0,4,17019,0},
