    {17035,"Forces of the Legion",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"These creatures warp in at various locations and move directly to Eonar's essence. If they reach her essence they will inflict damage to her until they are defeated.",-1,17036,0,2,2025,16500,37,0,0},
