    {17046,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Interrupt |cFF2959D3|Hspell:248321|h[Conflagration]|h|r when the raid has safely arrived on the correct platform to prevent |cFF2959D3|Hspell:248424|h[Gathering Power]|h|r from stacking too high.\n\n$bullet;Avoid triggering traps such as |cFF2959D3|Hspell:247641|h[Stasis Trap]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:247962|h[Blastwire]|h|r when traversing the walkways!\n\n$bullet;Move away from players afflicted with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:247552|h[Sleep Canister]|h|r to avoid |cFF2959D3|Hspell:247565|h[Slumber Gas]|h|r.",0,0,0,2,2009,16202,3,16200,0},
