    {17050,"Gift of the Lifebinder",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Eonar causes the Gift of the Lifebinder to spring forth to save the players. While the Gift of the Lifebinder lives, players may freely Release Spirit after dying. If players move to the tree as ghosts, they will be returned to life, at the cost of some of the Gift of the Lifebinder's Life Energy.\n\n\n\nWhen the Gift of the Lifebinder's Life Energy is depleted, it becomes the Withered Gift of the Lifebinder.",-1,17051,80581,0,2031,0,60,16996,0},
    {17051,"Withered Gift of the Lifebinder",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Players may heal the Withered Gift of the Lifebinder. Additionally, when they use it to resurrect, it is afflicted by Withering Roots.",-1,16999,81089,0,2031,0,61,17050,0},
    {17064,"Section 28",0,0,0,2,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,0,1986,16563,8,16553,0},
