    {17077,"The Stellar Armory",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"Periodically, two of the Constellar Designates will be granted arms from the Stellar Armory. When equipped with these arms, the Designates will no longer use their other abilities and will instead engage in melee attacks.",-1,17078,0,0,2031,0,38,17070,0},
