    {17091,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Azerokk's Earthrager allies are dangerous if left uncontrolled, and can inflict heavy damage even to the sturdiest foes. Control them with crowd control or with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:257481|h[Fracking Totem]|h|r as left behind by the Venture Co. Seismologists.",-1,25980,0,0,2114,17113,1,0,0},
    {17092,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Run from Earthragers that target you with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:257582|h[Raging Gaze]|h|r, and snare them if possible.",1,0,0,2,2114,0,5,17091,0},
    {17093,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Run from Earthragers that target you with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:257582|h[Raging Gaze]|h|r, and snare them if possible.",-1,0,0,4,2114,17094,3,17091,0},
    {17094,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Keep Azerokk away from your allies to protect them from one source of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:258628|h[Resonant Quake]|h|r.",-1,0,0,3,2114,17092,4,17091,0},
    {17095,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Rixxa Fluxflame will spray |cFF2959D3|Hspell:259022|h[Azerite Catalyst]|h|r at players, which will leave behind patches of the toxic substance. Rixxa will push patches of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:259022|h[Azerite Catalyst]|h|r away from her when she targets players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:259940|h[Propellant Blast]|h|r.",-1,17096,0,0,2115,18920,1,0,0},
    {17096,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Be mindful of where Rixxa places her |cFF2959D3|Hspell:259022|h[Azerite Catalyst]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Avoid being pushed into |cFF2959D3|Hspell:259022|h[Azerite Catalyst]|h|r by Rixxa's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:259940|h[Propellant Blast]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2115,17097,2,17095,0},
    {17097,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Be mindful of where Rixxa places her |cFF2959D3|Hspell:259022|h[Azerite Catalyst]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Avoid being pushed into |cFF2959D3|Hspell:259022|h[Azerite Catalyst]|h|r by Rixxa's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:259940|h[Propellant Blast]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,2115,17098,3,17095,0},
    {17098,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Maneuver Rixxa away from patches of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:259022|h[Azerite Catalyst]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Be mindful of where Rixxa places her |cFF2959D3|Hspell:259022|h[Azerite Catalyst]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Avoid being pushed into |cFF2959D3|Hspell:259022|h[Azerite Catalyst]|h|r by Rixxa's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:259940|h[Propellant Blast]|h|r.",-1,0,0,3,2115,0,4,17095,0},
    {17099,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Mogul Razdunk's Azerite-powered war machine can attack players at ground level with guns, as well as from the air with a powerful drill.",-1,17100,0,0,2116,18916,1,0,0},
    {17100,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Minimize the number of your allies struck by explosions from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:260838|h[Homing Missile]|h|r when you are targeted.\n\n$bullet;Mogul Razdunk must strike |cFF2959D3|Hspell:270277|h[Big Red Rocket]|h|r shells with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:260202|h[Drill Smash]|h|r to force him to return to the ground.",-1,0,0,2,2116,17101,2,17099,0},
    {17101,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Lead |cFF2959D3|Hspell:260838|h[Homing Missile]|h|r away from your allies to limit the number of targets it can damage.\n\n$bullet;Mogul Razdunk must strike |cFF2959D3|Hspell:270277|h[Big Red Rocket]|h|r shells with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:260202|h[Drill Smash]|h|r to force him to return to the ground.",-1,0,0,4,2116,17102,3,17099,0},
    {17102,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Mogul Razdunk will call Venture Co. Skyscorchers in to assist him when he begins Death from Above.\n\n$bullet;Mogul Razdunk must strike |cFF2959D3|Hspell:270277|h[Big Red Rocket]|h|r shells with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:260202|h[Drill Smash]|h|r to force him to return to the ground.",-1,0,0,1,2116,0,4,17099,0},
