    {17346,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Auriaya patrols the Observation Ring with her four Sanctum Sentries which will ravage their target with a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:64666|h[Savage Pounce]|h|r when engaged. She summons other guardians during the encounter which she commands to disrupt her enemies.",-1,17347,0,0,1643,17350,1,0,0},
    {17347,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Stop casting spells to avoid being interrupted while the Feral Defender is casting |cFF2959D3|Hspell:64496|h[Feral Rush]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Interrupt Auriaya's casts of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:64389|h[Sentinel Blast]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Assist in splitting the damage of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:64422|h[Sonic Screech]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,1643,17348,2,17346,0},
    {17348,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Be prepared for heavy damage when Auriaya is engaged from her Sanctum Sentry's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:64666|h[Savage Pounce]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Assist in splitting the damage of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:64422|h[Sonic Screech]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Stop casting spells to avoid being interrupted while the Feral Defender is casting |cFF2959D3|Hspell:64496|h[Feral Rush]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,1643,17349,3,17346,0},
