    {17507,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Cragmaw's abilities shed Blood Tick Larvae throughout the arena. Deal with Cragmaw's attacks while stomping on Blood Tick Larvae before their |cFF2959D3|Hspell:260416|h[Metamorphosis]|h|r can complete.",-1,17508,0,0,2131,17514,1,0,0},
