    {17749,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Sergeant Bainbridge fixates on a random enemy and attempts to catch them with his |cFF2959D3|Hspell:261106|h[Hangman's Noose]|h|r. The longer Bainbridge chases enemies, the faster he gets with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:257649|h[Boiling Rage]|h|r.\n\n\n\nAs the fight progresses, Kul Tiran forces engage the party while the area is bombarded by a continual |cFF2959D3|Hspell:257585|h[Cannon Barrage]|h|r.\n\n\n\n|cFF2959D3|Hspell:273716|h[Heavy Ordnance]|h|r appears during the barrage, and  unless it is detonated before time expires it will explode and damage the party.",-1,17750,0,0,2133,17753,1,0,0},
    {17750,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Kill Kul Tiran forces.\n\n$bullet;When the target of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:260954|h[Iron Gaze]|h|r, run away.",-1,0,0,2,2133,17751,2,17749,0},
    {17751,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Kul Tiran Marskmen inflict damage to everyone in the party.\n\n$bullet;If |cFF2959D3|Hspell:273716|h[Heavy Ordnance]|h|r explodes it does massive damage to the party.\n\n$bullet;When the target of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:260954|h[Iron Gaze]|h|r, run away.",-1,0,0,4,2133,17752,3,17749,0},
    {17752,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid being in melee range with Sergeant Bainbridge due to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:256867|h[Heavy Hitter]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Face Kul Tiran Vanguard's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:257292|h[Heavy Slash]|h|r away from the party.\n\n$bullet;Run over |cFF2959D3|Hspell:273716|h[Heavy Ordnance]|h|r to prevent them from damaging the party.",-1,0,0,1,2133,0,4,17749,0},
    {17753,"Section 5",0,2,256867,2,{"wago"},nil,2,0,0,32,2133,17754,5,0,0},
    {17754,"Section 6",0,2,260954,2,{"wago"},nil,2,17761,0,0,2133,17756,6,0,0},
