    {18242,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Focus attacks to defeat the Forgotten Denizens when afflicted by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:267360|h[Grasp of the Sunken City]|h|r to return to the surface.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:269419|h[Yawning Gate]|h|r silences and damages all players in an area around Vol'zith the Whisperer.",1,0,0,2,2156,17906,2,17905,0},
    {18243,"Tanks",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Beware that Sunken Denizens have heavy melee attacks due to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:267548|h[Leviathan's Wake]|h|r. Defeat one while afflicted with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:267360|h[Grasp of the Sunken City]|h|r to return to the surface.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:269419|h[Yawning Gate]|h|r silences and damages all players in an area around Vol'zith the Whisperer.",1,0,0,1,2156,17908,5,17905,0},
    {18244,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Dominated by Zul's dark magic, Dazar returns from the dead with his overwhelming martial prowess intact. \n\n\n\nAt $269563s1% health, he calls for his hunting raptor Raban to join the fray.\n\n\n\nAt $269563s2% health, he mounts for T'zala, his loyal steed, who protects him with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:269351|h[Eternal Guardian]|h|r.\n\n\n\nFinally, at $269563s3%, he activates the spear launchers in his room, which continue to fire at players until Dazar is defeated.",-1,18245,0,0,2172,18248,1,0,0},
    {18245,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;The last two hits of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:268586|h[Blade Combo]|h|r deal very heavy damage. Save defensive abilities for them.\n\n$bullet;When Reban joins the battle, move to intercept him before he attacks other members of the group.",-1,0,0,1,2172,18246,2,18244,0},
    {18246,"Healer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:268586|h[Blade Combo]|h|r will deal heavy damage to your tank.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:268932|h[Quaking Leap]|h|r deals group damage that decreases the further you are away from the targeted player. If you are targeted, move away from the group, and move away from other players who are targeted!",-1,0,0,4,2172,18247,3,18244,0},
    {18247,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;If you are targeted with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:268932|h[Quaking Leap]|h|r, move away from the group - or, if another player is targeted, move away from them!",-1,0,0,2,2172,0,4,18244,0},
    {18248,"Section 5",0,2,268403,2,{"wago"},nil,2,0,0,0,2172,18249,5,0,0},
