    {18588,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The Hailstone Construct uses a variety of attacks to chill its enemies, from inflicting Frost damage in its melee swings to massive AOE attacks that both slow and freeze anyone hit.",-1,18589,0,0,2197,18584,1,0,0},
    {18589,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:274888|h[Ice-rimed Fists]|h|r causes all of Hailstone Construct's attacks to cause Frost damage instead of Physical, so magical defenses will be handy.\n\n$bullet;Use cover created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:274896|h[Permafrost Spike]|h|r to avoid being frozen by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:274895|h[Freezing Tempest]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Move to avoid |cFF2959D3|Hspell:274891|h[Glacial Breath]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2197,18590,2,18588,0},
    {18590,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Use cover created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:274896|h[Permafrost Spike]|h|r to avoid being frozen by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:274895|h[Freezing Tempest]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Move to avoid |cFF2959D3|Hspell:274891|h[Glacial Breath]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2197,18591,3,18588,0},
    {18591,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Use cover created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:274896|h[Permafrost Spike]|h|r to avoid being frozen by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:274895|h[Freezing Tempest]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Move to avoid |cFF2959D3|Hspell:274891|h[Glacial Breath]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Tanks may required additional healing since |cFF2959D3|Hspell:274888|h[Ice-rimed Fists]|h|r causes all of Hailstone Construct's attacks to cause Frost damage instead of Physical.",-1,0,0,4,2197,0,4,18588,0},
    {18592,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Warbringer Yenajz periodically calls down |cFF2959D3|Hspell:274904|h[Reality Tears]|h|r and draws players in to the center of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:274932|h[Endless Abyss]|h|r.",-1,18593,0,0,2198,18596,1,0,0},
    {18593,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid |cFF2959D3|Hspell:274904|h[Reality Tear]|h|r as they impact the ground.\n\n$bullet;Quickly move away from Warbringer Yenajz when he casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:274932|h[Endless Abyss]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:274842|h[Void Nova]|h|r inflicts heavy unavoidable damage.",-1,0,0,1,2198,18594,2,18592,0},
    {18594,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid |cFF2959D3|Hspell:274904|h[Reality Tear]|h|r as they impact the ground.\n\n$bullet;Quickly move away from Warbringer Yenajz when he casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:274932|h[Endless Abyss]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:274842|h[Void Nova]|h|r inflicts heavy unavoidable damage.",-1,0,0,4,2198,18595,3,18592,0},
    {18595,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid |cFF2959D3|Hspell:274904|h[Reality Tear]|h|r as they impact the ground.\n\n$bullet;Quickly move away from Warbringer Yenajz when he casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:274932|h[Endless Abyss]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:274842|h[Void Nova]|h|r inflicts heavy unavoidable damage.",-1,0,0,2,2198,0,4,18592,0},
    {18596,"Section 5",0,2,274842,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2198,18597,5,0,0},
