    {19349,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Ensure only one ranged player receives |cFF2959D3|Hspell:283524|h[Aphotic Blast]|h|r from Zaxasj the Speaker to minimize its effects.\n\n$bullet;Stagger interrupts on |cFF2959D3|Hspell:283540|h[Witness the End]|h|r to manage incoming damage.\n\n$bullet;Destroy |cFF2959D3|Hspell:282515|h[Visage from Beyond]|h|r before it can cast |cFF2959D3|Hspell:282517|h[Terrifying Echo]|h|r.",0,0,0,2,2328,18968,3,18966,0},
