    {19540,"Soul of the Tidepriest",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"When Brother Joseph dies, his soul appears and begins channeling |cFF2959D3|Hspell:284864|h[Greater Tidal Empowerment]|h|r on Laminaria. When both Tidepriests are dead, their souls depart.",-1,19541,0,32,2337,0,25,19262,0},
