    {19688,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:282447|h[Kimbul's Wrath]|h|r is continuously spread throughout the raid during the encounter.\n\n$bullet;Dispel allies affected by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:285878|h[Mind Wipe]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Move to Pa'ku during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:282107|h[Pa'ku's Wrath]|h|r to avoid taking lethal damage.\n\n$bullet;When you dispel |cFF2959D3|Hspell:284663|h[Bwonsamdi's Wrath]|h|r it will jump to the closest target that does not have this effect.",0,0,0,4,2330,19842,4,19009,0},
