    {20193,"Intermission: The Moulting Hatchery",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"Orogozoa departs from the egg chamber and makes its way to the Naga chambers, below. All stacks of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:298242|h[Incubation Fluid]|h|r reset.",-1,20194,0,0,2351,19970,19,0,0},
