    {20471,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Defeat Horrific Summoners before the raid becomes overwhelmed.\n\n$bullet;Defeat Horrific Visions before they transform into Unleashed Nightmares.\n\n$bullet;Focus damage on Za'qul's echoes while he is casting |cFF2959D3|Hspell:301068|h[Psychotic Split]|h|r to trigger |cFF2959D3|Hspell:296084|h[Mind Fracture]|h|r.\n\n$bullet:Don't stop moving when affected by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:293509|h[Manifest Nightmares]|h|r to avoid |cFF2959D3|Hspell:303819|h[Nightmare Pools]|h|r.",0,0,0,2,2349,20872,2,19911,0},
