    {21348,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Utilize |cFF2959D3|Hspell:307839|h[Devoured Abyss]|h|r to escape the effects of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:308044|h[Stygian Annihilation]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Avoid triggering |cFF2959D3|Hspell:314992|h[Drain Essence]|h|r near allies.",0,0,0,4,2365,21349,7,20551,0},
    {21349,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Utilize |cFF2959D3|Hspell:307839|h[Devoured Abyss]|h|r to escape the effects of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:308044|h[Stygian Annihilation]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Avoid triggering |cFF2959D3|Hspell:314992|h[Drain Essence]|h|r near allies.\n\n$bullet;Remove |cFF2959D3|Hspell:314337|h[Ancient Curse]|h|r before the curse becomes deadly.",0,0,0,4,2365,0,8,20551,0},
    {21350,"Tanks",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Take turns tanking to mitigate the effects of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:307545|h[Shadow Claws]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:307399|h[Shadow Wounds]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Utilize |cFF2959D3|Hspell:307839|h[Devoured Abyss]|h|r to escape the effects of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:308044|h[Stygian Annihilation]|h|r and interrupt the spellcasting of Dark Manifestations.\n\n$bullet;Intercept orbs of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:306290|h[Forbidden Mana]|h|r before they reach Maut and use their power to aid your allies.",0,0,0,1,2365,20552,2,20551,0},
    {21351,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Utilize |cFF2959D3|Hspell:307839|h[Devoured Abyss]|h|r to escape the effects of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:308044|h[Stygian Annihilation]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Quickly break Maut's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:306005|h[Obsidian Skin]|h|r before it completes its cast of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:305722|h[Obsidian Shatter]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Destroy Dark Manifestations before they're able to aid Maut.",0,0,0,2,2365,20592,4,20551,0},
