    {21428,"Clotted Corruption",0,1,0,2,{"wago"},"When Il'gynoth submerges and his organs are revealed, a deadly Clotted Corruption forms. Capable of absorbing the Blood of Ny'alotha, this mass of plasma can quickly grow out of control.",0,21429,85116,4097,2374,0,29,20993,0},
