    {21494,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Echelon assaults enemies attempting to enter the Cathedral.  He calls swarms of Undying Stonefiends, which can only be destroyed when struck with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:319592|h[Stone Shattering Leap]|h|r while in |cFF2959D3|Hspell:319724|h[Stone Form]|h|r.",-1,21497,0,0,2387,21507,1,0,0},
    {21495,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:319592|h[Stone Shattering Leap]|h|r destroys Undying Stonefiends that are in Stone Form in the impact area.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:319603|h[Flesh to Stone]|h|r stuns all nearby players.",-1,0,0,2,2387,21496,3,21494,0},
    {21496,"Healer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:319592|h[Stone Shattering Leap]|h|r inflicts significant damage to Echelon's target and moderate damage to all players.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:319603|h[Flesh to Stone]|h|r stuns all nearby players.",-1,0,0,4,2387,0,4,21494,0},
    {21497,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:319592|h[Stone Shattering Leap]|h|r destroys Undying Stonefiends that are in Stone Form in the impact area.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:319603|h[Flesh to Stone]|h|r stuns all nearby players.",-1,0,0,1,2387,21495,2,21494,0},
    {21498,"Section 5",0,2,319592,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,22836,0,0,2387,21506,12,0,0},
