    {21604,"Carrion Worm",0,1,0,2,{"wago"},"Carrion Worms hunger for blood, searching out random players to feast upon.\n\n$[!8\n\n\n\nIn Mythic difficulty, Carrion Worms now erupt into a pool of Fetid Gas upon dying.$]",0,21605,15963,0,2395,0,10,21571,0},
