    {21646,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"At the start of the encounter, Ingra Maloch uses |cFF2959D3|Hspell:321006|h[Soul Shackle]|h|r to take control of Droman Oulfarran, and players must endure both of their attacks.\n\n\n\nWhen Oulfarran reaches $321006s2% health, they break free and strike back at Maloch with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:323059|h[Droman's Wrath]|h|r.",-1,21647,0,0,2400,21650,1,0,0},
    {21647,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Interrupt |cFF2959D3|Hspell:323057|h[Spirit Bolt]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Avoid being hit by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:323137|h[Bewildering Pollen]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2400,21648,2,21646,0},
    {21648,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Interrupt |cFF2959D3|Hspell:323057|h[Spirit Bolt]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Avoid being hit by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:323137|h[Bewildering Pollen]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2400,21649,3,21646,0},
    {21649,"Healer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid being hit by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:323137|h[Bewildering Pollen]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:323146|h[Death Shroud]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to all players.",-1,0,0,4,2400,0,4,21646,0},
    {21650,"Stage 1: Foul Magic",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"Maloch's drust magic controls Oulfarran, making them hostile to players.",-1,21787,0,0,2400,21651,5,0,0},
    {21651,"Stage 2: Wrath of the Forest",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"At $321006s2% health, Oulfarran breaks free of Maloch's control and assists players in battle.",-1,21655,0,0,2400,0,18,0,0},
