    {21658,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Gorechop periodically calls forth a wall of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322795|h[Meat Hooks]|h|r to sweep through the chamber, delivering Oozing Leftovers that assist their master.",-1,21659,0,0,2401,21679,1,0,0},
    {21659,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Watch out for |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322795|h[Meat Hooks]|h|r as they sweep across the arena.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:323515|h[Hateful Strike]|h|r inflicts heavy Phsyical damage.\n\n$bullet; Oozing Leftover leave pools of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:321447|h[Coagulating Ooze]|h|r when defeated.",-1,0,0,1,2401,21661,2,21658,0},
    {21660,"Healer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Watch out for |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322795|h[Meat Hooks]|h|r as they sweep across the arena.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:323515|h[Hateful Strike]|h|r inflicts heavy Phsyical damage to Gorechop's primary target.\n\n$bullet; Players struck by a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322795|h[Meat Hook]|h|r suffer periodic damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:323406|h[Jagged Gash]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,2401,0,4,21658,0},
    {21661,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Watch out for |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322795|h[Meat Hooks]|h|r as they sweep across the arena.\n\n$bullet; Oozing Leftover leave pools of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:321447|h[Coagulating Ooze]|h|r when defeated.",-1,0,0,2,2401,21660,3,21658,0},
