    {21686,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Mistcaller plays |cFF2959D3|Hspell:321471|h[Guessing Game]|h|r at 70%, 40% and 10% health. Killing the correct Illusionary Clone will end the guessing game and flush Mistcaller out of hiding.",-1,21689,0,0,2402,21690,1,0,0},
    {21687,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;During |cFF2959D3|Hspell:321873|h[Freeze Tag]|h|r, avoid the Illusionary Vulpin even if it is not chasing you.\n\n$bullet;Only the target of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:321828|h[Patty Cakes]|h|r can interrupt the cast.",-1,0,0,2,2402,21688,3,21686,0},
