    {21746,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Tred'ova feasts upon the Cocoon of Lakali at 70% and 40% health, triggering |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322450|h[Consumption]|h|r. After feasting Tred'ova becomes more intelligent, increasing the power of several of her abilities.",-1,21749,0,0,2405,22385,1,0,0},
    {21747,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Move away from allies you are tethered to when affected by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322648|h[Mind Link]|h|r to reduce party wide damage.\n\n$bullet;Gormling larva will fixate on players afflicted with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322563|h[Marked Prey]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Shatter |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322527|h[Gorging Shield]|h|r in order to interrupt |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322450|h[Consumption]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2405,21748,3,21746,0},
    {21748,"Healer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Move away from allies you are tethered to when affected by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322648|h[Mind Link]|h|r to reduce party wide damage.\n\n$bullet;Gormling larva will fixate on players afflicted with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322563|h[Marked Prey]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Shatter |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322527|h[Gorging Shield]|h|r in order to interrupt |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322450|h[Consumption]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,2405,0,4,21746,0},
