    {21754,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Halkias, the Sin-Stained Goliath leaves fields of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:323001|h[Glass Shards]|h|r in his destructive wake.  He is able to focus the lights of Revendreth into beams of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322913|h[Refracted Sinlight]|h|r.",-1,21755,0,0,2406,21762,1,0,0},
    {21755,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322936|h[Crumbling Slam]|h|r inflicts massive damage to all players near Halkias' target.\n\n$bullet; Dodge |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322913|h[Refracted Sinlight]|h|r and beware Halkias changing directions.",-1,0,0,1,2406,21757,2,21754,0},
    {21756,"Healer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322943|h[Heave Debris]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322936|h[Crumbling Slam]|h|r both inflict moderate group damage upon impact.\n\n$bullet; Dodge |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322913|h[Refracted Sinlight]|h|r and beware Halkias changing directions.",-1,0,0,4,2406,0,4,21754,0},
    {21757,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322943|h[Heave Debris]|h|r inflicts massive damage to players in the impact area.\n\n$bullet; Dodge |cFF2959D3|Hspell:322913|h[Refracted Sinlight]|h|r and beware Halkias changing directions.",-1,0,0,2,2406,21756,3,21754,0},
