    {21865,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Oryphrion spends anima to fuel their attacks. Standing in an |cFF2959D3|Hspell:324392|h[Anima Field]|h|r will empower Oryphrion and remove the anima cost of abilities.\n\n\n\nOnce Oryphrion hits 0 anima, they become |cFF2959D3|Hspell:323878|h[Drained]|h|r and will then |cFF2959D3|Hspell:324046|h[Recharge Anima]|h|r.",-1,21866,0,0,2414,21931,1,0,0},
    {21866,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:324392|h[Anima Fields]|h|r created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:324444|h[Empyreal Ordnance]|h|r empower Oryphrion.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:324608|h[Charged Stomp]|h|r inflicts heavy Arcane damage in an area and reduces player movement speed.",-1,0,0,1,2414,21868,2,21865,0},
    {21867,"Healer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:324608|h[Charged Stomp]|h|r inflicts heavy Arcane damage in an area and reduces player movement speed.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:323072|h[Purifying Blast]|h|r inflicts damage to nearby allies.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:324392|h[Anima Fields]|h|r created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:324444|h[Empyreal Ordnance]|h|r empower Oryphrion.",-1,0,0,4,2414,0,4,21865,0},
    {21868,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:323072|h[Purifying Blast]|h|r inflicts damage to nearby allies.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:324392|h[Anima Fields]|h|r created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:324444|h[Empyreal Ordnance]|h|r empower Oryphrion.",-1,0,0,2,2414,21867,3,21865,0},
    {21876,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Periodically Executor Tarvold summons forth one of the multitude of manifestiations he has imprisioned.  These manifestations consume the latent anima from the surroundings, growing larger over time.  When they are slain they erupt into a pool of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:323551|h[Residue]|h|r.",-1,21877,0,0,2415,22078,1,0,0},
    {21877,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Fleeting Manifestations leave behind large pools of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:323551|h[Residue]|h|r upon death.",-1,0,0,1,2415,21878,2,21876,0},
    {21878,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Quickly kill Fleeting Manifestations.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:322554|h[Castigate]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to players near the target.",-1,0,0,2,2415,21879,3,21876,0},
    {21879,"Healer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; While Fleeting Manifesations are alive they inflict party-wide damage with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:323548|h[Growing Pride]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:322554|h[Castigate]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to players near the target.",-1,0,0,4,2415,0,4,21876,0},
    {21880,"Section 5",0,2,322554,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2415,21891,6,0,0},
    {21883,"Fleeting Manifestation",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},"Fleeting Manifestations absorb latent anima, gaining energy over time.  Upon reaching 100 Energy the Fleeting Manifestation ertupts, creating pool of Residue.",-1,21888,94279,0,2415,0,8,21891,0},
    {21884,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Ventunax, the Dark Kyrian Praetor, is honed to such a razor's edge, and moves with such speed, that she leaves |cFF2959D3|Hspell:323927|h[Shadowhirls]|h|r in her wake. Avoid the Dark Bolts emitted from each |cFF2959D3|Hspell:323927|h[Shadowhirl]|h|r when Ventunax makes a move.\n\n\n\nWhen depleted of Anima energy, Ventunax takes a moment to recharge, while |cFF2959D3|Hspell:323927|h[Shadowhirls]|h|r continuously erupt.",-1,21885,0,0,2416,21892,1,0,0},
    {21885,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Regain Ventunax's focus when she strikes at an ally with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:324148|h[Dark Stride]|h|r",-1,0,0,1,2416,21887,2,21884,0},
    {21886,"Healer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Allies are likely to take high damage when there are many |cFF2959D3|Hspell:323927|h[Shadowhirls]|h|r within the arena",-1,0,0,4,2416,0,4,21884,0},
    {21887,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid |cFF2959D3|Hspell:324141|h[Dark Bolts]|h|r from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:323927|h[Shadowhirls]|h|r",-1,0,0,2,2416,21886,3,21884,0},
    {21888,nil,0,2,323551,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2415,21916,9,21883,0},
