    {21912,"Overview",0,3,0,1,{"wago"},"Xy'mox creates wormholes players can travel between and removes Sire Denathrius' Relics from their display cases, unleashing their powers on players. \n\n\n\nAt $340558s2% and $340558s3% remaining health, Xy'mox will return active Relics to their display case and bring out another.\n\n$[!16\n\nIn Mythic difficulty, Denathrius' Relics remain available for the remainder of the encounter once they are removed from their display.$]",-1,21913,0,0,2418,22122,1,0,0},
    {21913,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Utilize wormholes created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:328437|h[Dimensional Tear]|h|r to quickly reposition.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:325361|h[Glyph of Destruction]|h|r inflicts substantial Arcane damage to nearby players.",-1,0,0,1,2418,21914,2,21912,0},
    {21914,"Healer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Coordinate with allies to place wormholes created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:328437|h[Dimensional Tear]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Utilize wormholes created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:328437|h[Dimensional Tear]|h|r to quickly reposition.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:325399|h[Hyperlight Spark]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:325361|h[Glyph of Destruction]|h|r inflict damage to all players.",-1,0,0,4,2418,21915,3,21912,0},
    {21915,"Damage",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Coordinate with allies to place wormholes created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:328437|h[Dimensional Tear]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Utilize wormholes created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:328437|h[Dimensional Tear]|h|r to quickly reposition.\n\n$bullet; Seeds of Extinction created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:329770|h[Root of Extinction]|h|r can be picked up and moved.",-1,0,0,2,2418,0,4,21912,0},
    {21916,"Section 9",0,2,323548,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2415,0,10,21883,0},
    {21918,"Section 2",0,2,324459,0,{"wago"},"$[!23\n\n\n\nIn Mythic difficulty, Globgrog also beckons a Slimy Smorgasbord.$]",-1,0,0,0,2419,21924,6,0,0},
    {21920,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"At full energy, Globgrog will |cFF2959D3|Hspell:324459|h[Beckon Slime]|h|r, summoning nearby Slimy Morsels that slowly move towards him. When a Slimy Morsel reaches Globgrog, he will |cFF2959D3|Hspell:319780|h[Consume Slime]|h|r, restoring his health.",-1,21923,0,0,2419,22353,1,0,0},
    {21921,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Globgrog will |cFF2959D3|Hspell:319780|h[Consume Slime]|h|r if a Slimy Morsel reaches him.\n\n\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:324667|h[Slime Wave]|h|r inflicts high damage to players in a frontal cone.",-1,0,0,2,2419,21922,3,21920,0},
    {21922,"Healer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:324527|h[Plaguestomp]|h|r inflicts party-wide damage.\n\n\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:324667|h[Slime Wave]|h|r inflicts high damage to players in a frontal cone.",-1,0,0,4,2419,0,4,21920,0},
    {21923,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Globgrog will |cFF2959D3|Hspell:319780|h[Consume Slime]|h|r if a Slimy Morsel reaches him.\n\n\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:324667|h[Slime Wave]|h|r inflicts high damage to players in a frontal cone.",-1,0,0,1,2419,21921,2,21920,0},
