    {21973,"Primal Anima Containers",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"Anima containers are placed around Lady Inerva Darkvein's balcony that gradually gather anima energy to empower each of her abilities. \n\n\n\nPlayers can interact with the containers to open them, and close them by interacting with them again.\n\n\n\nOpen containers vent their |cFF2959D3|Hspell:325184|h[Loose Anima]|h|r into the playspace.\n\n\n\nWhen any container reaches full capacity, a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:325225|h[Container Breach]|h|r occurs.  The breach continues to damage players until the anima level is reduced below capacity.",-1,22942,0,32,2420,22564,5,0,0},
    {21974,"Section 2",0,2,325225,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,16,2420,22423,8,21973,0},
    {21975,"Section 3",0,2,325184,0,{"wago"},"$[!14,15,16,17,18\n\n\n\nThe damage of Loose Anima increases with each open Primal Anima Container.$]",-1,0,0,4,2420,21974,7,21973,0},
    {21976,"Section 4",0,2,341623,0,{"wago"},"$[!14,15,16,17\n\n\n\nLady Inerva Darkvein uses this ability when the Container of Desire surpasses 33% capacity.$]$[!16\n\n\n\nOn Mythic Raid difficulty, the target is attacked by two images of their |cFF2959D3|Hspell:335322|h[Hidden Desires]|h|r.$]",-1,22572,0,0,2420,22576,15,22571,0},
    {21977,nil,0,2,325382,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2420,22591,20,22576,0},
