    {22059,"Stage Two: The Crimson Chorus",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"Once fully cleansed, players find themselves in the grand Observatorium, where countless mirrors are used to watch and manipulate events throughout the Shadowlands and beyond.\n\n\n\nPlayers can enter these mirrors to travel great distances, but there is no escape from Denathrius.",-1,22406,0,0,2424,22195,26,0,0},
