    {22170,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet; Intercept beams of energy from Millhouse's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:320786|h[Power Overwhelming]|h|r to deny Millhouse and gain temporary power, at a cost.\n\n$bullet; Dismantle Millificent's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:320811|h[Experimental Squirrel Bomb]|h|r to reduce party damage taken.",3,0,0,2,2409,21795,3,21794,0},
    {22171,"Healer",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet; Intercept beams of energy from Millhouse's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:320786|h[Power Overwhelming]|h|r to deny Millhouse and gain temporary power, at a cost.\n\n$bullet; Millificent's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:320145|h[Buzz-Saw]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:320168|h[Thrown Buzz-Saw]|h|r's damage-over-time effect, |cFF2959D3|Hspell:320147|h[Bleeding]|h|r, can be intense when multiple stacks are present.",3,0,0,4,2409,21797,5,21794,0},
    {22172,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Over the course of the encounter the Hungering Destroyer gains energy.  Upon reaching 100 energy, the Hungering Destroyer casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:334522|h[Consumes]|h|r attempting to devour all nearby life energy.",-1,22403,0,0,2428,22176,1,0,0},
    {22173,"Tanks",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet; Coordinate with your co-tank to manage |cFF2959D3|Hspell:332295|h[Growing Hunger]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Move away from the Hungering Destroyer when it casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:334522|h[Consume]|h|r.",0,0,0,1,2428,22174,5,22172,0},
    {22174,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:329298|h[Gluttonous Miasma]|h|r prevents all healing received by afflicted targets but siphons health from afflicted targets' nearby allies.\n\n$bullet; Position yourself to avold hitting other players when targeted by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:338614|h[Volatile Ejection]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Move away from the Hungering Destroyer when it casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:334522|h[Consume]|h|r.",0,0,0,4,2428,22175,6,22172,0},
    {22175,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:329298|h[Gluttonous Miasma]|h|r prevents all healing received by afflicted targets but siphons health from afflicted targets' nearby allies.\n\n$bullet; Position yourself to avold hitting other players when targeted by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:338614|h[Volatile Ejection]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Move away from the Hungering Destroyer when it casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:334522|h[Consume]|h|r.",0,0,0,2,2428,0,7,22172,0},
