    {22439,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Valinor activates once all of the nearby barrels of anima have been destroyed, under the orders of Lysonia, who floats nearby. His powerful Anima Charges deal damage in an area and should be avoided, and he can decimate groups of foes with Charged Anima Blast if they do not spread out. Periodically, Valinor will cast Unleashed Anima, blasting many areas with Anima Charges for its duration.",-1,22440,0,0,2430,22443,1,0,0},
