    {23015,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Timecap'n Hooktail commands her infamous pirate ship, The Hourglass, to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:347370|h[Cannon Barrage]|h|r the beach while she engages players in close combat.\n\n\n\nCorsair Brutes grapple from the deck to support their captain, but her |cFF2959D3|Hspell:347149|h[Infinite Breath]|h|r is deadly for players and Corsairs alike.",-1,23016,0,0,2449,23019,1,0,0},
    {23016,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Hooktail's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:347149|h[Infinite Breath]|h|r can damage and stun players, but it also kills Corsair Brutes instantly.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:347370|h[Cannon Barrage]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to players in the impact area.",-1,0,0,2,2449,23017,2,23015,0},
    {23017,"Healer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:352345|h[Anchor Shot]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to a random player.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:347370|h[Cannon Barrage]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to players in the impact area.",-1,0,0,4,2449,23018,3,23015,0},
    {23018,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Hooktail's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:347149|h[Infinite Breath]|h|r can damage and stun players, but it also kills Corsair Brutes instantly.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:347370|h[Cannon Barrage]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to players in the impact area.",-1,0,0,1,2449,0,4,23015,0},
