    {23038,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"So'azmi deploys |cFF2959D3|Hspell:347426|h[Relocators]|h|r which players must use to avoid his |cFF2959D3|Hspell:347481|h[Shuri]|h|r ability.\n\n\n\nAt $1245634s1% and $1245634s2% health, So'azmi |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245634|h[Divides]|h|r the playspace to impede players' movement.\n\n\n\nAt 100 energy, So'azmi prepares his deadly |cFF2959D3|Hspell:357188|h[Double Technique]|h|r, which must be interrupted multiple times.",-1,23040,0,0,2451,23031,1,0,0},
    {23039,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Use |cFF2959D3|Hspell:347426|h[Relocators]|h|r to avoid the damage of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:347481|h[Shuri]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:357188|h[Double Technique]|h|r must be interrupted multiple times to prevent its damage.",-1,0,0,1,2451,0,4,23038,0},
