    {23963,"Stage One: War and Duty",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"If the Prototype of War or the Prototype of Duty reaches 40% health remaining, both retreat to the Progenitor Forge. The Prototype of Absolution and the Prototype of Renewal then begin their assault upon players.",-1,24530,0,0,2460,24119,5,0,0},
