    {24920,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Telash attacks players with powerful frost magic that leaves behind |cFF2959D3|Hspell:387150 |h[Frozen Ground]|h|r. Upon reaching 100 energy, Telash charges up for  |cFF2959D3|Hspell:388008 |h[Absolute Zero]|h|r.",-1,24921,0,0,2483,25634,1,0,0},
    {24921,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:388008 |h[Absolute Zero]|h|r does heavy damage to all players, which can be reduced by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:388072 |h[Vault Rune]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:386781 |h[Frost Bomb]|h|r inflicts damage around players and creates |cFF2959D3|Hspell:387150 |h[Frozen Ground]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2483,24922,2,24920,0},
    {24922,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:388008 |h[Absolute Zero]|h|r does heavy damage to all players, which can be reduced by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:388072 |h[Vault Rune]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:386781 |h[Frost Bomb]|h|r inflicts damage around players and creates |cFF2959D3|Hspell:387150 |h[Frozen Ground]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:387151 |h[Icy Devastator]|h|r will focus on one player inflicting moderate damage.",-1,0,0,4,2483,24923,3,24920,0},
    {24923,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:388008 |h[Absolute Zero]|h|r does heavy damage to all players, which can be reduced by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:388072 |h[Vault Rune]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:386781 |h[Frost Bomb]|h|r inflicts damage around players and creates |cFF2959D3|Hspell:387150 |h[Frozen Ground]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2483,0,4,24920,0},
    {24925,"Ability",0,2,386781,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,25596,0,0,2483,25597,8,0,0},
    {24926,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Sentinel Talondras begins the fight with two applications of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:372600|h[Inexorable]|h|r, each which absorbs the next stun effect cast on Talondras. \n\n\n\nWhen the fight begins, Talondras manifests |cFF2959D3|Hspell:372623|h[Resonating Orb]|h|r to stun players and begins to charge the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:372716|h[Ancient Dynamo]|h|r. \n\n\n\nIf the dynamo reaches 100 energy before being stunned, it provides |cFF2959D3|Hspell:372719|h[Titanic Empowerment]|h|r to Sentinel Talondras.",-1,24927,0,0,2484,24935,1,0,0},
    {24927,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:372623|h[Resonating Orb]|h|r will stun any player or monster it comes into contact with.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:372600|h[Inexorable]|h|r can be removed by Stun effects, causing the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:372716|h[Ancient Dynamo]|h|r to become vulnerable.",-1,0,0,1,2484,24928,2,24926,0},
    {24928,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:372623|h[Resonating Orb]|h|r will stun any unit it comes into contact with.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:372600|h[Inexorable]|h|r can be removed by Stun effects, causing the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:372716|h[Ancient Dynamo]|h|r to become vulnerable.",-1,0,0,2,2484,24929,3,24926,0},
    {24929,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:372701|h[Crushing Stomp]|h|r inflicts high damage to all players.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:372718|h[Earthen Shards]|h|r causes one player to bleed for high damage over its duration.",-1,0,0,4,2484,0,4,24926,0},
    {24930,nil,0,2,372600,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2484,24934,6,24935,0},
