    {25483,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Umbrelskul continually unleashes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:385078 |h[Arcane Eruptions]|h|r that create |cFF2959D3|Hspell:385267 |h[Crackling Vortexes]|h|r that wander the area.\n\n\n\nAt 75%, 50%, and 25% remaining health Umbreskul creates Detonating Crystals that begin to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:385331 |h[Fracture]|h|r.",-1,25484,0,0,2508,26064,1,0,0},
    {25484,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:384978 |h[Dragon Strike]|h|r inflicts heavy damage.",-1,0,0,1,2508,25714,2,25483,0},
