    {25504,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Professor Maxdormu conjures a lesson that recalls the story of Vexamus, introducing the elemental's arsenal of Arcane abilities as the narrative progresses. The professor's magic book summons |cFF2959D3|Hspell:387691|h[Arcane Orbs]|h|r that gravitate towards Vexamus and grant it more power if not intercepted.",-1,25505,0,0,2509,25622,1,0,0},
    {25505,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:385958|h[Arcane Expulsion]|h|r inflicts heavy damage in a frontal cone.\n\n$bullet;Vexamus gains energy from absorbing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:387691|h[Arcane Orbs]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2509,25506,2,25504,0},
    {25506,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:386173|h[Mana Bombs]|h|r leave behind a pool of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:386201|h[Corrupted Mana]|h|r after detonating.\n\n$bullet;Vexamus gains energy from absorbing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:387691|h[Arcane Orbs]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2509,25507,3,25504,0},
    {25507,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:386173|h[Mana Bombs]|h|r leave behind a pool of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:386201|h[Corrupted Mana]|h|r after detonating.\n\n$bullet;Vexamus gains energy from absorbing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:387691|h[Arcane Orbs]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,2509,0,4,25504,0},
