    {25884,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Liskanoth harnesses her power to confine players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:389287|h[Glacial Storm]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:388767|h[Binding Ice]|h|r. Upon reaching 100 energy, Liskanoth ascends to the skies and sweeps the valley, unleashing a powerful |cFF2959D3|Hspell:389762|h[Deep Freeze]|h|r on players below.",-1,25885,0,0,2518,25888,1,0,0},
    {25885,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:388767|h[Binding Ice]|h|r roots targets in place until they are defeated.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:389287|h[Glacial Storm]|h|r leaves behind frozen patches of ground that reduce players' movement speed.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:389762|h[Deep Freeze]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to all in Liskanoth's path and leaves them frozen.",-1,0,0,2,2518,25886,2,25884,0},
    {25886,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:389287|h[Glacial Storm]|h|r leaves behind frozen patches of ground that reduce players' movement speed.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:389762|h[Deep Freeze]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to all in Liskanoth's path and leaves them frozen.",-1,0,0,4,2518,25887,3,25884,0},
    {25887,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:388925|h[Chilling Breath]|h|r inflicts heavy damage and applies |cFF2959D3|Hspell:388924|h[Biting Frost]|h|r to all hit\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:389287|h[Glacial Storm]|h|r leaves behind frozen patches of ground that reduce players' movement speed.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:389762|h[Deep Freeze]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to all in Liskanoth's path and leaves them frozen.",-1,0,0,1,2518,0,4,25884,0},
