    {25942,"Tanks",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet; Maruuk often casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:382836|h[Brutalize]|h|r on his current target.\n\n\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:385339|h[Earthsplitter]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to any player in the area on impact.\n\n\n\n$bullet; Maruuk's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:386063|h[Frightful Roar]|h|r will cause nearby players to flee.",3,0,0,1,2478,24771,2,24770,0},
