    {26221,"Zaqali Wallclimber",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Wallclimbers periodically ascend the rampart walls and attempt to breach the sealed door. Their melee attacks cause |cFF2959D3|Hspell:404687|h[Barrier Backfire]|h|r.",-1,0,110916,0,2524,27094,30,26604,0},
