    {26291,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The Timeways coalesce in response to Nozdormu's intervention. Fields of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:403910|h[Decaying Time]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:403912|h[Accelerating Time]|h|r continually tick around the Manifested Timestream, manipulating how their abilities execute.",-1,26292,0,0,2528,26295,1,0,0},
    {26292,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:403910|h[Decaying Time]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:403912|h[Accelerating Time]|h|r impactfully manipulate |cFF2959D3|Hspell:405431|h[Fragments of Time]|h|r's travel speed.\n\n$bullet;Manifested Timeways casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:414307|h[Radiant]|h|r when there are no valid targets in melee range.",-1,0,0,1,2528,26294,2,26291,0},
    {26293,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:404141|h[Chrono-faded]|h|r's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:405448|h[Chronofade]|h|r is dangerous when afflicted with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:403910|h[Decaying Time]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:403910|h[Decaying Time]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:403912|h[Accelerating Time]|h|r impactfully manipulate |cFF2959D3|Hspell:405431|h[Fragments of Time]|h|r's travel speed.",-1,0,0,2,2528,0,4,26291,0},
    {26294,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:404141|h[Chrono-faded]|h|r's released |cFF2959D3|Hspell:405448|h[Chronofade]|h|r travels notably faster when dispelled inside |cFF2959D3|Hspell:403912|h[Accelerating Time]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:403910|h[Decaying Time]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:403912|h[Accelerating Time]|h|r impactfully manipulate |cFF2959D3|Hspell:405431|h[Fragments of Time]|h|r's travel speed.",-1,0,0,4,2528,26293,3,26291,0},
    {26295,"Timeways Conflux",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"Shifting fields of time energy surrounds the Manifested Timeways, applying Accelerating Time or Decaying Time.",-1,26296,0,32,2528,26298,5,0,0},
    {26296,"Section 6",0,2,403910,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2528,26297,6,26295,0},
