    {26415,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Chronikar stomps, forming |cFF2959D3|Hspell:401794|h[Withering Sandpools]|h|r that deny ground. Additionally, she uses her time-bending axe to strike with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:413013|h[Chronoshear]|h|r. At 100 energy, she leaps at players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:413105|h[Eon Shatter]|h|r, unleashing fragments of timespace.",-1,27220,0,2,2521,26406,1,0,0},
