    {27247,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Anduin Lothar commands the Forces of the Alliance in an infinite battle against the Forces of the Horde. With Lion's Fang, the Highblade of Stormwind in hand, Lothar cleaves his foes, rallies his troops, and exercises skill at slaying enemies.",-1,27248,0,0,2534,27251,1,0,0},
    {27248,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:418047|h[FOR THE ALLIANCE!]|h|r brings additional enemy combatants against players.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:410234|h[Bladestorm]|h|r pursues a marked player, inflicting damage in a nearby radius.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:418056|h[Shockwave]|h|r casts three times in rapid succession.",-1,0,0,2,2534,27249,2,27247,0},
    {27249,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:418047|h[FOR THE ALLIANCE!]|h|r brings additional enemy combatants against players.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:410234|h[Bladestorm]|h|r pursues a marked player, inflicting damage in a nearby radius.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:418056|h[Shockwave]|h|r casts three times in rapid succession.",-1,0,0,4,2534,27250,3,27247,0},
    {27250,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:418059|h[Mortal Strikes]|h|r strikes twice, applying |cFF2959D3|Hspell:410497|h[Mortal Wounds]|h|r on each swing.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:418047|h[FOR THE ALLIANCE!]|h|r brings additional enemy combatants against players.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:418056|h[Shockwave]|h|r casts three times in rapid succession.",-1,0,0,1,2534,0,4,27247,0},
    {27251,"The Infinite Battlefield",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"This Time-Lost Battlefield rages on. Forces of the Horde and Alliance do battle, endlessly entering the arena.",-1,27252,0,0,2534,27260,5,0,0},
    {27252,"Forces of the Alliance",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,27253,0,0,2534,0,6,27251,0},
