    {27321,"Fiery Treant",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Fiery Treants seek to spread flame throughout the temple and leave behind Burning Ground.\n\n\n\nWhen killed, they transform into a Charred Treant.",-1,27330,113611,0,2553,27322,13,27313,0},
    {27322,"Charred Treant",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Charred Treants are inert and can be healed.\n\n\n\nWhen they reach full health, they transform into a Renewed Treant.",-1,0,113612,4,2553,27323,17,27313,0},
    {27323,"Renewed Treant",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Friendly Renewed Treants channel Nature's Gift, sacrificing their own life to empower the Seed of Life.",-1,27332,113613,0,2553,0,18,27313,0},
    {27324,"Scorching Roots",0,1,0,2,{"wago"},"Scorching Roots fixate on random players, pursuing them relentlessly and speed over time.\n\n\n\nWhen killed, they transform into Charred Brambles.$[!15\n\n\n\nOn Heroic and Mythic difficulties, Scorched Roots remain untargetable until doused with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:425249|h[Dream Blossom]|h|r.$]$[!16\n\n\n\nOn Heroic and Mythic difficulties, Scorched Roots remain untargetable until doused with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:425249|h[Dream Blossom]|h|r.$]",0,28086,115925,8,2553,27326,23,27312,0},
    {27326,"Charred Brambles",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Charred Brambles are inert and can be healed.\n\n\n\nWhen they reach full health, they transform into a Renewed Bramble Barrier.",-1,0,113920,4,2553,27327,25,27312,0},
    {27327,"Renewed Bramble Barrier",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},"Renewed Bramble Barriers provide protection against Raging Inferno.\n\n\n\nWhen destroyed, they erupt in Explosive Bark.",-1,27408,113921,0,2553,0,26,27312,0},
