    {27537,"Burning Treant Form",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},"Tindral shapeshifts into a flaming Treant, periodically afflicting players with Suppressive Ember.",-1,27810,114072,0,2565,28059,69,27506,0},
    {27540,"Section 16",0,2,420659,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,27401,0,0,2560,27403,5,0,0},
    {27541,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Kyrioss summons |cFF2959D3|Hspell:474071|h[Wild Lightning]|h|r to strike at players. \n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, Kyrioss flies to the center of the chamber to unleash a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:444250|h[Lightning Torrent]|h|r before surging back into battle.",-1,27542,0,0,2566,27547,1,0,0},
    {27542,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; When it reaches 100 energy, Kyrioss flies to the center of the chamber and unleashes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:444250|h[Lightning Torrent]|h|r.\n\n$[23$bullet; Kyrioss strikes players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214320|h[Grounding Bolt]|h|r during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:444250|h[Lightning Torrent]|h|r.$]",-1,0,0,1,2566,27543,2,27541,0},
    {27543,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; When it reaches 100 energy, Kyrioss flies to the center of the chamber and unleashes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:444250|h[Lightning Torrent]|h|r.\n\n$[23$bullet; Kyrioss strikes players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214320|h[Grounding Bolt]|h|r during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:444250|h[Lightning Torrent]|h|r.$]",-1,0,0,2,2566,27544,3,27541,0},
    {27544,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; When it reaches 100 energy, Kyrioss flies to the center of the chamber and unleashes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:444250|h[Lightning Torrent]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Players stunned by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:420739|h[Lightning Torrent]|h|r can be dispelled.\n\n$[23$bullet; Kyrioss strikes players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214320|h[Grounding Bolt]|h|r during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:444250|h[Lightning Torrent]|h|r.$]",-1,0,0,4,2566,0,4,27541,0},
    {27545,"Section 5",0,2,444250,2,{"wago"},nil,3,0,0,160,2566,31169,6,0,0},
    {27547,"Section 7",0,2,420739,2,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,4128,2566,27545,5,0,0},
    {27548,"Section 8",0,2,419871,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2566,27783,11,0,0},
    {27552,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Stormguard Gorren, empowered by the Void, attempts to periodically twist a player's soul with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:424737|h[Chaotic Corruption]|h|r latching on to nearby players.\n\n\n\nGorren will use |cFF2959D3|Hspell:425048|h[Dark Gravity]|h|r to pull in all his foes and crush them with his hammer's might.",-1,27554,0,0,2567,27862,1,0,0},
    {27553,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Upon expiration, |cFF2959D3|Hspell:424739|h[Chaotic Corruption]|h|r erupts and leaps to the closest player.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:425052|h[Dark Gravity]|h|r pulls players towards Stormguard Gorren before erupting.",-1,0,0,1,2567,0,4,27552,0},
    {27554,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Upon expiration, |cFF2959D3|Hspell:424739|h[Chaotic Corruption]|h|r erupts and leaps to the closest player.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:425052|h[Dark Gravity]|h|r pulls players towards Stormguard Gorren before erupting.",-1,0,0,2,2567,27555,2,27552,0},
    {27555,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Upon expiration, |cFF2959D3|Hspell:424739|h[Chaotic Corruption]|h|r erupts and leaps to the closest player.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:424739|h[Chaotic Corruption]|h|r inflicts moderate periodic damage to its current target.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:425052|h[Dark Gravity]|h|r inflicts moderate damage to all players for its duration.",-1,0,0,4,2567,27553,3,27552,0},
    {27557,"Section 6",0,2,425048,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,16,2567,27861,10,0,0},
    {27558,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The Voidstone Monstrosity assaults players with corrupted attacks while shielding itself in a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:445262|h[Void Shell]|h|r from Stomrider Vokmar's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:424371|h[Storm's Vengeance]|h|r.",-1,27560,0,0,2568,30041,1,0,0},
    {27559,"Tanks",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:445457|h[Oblivion Wave]|h|r inflicts Shadow damage to players in its path.\n\n$bullet; The Monstrosity irradiates all players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:423393|h[Entropy]|h|r while no players are in melee range.",3,0,0,1,2568,31370,4,27558,0},
    {27560,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet; Stormrider Vokmar's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:458082|h[Stormrider's Charge]|h|r destroys nearby Voidstone Fragments.\n\n$bullet; Shattering |cFF2959D3|Hspell:445262|h[Void Shell]|h|r allows Stormrider Vokmar's to strike with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:424371|h[Storm's Vengeance]|h|r",3,0,0,2,2568,27561,2,27558,0},
    {27561,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet; Stormrider Vokmar's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:458082|h[Stormrider's Charge]|h|r destroys nearby Voidstone Fragments.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:429487|h[Unleash Corruption]|h|r inflicts moderate Shadow damage to players.\n\n$bullet; Voidstone Awakened inflict increasing damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:429029|h[Corruption Overload]|h|r.",3,0,0,0,2568,27559,3,27558,0},
