    {27927,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Prioress Murrpray harnesses the power of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:425544|h[The Sacred Flame]|h|r to vanquish her foes, burning them with its purifying beam of light.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 50% health, Murrpray retreats to the Sacred Flame and shrouds herself with a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:423588|h[Barrier of Light]|h|r while calling upon her devoted followers.",-1,27930,0,0,2573,27934,1,0,0},
    {27928,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;  Prioress Murrpray inflicts increasing Holy damage while |cFF2959D3|Hspell:423588|h[Barrier of Light]|h|r holds.\n\n$bullet;  Arathor Devoted inflict Holy damage to nearby players while affected by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:425022|h[Overwhelming Power]|h|r.",3,0,0,2,2573,27929,3,27927,0},
