    {28096,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Skarmorak draws power from Crystal Shards, bolstering |cFF2959D3|Hspell:423200|h[Fortified Shell]|h|r.\n\n\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:423557|h[Unstable Fragments]|h|r increases healing, and damage dealt to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:423228|h[Fortified Shell]|h|r, but also inflicts Shadow Damage.",-1,0,0,2,2579,28097,2,28087,0},
    {28097,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:423557|h[Unstable Fragments]|h|r increases healing, and damage dealt to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:423228|h[Fortified Shell]|h|r, but also inflicts Shadow Damage.\n\n\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:423324|h[Void Discharge]|h|r inflicts Shadow damage until Fortified Shell is broken.",-1,0,0,4,2579,28098,3,28087,0},
    {28098,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Skarmorak inflicts heavy Physical damage to its current target with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:422233|h[Crystalline Smash]|h|r.\n\n\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:423557|h[Unstable Fragments]|h|r increases healing, and damage dealt to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:423228|h[Fortified Shell]|h|r, but also inflicts Shadow Damage.",-1,0,0,1,2579,0,4,28087,0},
