    {28178,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Anub'ikkaj patrols the streets of Mereldar, strengthened through |cFF2959D3|Hspell:427192|h[Empowered Might]|h|r from his nerubian lieutenants. Each of his allies grants formidable power while alive.",-1,28179,0,0,2581,28183,1,0,0},
    {28179,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:426860|h[Dark Orb]|h|r's final explosion inflicts less damage the farther it travels.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:426787|h[Shadowy Decay]|h|r inflicts substantial damage to all players.",-1,0,0,4,2581,28180,2,28178,0},
    {28180,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:426860|h[Dark Orb]|h|r's final explosion inflicts less damage the farther it travels.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:427001|h[Terrifying Slam]|h|r inflicts substantial damage and knocks back, fearing other players caught near the primary target.",-1,0,0,1,2581,28181,3,28178,0},
    {28181,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:426860|h[Dark Orb]|h|r's final explosion inflicts less damage the farther it travels.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:427001|h[Terrifying Slam]|h|r inflicts substantial damage and fears other players caught near the primary target.",-1,0,0,2,2581,0,4,28178,0},
    {28182,"Anub'ikkaj",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,28187,114315,0,2581,0,7,0,0},
    {28183,"Empowered Nerubians",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"Anub'ikkaj gains increased power from his nerubian lieutenants: Ascendant Vis'coxria, Deathscreamer Iken'tak, and Ixkreten the Unbreakable. Defeating them removes this power.",-1,28191,0,32,2581,28182,5,0,0},
