    {28202,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Void Speaker Eirich begins the encounter by tearing open 2 |cFF2959D3|Hspell:427315|h[Void Rift]|h|r. Periodically, the Void Speaker will afflict players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:427329|h[Void Corruption]|h|r which can only be removed by moving close to an active |cFF2959D3|Hspell:427315|h[Void Rift]|h|r.",-1,28203,0,0,2582,28206,1,0,0},
    {28203,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; The damage of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:427329|h[Void Corruption's]|h|r increases over time until it is removed.\n\n$bullet; Touching the center of a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:427315|h[Void Rift]|h|r inflicts lethal damage.",-1,0,0,1,2582,28204,2,28202,0},
    {28204,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; The damage of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:427329|h[Void Corruption's]|h|r increases over time until it is removed.\n\n$bullet; Touching the center of a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:427315|h[Void Rift]|h|r inflicts lethal damage.",-1,0,0,2,2582,28205,3,28202,0},
    {28205,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; The damage of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:427329|h[Void Corruption's]|h|r increases over time until it is removed.\n\n$bullet; Touching the center of a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:427315|h[Void Rift]|h|r inflicts lethal damage.",-1,0,0,4,2582,0,4,28202,0},
