    {28393,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Avanoxx consumes with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:438471|h[Voracious Bites]|h|r and signals to Starved Crawlers with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:438476|h[Alerting Shrill]|h|r that grow in |cFF2959D3|Hspell:438490|h[Hunger]|h|r over time. \n\n\n\nAvanoxx unleashes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:438473|h[Gossamer Onslaught]|h|r and causes additional undercrawler eggs to fall from above. |cFF2959D3|Hspell:434830|h[Vile Webbing]|h|r serves as the perfect trap for her prey.\n\n$[!8,23 \n\nIn Mythic difficulty, Avanoxx becomes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:446788|h[Insatiable]|h|r.$]",-1,28394,0,0,2583,29111,1,0,0},
    {28394,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:438471|h[Voracious Bite]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to its target and increases damage taken for a period of time.\n\n$bullet; Standing in |cFF2959D3|Hspell:434830|h[Vile Webbing]|h|r causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:436614|h[Web Wrap]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:438490|h[Hunger]|h|r causes Starved Crawlers to fixate on other players.",-1,0,0,1,2583,28395,2,28393,0},
    {28395,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Standing in |cFF2959D3|Hspell:434830|h[Vile Webbing]|h|r causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:436614|h[Web Wrap]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Starved Crawlers grow in |cFF2959D3|Hspell:438490|h[Hunger]|h|r over time.",-1,0,0,2,2583,28396,3,28393,0},
    {28396,"Healer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Standing in |cFF2959D3|Hspell:434830|h[Vile Webbing]|h|r causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:436614|h[Web Wrap]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:438476|h[Alerting Shrill]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:438473|h[Gossamer Onslaught]|h|r inflict substantial party-wide damage.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:438471|h[Voracious Bite]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to its target and increases damage taken for a period of time.",-1,0,0,4,2583,0,4,28393,0},
    {28397,nil,0,2,438471,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,1,2583,0,12,0,0},
    {28400,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Anub'zekt fights fiercely alongside his brood, attacking with brutal |cFF2959D3|Hspell:433425|h[Impale]|h|r attacks while |cFF2959D3|Hspell:433747|h[Ceaseless Swarms]|h|r roam the battlefield. Upon reaching 100 energy, he calls upon his entire brood, dragging enemies into the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:433766|h[Eye of the Swarm]|h|r.",-1,28401,0,0,2584,28864,1,0,0},
    {28401,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Anub'zekt fires |cFF2959D3|Hspell:433425|h[Impale]|h|r in front of himself, inflicting high damage and knocking back players hit.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:433766|h[Eye of the Swarm]|h|r surrounds the arena and limits mobility.",-1,0,0,1,2584,28402,2,28400,0},
    {28402,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:433747|h[Ceaseless Swarms]|h|r burst forth from players infected by|cFF2959D3|Hspell:433740|h[Infestation]|h|r .\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:433677|h[Burrow Charge]|h|r inflicts high damage to players in a line in front of Anub'zekt.",-1,0,0,2,2584,28403,3,28400,0},
    {28403,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:433747|h[Ceaseless Swarms]|h|r burst forth from players infected by|cFF2959D3|Hspell:433740|h[Infestation]|h|r .\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:433766|h[Eye of the Swarm]|h|r surrounds the arena and limits mobility.",-1,0,0,4,2584,0,4,28400,0},
    {28404,"Stage One: <PH>",0,2,433425,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,1,2584,0,11,0,0},
    {28405,"Section 7",0,2,433677,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2584,28404,10,0,0},
    {28406,"Stage Two: <PH>",0,2,433740,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,28863,0,4,2584,28405,8,0,0},
    {28407,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"A stream of Bloodworkers ferry |cFF2959D3|Hspell:431985|h[Black Blood]|h|r for Ki'katal the Harvester. When struck, they drop their slime cargo and flee.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, Ki'katal the Harvester manifests a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:432117|h[Cosmic Singularity]|h|r, pulling all players in towards the detonation.",-1,28408,0,0,2585,28411,1,0,0},
    {28408,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Stepping within Black Blood causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:432031|h[Grasping Blood]|h|r to root players in place and prevent them from moving.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:432117|h[Cosmic Singularity]|h|r pulls all players in and inflicts high damage.",-1,0,0,1,2585,28409,2,28407,0},
    {28409,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Stepping within Black Blood causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:432031|h[Grasping Blood]|h|r to root players in place and prevent them from moving.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:432117|h[Cosmic Singularity]|h|r pulls all players in and inflicts high damage.",-1,0,0,2,2585,28410,3,28407,0},
    {28410,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Stepping within Black Blood causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:432031|h[Grasping Blood]|h|r to root players in place and prevent them from moving.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:432117|h[Cosmic Singularity]|h|r pulls all players in and inflicts high damage.",-1,0,0,4,2585,0,4,28407,0},
    {28411,"Bloodworkers",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},"Bloodworkers carry Black Blood. Any damage taken causes the drone to drop it and flee.",-1,28573,116347,0,2585,28574,5,0,0},
    {28414,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Brew Master Aldryr harnesses the explosive power of Cinderbrew, assaulting players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:432198|h[Blazing Belch]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:432182|h[Throw Cinderbrew]|h|r.\n\n\n\nAt 66% and 33% health, Brew Master Aldryr begins |cFF2959D3|Hspell:442525|h[Happy Hour]|h|r and causes Thirsty Patrons to unleash a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:431896|h[Rowdy Yell]|h|r.",-1,28415,0,0,2586,28964,1,0,0},
    {28415,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Thirsty Patrons inflict Physical damage to all players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:431896|h[Rowdy Yell]|h|r until appeased.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:432229|h[Keg Smash]|h|r inflicts high Physical damage and forms pools of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:432196|h[Hot Honey]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2586,28416,2,28414,0},
    {28416,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Thirsty Patrons inflict Physical damage to all players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:431896|h[Rowdy Yell]|h|r until appeased.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:432198|h[Blazing Belch]|h|r inflicts high Fire damage towards a player in a frontal cone.",-1,0,0,2,2586,28417,3,28414,0},
    {28417,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Thirsty Patrons inflict Physical damage to all players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:431896|h[Rowdy Yell]|h|r until appeased.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:432182|h[Throw Cinderbrew]|h|r inflicts significant Fire damage to targeted players.",-1,0,0,4,2586,0,4,28414,0},
    {28420,"Thirsty Patron",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,28578,119017,0,2586,28965,6,28964,0},
    {28421,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$[1,2I'pa embodies Cinderbrew itself, assailing players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:439365|h[Spouting Stout]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:439202|h[Burning Fermentation]|h|r. Brew Drops cause |cFF2959D3|Hspell:440104|h[Fill 'Er Up]|h|r if they reach I'pa. Defeating them creates pools of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:440087|h[Oozing Honey]|h|r that shrink.$]$[8,23I'pa embodies Cinderbrew itself, assailing players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:439365|h[Spouting Stout]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:439202|h[Burning Fermentation]|h|r. Brew Drops cause |cFF2959D3|Hspell:440104|h[Fill 'Er Up]|h|r if they reach I'pa. Defeating them creates pools of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:440087|h[Oozing Honey]|h|r that shrink until the drops reform.$]",-1,28422,0,0,2587,28426,1,0,0},
    {28422,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:439031|h[Bottoms Uppercut]|h|r inflicts high Physical damage and knocks the targeted player back.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:439365|h[Spouting Stout]|h|r creates Brew Drops and inflicts moderate Fire damage to all players.",-1,0,0,1,2587,28423,2,28421,0},
    {28423,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:439365|h[Spouting Stout]|h|r creates Brew Drops and inflicts moderate Fire damage to all players.\n\n$bullet;Brew Drops cause |cFF2959D3|Hspell:440104|h[Fill 'Er Up]|h|r  if they reach I'pa.",-1,0,0,2,2587,28424,3,28421,0},
    {28424,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:439202|h[Burning Fermentation]|h|r inflicts high Fire damage to afflicted players unless dispelled.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:439365|h[Spouting Stout]|h|r creates Brew Drops and inflicts moderate Fire damage to all players.",-1,0,0,4,2587,0,4,28421,0},
    {28426,"Section 7",0,2,439365,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,29566,0,32,2587,28918,5,0,0},
    {28427,"Brew Drop",0,1,0,3,{"wago"},"Brew Drops move towards I'pa upon forming.",0,30226,117828,2,2587,0,9,28426,0},
    {28428,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Benk Buzzbee distributes barrels of delicious honey during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:438025|h[Snack Time]|h|r, attracting Ravenous Cinderbees.\n\n\n\nDefeated Cinderbees become docile enough to be mounted by players and will charge forward with a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:438763|h[Bee-Haw!]|h|r command.",-1,28429,0,0,2588,28852,1,0,0},
    {28429,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:440134|h[Honey Marinade]|h|r  drips off targeted players on expiration, creating pools of flaming honey that inflict Fire Damage.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:438025|h[Snack Time]|h|r barrels in the arena will periodically attract Ravenous Cinderbees.",-1,0,0,1,2588,28430,2,28428,0},
    {28430,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;At 1 HP, Ravenous Cinderbees become tame enough to be ridden by players.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:438025|h[Snack Time]|h|r barrels are destroyed by the impact of a Ravenous Cinderbee charging forward with a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:438763|h[Bee-Haw!]|h|r",-1,0,0,2,2588,28431,3,28428,0},
    {28431,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:439524|h[Fluttering Wing]|h|r inflicts moderate Nature damage to all players.\n\n$bullet;Ravenous Cinderbees dart between random players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:438971|h[Shredding Sting]|h|r, afflicting them with a stacking Bleed debuff.",-1,0,0,4,2588,0,4,28428,0},
    {28435,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Goldie Baronbottom uses |cFF2959D3|Hspell:435567|h[Spread the Love!]|h|r to launch Cinderbrew Bombs into the area. Goldie's weapon attacks can set nearby Cimderbrew Bombs alight.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, Goldie Baronbottom casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:435622|h[Let It Hail!]|h|r detonating any remaining Cinderbrew Bombs.",-1,28790,0,0,2589,28439,1,0,0},
    {28436,"Tanks",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:435622|h[Let It Hail]|h|r detonates any remaining Cinderbrew Bombs.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:435789|h[Cindering Wounds]|h|r iinflicts heavy Fire damage over a short duration to all players for each Cinderbrew Bomb that detonates.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:436592|h[Cash Cannon]|h|r ignites nearby Cinderbrew Bombs, causing them to explode.",0,0,0,1,2589,28791,3,28435,0},
    {28437,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:435622|h[Let It Hail]|h|r detonates any remaining Cinderbrew Bombs.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:435789|h[Cindering Wounds]|h|r iinflicts heavy Fire damage over a short duration to all players for each Cinderbrew Bomb that detonates.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:436640|h[Burning Ricochet]|h|r bounces to nearby players and Cinderbrew Bombs.",0,0,0,2,2589,28792,5,28435,0},
    {28438,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:435622|h[Let It Hail]|h|r detonates any remaining Cinderbrew Bombs and inflicts heavy Physical damage to all players.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:435789|h[Cindering Wounds]|h|r iinflicts heavy Fire damage over a short duration to all players for each Cinderbrew Bomb that detonates.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:436640|h[Burning Ricochet]|h|r inflicts heavy Fire damage over time to afflicted players.",0,0,0,4,2589,0,7,28435,0},
    {28439,"Stage One: <PH>",0,2,435567,1,{"wago"},"$[!8,23,\n\n\n\nOn Mythic difficulty, some Cinderbrew Bombs are replaced with Volatile Barrels.$]",-1,28730,0,0,2589,28762,8,0,0},
