    {28454,"Section 36",0,2,427722,2,{"wago"},"$[!15\n\n\n\nIn Heroic difficulty, Weaver's Burden applies Woven Resonance and spreads to additional players. Upon expiration, a Barrier Blossom springs to life at the target's location.$]",0,28455,0,9,2556,28218,15,28355,0},
    {28455,"Section 37",0,2,423195,2,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,0,2556,28456,16,28454,0},
    {28456,"Section 38",0,2,428273,2,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,9,2556,28457,17,28454,0},
    {28457,"Section 35",0,2,423369,2,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,8,2556,0,18,28454,0},
    {28458,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Speakers Brokk and Dorlita unleash a calculated assault of metal and flame, using abilites like |cFF2959D3|Hspell:428161|h[Molten Metal]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:449169|h[Lava Cannon]|h|r and even activating |cFF2959D3|Hspell:428819|h[Exhaust Vents]|h|r to fill the area with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:429999|h[Flaming Scrap]|h|r.\n\n\n\nBrokk periodically uses |cFF2959D3|Hspell:428202|h[Scrap Song]|h|r to conjure and launch a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:428547|h[Scrap Cube]|h|r, which Dorlita then locks onto for an explosive |cFF2959D3|Hspell:428508|h[Blazing Crescendo]|h|r.",-1,28463,0,0,2590,28932,1,0,0},
    {28459,"Speaker Brokk",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,30382,115818,0,2590,28461,6,0,0},
    {28461,"Speaker Dorlita",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,28468,72873,0,2590,0,12,0,0},
    {28463,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; When one Speaker is defeated before the other, the surviving Speaker empowers themselves with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:439577|h[Silenced Speaker]|h|r.\n\n\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:428161|h[Molten Metal]|h|r damages and slows all players unless interrupted.\n\n\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:428120|h[Lava Cannon]|h|r, |cFF2959D3|Hspell:428547|h[Scrap Cube]|h|r, and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:428535|h[Blazing Crescendo]|h|r inflict heavy damage to players who fail to avoid them.",-1,0,0,2,2590,28464,2,28458,0},
    {28464,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:428161|h[Molten Metal]|h|r damages and slows all players unless interrupted.\n\n\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:428535|h[Blazing Crescendo]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:443954|h[Exhaust Vents]|h|r inflict significant damage to all party members. \n\n\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:428120|h[Lava Cannon]|h|r, |cFF2959D3|Hspell:428547|h[Scrap Cube]|h|r, and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:428535|h[Blazing Crescendo]|h|r inflict heavy damage to players who fail to avoid them.",-1,0,0,4,2590,28465,3,28458,0},
    {28465,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; When one Speaker is defeated before the other, the surviving Speaker empowers themselves with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:439577|h[Silenced Speaker]|h|r.\n\n\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:428161|h[Molten Metal]|h|r damages and slows all players unless interrupted.\n\n\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:428120|h[Lava Cannon]|h|r, |cFF2959D3|Hspell:428547|h[Scrap Cube]|h|r, and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:428535|h[Blazing Crescendo]|h|r inflict heavy damage to players who fail to avoid them.",-1,0,0,1,2590,0,4,28458,0},
