    {28730,"Section 7",0,2,435788,0,{"wago"},"$[!8,23,\n\n\n\nOn Mythic difficulty, detonating a Volatile Barrel afflicts all players with Cindering Wounds.$]",-1,28729,0,0,2589,0,9,28439,0},
    {28732,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The Coaglamation casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:441216|h[Viscous Darkness]|h|r to release orbs of black blood that move towards the The Coaglamation to heal it. Players can intercept orbs of black blood to prevent them from reaching The Coaglamation, but are afflicted with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:442285|h[Corrupted Coating]|h|r each time they come into contact with an orb of black blood.",-1,28733,0,0,2600,30077,1,0,0},
    {28733,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell: 441216|h [Viscous Darkness]|h|r causes orbs of black blood to move towards The Coaglamation that players can intercept. Orbs of black blood that touch the Coaglamation heal it.\n\n$bullet;Players that intercept orbs of black blood are afflicted with |cFF2959D3|Hspell: 442285|h[Corrupted Coating]|h|r which absorbs healing recieved.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:445435|h [Blood Surge]|h|r creates pools of black blood.",-1,0,0,1,2600,28734,2,28732,0},
    {28734,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell: 441216|h [Viscous Darkness]|h|r causes orbs of black blood to move towards The Coaglamation that players can intercept. Orbs of black blood that touch the Coaglamation heal it.\n\n$bullet;Players that intercept orbs of black blood are afflicted with |cFF2959D3|Hspell: 442285|h[Corrupted Coating]|h|r which absorbs healing recieved.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell: 437533|h[Dark Pulse]|h|r inflicts significant damage to all players.",-1,0,0,4,2600,28735,3,28732,0},
    {28735,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell: 441216|h [Viscous Darkness]|h|r causes orbs of black blood to move towards The Coaglamation that players can intercept. Orbs of black blood that touch the Coaglamation heal it.\n\n$bullet;Players that intercept orbs of black blood are afflicted with |cFF2959D3|Hspell: 442285|h[Corrupted Coating]|h|r which absorbs healing recieved.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell: 437533|h[Dark Pulse]|h|r inflicts significant damage to all players.",-1,0,0,2,2600,0,4,28732,0},
