    {28893,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The lords of the Silken Court fight as rivals for the queen's favor, alternatingly assaulting their enemies with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:439992|h[Web Bomb]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:440158|h[Reckless Charge]|h|r.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 void energy, Takazj ascends into void form and begins to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:450980|h[Shatter Existence]|h|r. \n\n\n\nAfter rejoining the battle, Anub'arash begins to summon |cFF2959D3|Hspell:438677|h[Stinging Swarms]|h|r as Takazj evokes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:438355|h[Cataclysmic Entropy]|h|r. \n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 anger, Anub'arash enters a raging fury and unleashes a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:451277|h[Spike Storm]|h|r. \n\n\n\nNow with both members of the court at their full power, Anub'arash storms across the chamber with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:440158|h[Reckless Charge]|h|r as Takazj conjures Cataclysmic Entropy.",-1,28894,0,0,2608,29962,1,0,0},
    {28894,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:450980|h[Shatter Existence]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:451277|h[Spike Storm]|h|r apply heavy absorb shields to their casters.\n\n$bullet; Players who are |cFF2959D3|Hspell:449857|h[Impaled]|h|r are stunned until their impaling spike is destroyed.\n\n$bullet; Anub'arash summons scarabs into the chamber with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:438801|h[Call of the Swarm]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2608,28895,2,28893,0},
    {28895,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:438677|h[Stinging Swarm]|h|r transfers to the nearest player or Takazj upon removal.\n\n$bullet; Anub'arash becomes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:440179|h[Entangled]|h|r if he charges through |cFF2959D3|Hspell:440001|h[Binding Webs]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:460360|h[Burrowing Eruption]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:442994|h[Unleashed Swarm]|h|r  inflict heavy raid damage.",-1,0,0,4,2608,28896,3,28893,0},
    {28896,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Anub'arash's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:438218|h[Piercing Strike]|h|r inflicts heavy Physical damage. \n\n$bullet; Takazj moves throughout the chamber using |cFF2959D3|Hspell:450045|h[Skittering Leap]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:450483|h[Void Step]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; The fates of Anub'arash and Skeinspinner Takazj are linked through |cFF2959D3|Hspell:455363|h[Queen's Proclamation]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2608,0,4,28893,0},
    {28897,"Section 10",0,2,439646,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,1,2596,0,16,0,0},
    {28898,"Section 20",0,2,439576,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2601,28798,13,28797,0},
    {28899,"Section 21",0,2,439576,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2601,28769,23,28741,0},
    {28900,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Wounded during the events of the Dawnbreaker, Rasha'nan begins the encounter |cFF2959D3|Hspell:451575|h[Wounded in Battle]|h|r at $451575s1% health.\n\n\n\nAs the encounter progresses, she repositions around the arena casting |cFF2959D3|Hspell:452806|h[Acidic Eruption]|h|r and pelting players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:444094|h[Caustic Hail]|h|r.",-1,28901,0,0,2609,28904,1,0,0},
    {28901,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Waves of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:439789|h[Rolling Acid]|h|r move in the indicated direction and corrode any |cFF2959D3|Hspell:439780|h[Sticky Webs]|h|r into |cFF2959D3|Hspell:439776|h[Acid Pools]|h|r.\n\n$[14,17$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:434089|h[Spinneret's Strands]|h|r inflict party-wide damage when snapped.$]\n\n$[15$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:434089|h[Spinneret's Strands]|h|r affects all other players near the targeted player, and inflict party-wide damage when snapped.$]\n\n$[16$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:434089|h[Spinneret's Strands]|h|r form |cFF2959D3|Hspell:460789|h[Tacky Threads]|h|r when snapped.$]\n\n$[14,17$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:455287|h[Infested Bite]|h|r from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:439815|h[Infested Spawn]|h|r inflicts significant damage.$]\n\n$[15,16$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:439815|h[Infested Spawn]|h|r inflict high damage around targeted players upon impact.$]",-1,0,0,4,2609,28902,2,28900,0},
    {28902,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Waves of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:439789|h[Rolling Acid]|h|r move in the indicated direction and corrode any |cFF2959D3|Hspell:439780|h[Sticky Webs]|h|r into |cFF2959D3|Hspell:439776|h[Acid Pools]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:439815|h[Infested Spawn]|h|r roam freely after casting |cFF2959D3|Hspell:455287|h[Infested Bite]|h|r at their original target.\n\n$bullet;Unmitigated damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:444687|h[Savage Assault]|h|r stacks as |cFF2959D3|Hspell:458067|h[Savage Wound]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2609,28903,3,28900,0},
    {28903,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Waves of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:439789|h[Rolling Acid]|h|r move in the indicated direction and corrode any |cFF2959D3|Hspell:439780|h[Sticky Webs]|h|r into |cFF2959D3|Hspell:439776|h[Acid Pools]|h|r.\n\n$[14,17$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:434089|h[Spinneret's Strands]|h|r inflict party-wide damage when snapped.$]\n\n$[15$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:434089|h[Spinneret's Strands]|h|r affects all other players near the targeted player, and inflict party-wide damage when snapped.$]\n\n$[16$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:434089|h[Spinneret's Strands]|h|r form |cFF2959D3|Hspell:460789|h[Tacky Threads]|h|r when snapped.$]\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:439815|h[Infested Spawn]|h|r-targeted players birth new enemies that rampage, casting|cFF2959D3|Hspell:455287|h[Infested Bite]|h|r  repeatedly.",-1,0,0,2,2609,0,4,28900,0},
