    {28938,"Section 27",0,2,441084,2,{"wago"},"$[!15\n\n\n\nIn Heroic difficulty and above, the explosion inflicts damage to all players and Ansurek's globs of venom form |cFF2959D3|Hspell:437078|h[Acid]|h|r.$]$[!16\n\n\n\nIn Heroic difficulty and above, the explosion inflicts damage to all players and Ansurek's globs of venom form |cFF2959D3|Hspell:437078|h[Acid]|h|r.$]",0,29725,0,8,2602,0,28,30174,0},
