    {30059,"Mojo Puddle",132102,2,0,0,{"wago"},"Drakkari Elemental's Mojo Volley and Surge leave behind puddles of mojo that last for $55627d and inflict $459168s1 Nature damage every $459168t1 sec to nearby players.",-1,0,0,16,593,0,9,6421,0},
