    {30276,"Carrion Worm",0,1,0,2,{"wago"},"Carrion Worms hunger for blood, searching out random players to feast upon.\n\n$[!23\n\n\n\nIn Mythic difficulty, Carrion Worms now erupt into a pool of Fetid Gas upon dying.$]",3,30277,15963,0,2395,21604,6,21571,0},
