    {30281,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"General Umbriss controls Twilight Drakes with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:448847|h[Commanding Roar]|h|r. \n\n\n\nTwilight Drakes sear anyone caught by their |cFF2959D3|Hspell:448566|h[Shadowflame Breath]|h|r.",-1,30282,0,0,2617,29539,1,0,0},
    {30282,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; General Umbriss attacks his current target with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:447261|h[Skullsplitter]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2617,30285,2,30281,0},
    {30283,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet; General Umbriss causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:448882|h[Rock Spikes]|h|r beneath players.\n\n\n\n$bullet; Twilight Drakes unleash their |cFF2959D3|Hspell:448566|h[Shadowflame Breath]|h|r on the players.",3,0,0,4,2617,30287,5,30281,0},
    {30285,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet; General Umbriss causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:448882|h[Rock Spikes]|h|r beneath players.\n\n\n\n$bullet; Twilight Drakes unleash their |cFF2959D3|Hspell:448566|h[Shadowflame Breath]|h|r on the players.",3,0,0,2,2617,30286,3,30281,0},
    {30286,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet; General Umbriss causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:448882|h[Rock Spikes]|h|r beneath players and leaves behind |cFF2959D3|Hspell:448953|h[Rumbling Earth]|h|r.\n\n\n\n$bullet; Twilight Drakes unleash their |cFF2959D3|Hspell:448566|h[Shadowflame Breath]|h|r on the players.",0,0,0,2,2617,30283,4,30281,0},
    {30287,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet; General Umbriss causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:448882|h[Rock Spikes]|h|r beneath players and leaves behind |cFF2959D3|Hspell:448953|h[Rumbling Earth]|h|r.\n\n\n\n$bullet; Twilight Drakes unleash their |cFF2959D3|Hspell:448566|h[Shadowflame Breath]|h|r on the players.",0,0,0,4,2617,0,6,30281,0},
    {30288,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Throngus forges various weapons to decimate his enemies, causing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:452008|h[Blistering Heat]|h|r during the weapon's creation. \n\n\n\nThese massive weapons leaves behind searing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:449536|h[Molten Pools]|h|r with their attacks.",-1,30290,0,0,2627,29796,1,0,0},
    {30290,"Tank",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:449687|h[Molten Mace]|h|r massively bolsters the power of Throngus's melee swings.\n\n\n\n$bullet;Throngus slashes his enemies with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:447395|h[Fiery Cleave]|h|r and covers the ground with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:449536|h[Molten Pools]|h|r.",0,0,0,1,2627,30291,2,30288,0},
    {30291,"Tank",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Throngus slashes his enemies with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:447395|h[Fiery Cleave]|h|r and covers the ground with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:449536|h[Molten Pools]|h|r.",3,0,0,1,2627,30292,3,30288,0},
    {30292,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Throngus slashes his enemies with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:447395|h[Fiery Cleave]|h|r and covers the ground with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:449536|h[Molten Pools]|h|r.\n\n\n\n$bullet;Throngus unleashes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:449444|h[Molten Flurry]|h|r with his molten swords and ignites his foes with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:449474|h[Molten Spark]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2627,30293,4,30288,0},
    {30293,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Throngus slashes his enemies with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:447395|h[Fiery Cleave]|h|r and covers the ground with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:449536|h[Molten Pools]|h|r.\n\n\n\n$bullet;Throngus unleashes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:449444|h[Molten Flurry]|h|r with his molten swords and ignites his foes with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:449474|h[Molten Spark]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,2627,0,5,30288,0},
    {30294,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Erudax channels |cFF2959D3|Hspell:450079|h[Void Surge]|h|r and causes Void Tendrils to erupt from the ground, then summons |cFF2959D3|Hspell:449985|h[Shadow Gale]|h|r to destroy his enemies.",-1,30300,0,0,2619,29614,1,0,0},
    {30295,"Overview",0,3,0,1,{"wago"},"Drahga Shadowburner weakens his foes with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:450095|h[Curse of Entropy]|h|r and summons Invoked Shadowflame Spirits that explode with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:75238|h[Shadowflame Nova]|h|r.\n\n\n\nAt 1% health, Drahga forces the subjugated Twilight dragon Valiona to aide him in battle. Valiona knocks back players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:456751|h[Twilight Buffet]|h|r and scorches them with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:448105|h[Devouring Flame]|h|r.",-1,30296,0,0,2618,29546,1,0,0},
    {30296,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Drahga Shadowburner sears his current target with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:447966|h[Shadowflame Bolt]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2618,30297,2,30295,0},
    {30297,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Invoked Shadowflame Spirit erupts with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:75238|h[Shadowflame Nova]|h|r upon reaching its target.\n\n\n\n$bullet;Valiona's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:456751|h[Twilight Buffet]|h|r inflicts Shadowflame damage to all players and knocks them back.",-1,0,0,2,2618,30298,3,30295,0},
    {30298,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Invoked Shadowflame Spirit erupts with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:75238|h[Shadowflame Nova]|h|r upon reaching its target.\n\n\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:450095|h[Curse of Entropy]|h|r reduces target's movement speed and abosrbs healing.\n\n\n\n$bullet;Valiona's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:456751|h[Twilight Buffet]|h|r inflicts Shadowflame damage to all players and knocks them back.",-1,0,0,4,2618,0,4,30295,0},
    {30299,"Section 11",0,2,456719,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2619,0,14,29658,0},
    {30300,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:450100|h[Crush]|h|r inflicts heavy Shadow and Physical damage.\n\n\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:450088|h[Void Infusion]|h|r corrupts Alexstraza's eggs and turns them into Mutated Hatchlings.",-1,0,0,1,2619,30301,2,30294,0},
    {30301,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:449939|h[Shadow Gale]|h|r inflicts heavy shadow damage to players caught inside the storm.\n\n\n\n$bullet;Void Tendrils stun players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:450087|h[Depth's Grasp]|h|r.\n\n\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:450088|h[Void Infusion]|h|r corrupts Alexstraza's eggs and turns them into Mutated Hatchlings.",-1,0,0,2,2619,30303,3,30294,0},
    {30302,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:450079|h[Void Surge]|h|r blasts all players with shadow damage.\n\n\n\n$bullet;Erudax afflicts multiple players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:448057|h[Abyssal Corruption]|h|r, causing them to erupt in void energy.",0,0,0,4,2619,0,5,30294,0},
    {30303,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:450079|h[Void Surge]|h|r blasts all players with shadow damage.",3,0,0,4,2619,30302,4,30294,0},
