    {30319,"Overview",0,3,0,1,{"wago"},"Big M.O.M.M.A. commands an army of drones that, when defeated, cause Big M.O.M.M.A. to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:460156|h[Jumpstart]|h|r, inflicting heavy damage to all players but causing Big M.O.M.M.A. to take increased damage.\n\n\n\nAfterwards, Big M.O.M.M.A. requisitions an additional squadron of drones with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:471585|h[Mobilize Mechadrones]|h|r.",-1,30944,0,0,2648,30973,1,0,0},
    {30320,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Keeza Quickfuse blasts players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:460602|h[Quick Shot]|h|r and her |cFF2959D3|Hspell:473594|h[B.B.B.F.G.]|h|r while planting Ticking Time Bombs with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:460867|h[Big Bada BOOM!]|h|r.\n\n\n\nBront |cFF2959D3|Hspell:459799|h[Wallops]|h|r his enemies and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:459779|h[Barreling Charges]|h|r through anything in his path - Ticking Time Bombs included.",-1,30950,0,0,2649,30321,1,0,0},
    {30321,"Keeza Quickfuse",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,30325,123036,0,2649,30322,5,0,0},
