    {30331,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Flarendo and Torq put on a show for the audience, throwing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:473650|h[Scrapbombs]|h|r and afflicting arena combatants with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:473951|h[Static Charge]|h|r. \n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, Flarendo and Torq come together in a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:465833|h[Colossal Clash]|h|r!",-1,30332,0,0,2640,30336,1,0,0},
    {30332,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:472222|h[Blistering Spite]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472225|h[Galvanized Spite]|h|r  increase over time as players fight Flarendo and Torq.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214190|h[Eruption Stomp]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217933|h[Overload Burst]|h|r inflict heavy damage.\n\n$bullet; Flarendo and Torq take reduced damage while affected by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:471660|h[Raised Guard]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2640,30334,2,30331,0},
    {30333,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:472222|h[Blistering Spite]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472225|h[Galvanized Spite]|h|r  increase over time as players fight Flarendo and Torq.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:473650|h[Scrapbomb]|h|r inflicts damage split evenly among players in its explosion radius.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:465833|h[Colossal Clash]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to all players",-1,0,0,4,2640,0,4,30331,0},
    {30334,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:472222|h[Blistering Spite]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472225|h[Galvanized Spite]|h|r  increase over time as players fight Flarendo and Torq.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:473951|h[Static Charge]|h|r erupts into a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:473983|h[Static Discharge]|h|r once it builds to maximum charge.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:473650|h[Scrapbomb]|h|r will inflict massive damage to the raid if no player is hit.",-1,0,0,2,2640,30333,3,30331,0},
