    {30370,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Stix assaults the players while slowly gaining energy. Upon reaching 100 energy Stix uses |cFF2959D3|Hspell:464399|h[Electromagnetic Sorting]|h|r, pulling |cFF2959D3|Hspell:464854|h[Garbage Piles]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:464865|h[Discarded Doomsplosives]|h|r from the landfill while selecting several players to become |cFF2959D3|Hspell:461536|h[Rolling Rubbish]|h|r.\n\n\n\nEventually, Stix forces his mech into |cFF2959D3|Hspell:467117|h[Overdrive]|h|r and operates at |cFF2959D3|Hspell:473227|h[Maximum Output]|h|r until defeated.",-1,30371,0,0,2642,30388,1,0,0},
    {30371,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217954|h[Meltdown]|h|r inflicts major damage to Stix's current target, especially if they are affected by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:464112|h[Demolish]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Scrapmasters and Junkyard Hyenas can be absorbed by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:461536|h[Rolling Rubbish]|h|r, depositing them wherever the ball is destroyed.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:464865|h[Discarded Doomsplosive]|h|r inflicts devastating raidwide damage if not absorbed by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:461536|h[Rolling Rubbish]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2642,30372,2,30370,0},
    {30372,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Scrapmasters and Junkyard Hyenas can be absorbed by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:461536|h[Rolling Rubbish]|h|r, depositing them wherever the ball is destroyed.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:464149|h[Incinerator]|h|r can turn nearby garbage piles into |cFF2959D3|Hspell:464248|h[Hot Garbage]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:464865|h[Discarded Doomsplosive]|h|r inflicts devastating raidwide damage if not absorbed by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:461536|h[Rolling Rubbish]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2642,30373,3,30370,0},
    {30373,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:464399|h[Electromagnetic Sorting]|h|r inflicts significant raidwide damage.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:464149|h[Incinerator]|h|r can turn nearby garbage piles into |cFF2959D3|Hspell:464248|h[Hot Garbage]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:464865|h[Discarded Doomsplosive]|h|r inflicts devastating raidwide damage if not absorbed by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:461536|h[Rolling Rubbish]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,2642,0,4,30370,0},
