    {30420,"Section 50",0,2,465009,2,{"wago"},"$[!15,16\n\n\n\nIn Heroic and Mythic difficulty, the Dynamite Booty explosion additionally inflicts Fire damage over time.$]",0,0,0,8,2644,30417,22,31599,0},
    {30421,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Sprocketmonger Lockenstock prepares a demonstration for the players while slowly gaining energy. Conveyor belts around the factory produce explosive new technology for Lockenstock to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:473276|h[Activate Inventions!]|h|r .\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, Lockenstock prepares a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:466765|h[Beta Launch]|h|r of an improved contraption, infusing it with void powers before renewing his assault.",-1,31780,0,0,2653,30425,1,0,0},
    {30422,"Tanks",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Each application of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:465917|h[Gravi-Gunk]|h|r increases all damage taken.\n\n$bullet;The damage of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214872|h[Pyro Party Pack]|h|r is reduced the further the target is from other players.",0,0,0,1,2653,31778,3,30421,0},
    {30423,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:466235|h[Wire Transfer]|h|r inflicts significant damage to players standing within the effect",0,0,0,2,2653,31779,6,30421,0},
    {30424,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:465232|h[Sonic Ba-Boom]|h|r applies a damage over time effect to all players.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1218319|h[Voidsplosion]|h|r inflicts significant damage to all players and absorbs healing taken.",0,0,0,4,2653,0,8,30421,0},
    {30425,"Stage One: Assembly Required",0,2,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,31654,0,0,2653,30427,9,0,0},
    {30426,"Section 7",0,2,465232,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,4,2653,31126,33,30425,0},
    {30427,"Stage Two: Research and Destruction",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,30580,0,0,2653,0,37,0,0},
    {30428,"Overview",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"Chopper Redhook fixates on a random enemy. The longer Chopper chases enemies, the faster he gets with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:257649|h[Boiling Rage]|h|r.\n\n\n\nAs the fight progresses, Irontide forces engage the party while the area is bombarded by a continual |cFF2959D3|Hspell:257585|h[Cannon Barrage]|h|r.\n\n\n\n|cFF2959D3|Hspell:273716|h[Heavy Ordnance]|h|r appears during the barrage, and  unless it is detonated before time expires it will explode and damage the party.",0,30429,0,0,2654,30432,1,0,0},
    {30429,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Kill Irontide forces.\n\n$bullet;When the target of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:257459|h[On the Hook]|h|r, run away.",-1,0,0,2,2654,30430,2,30428,0},
    {30430,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Irontide Powdershots inflict damage to everyone in the party.\n\n$bullet;If |cFF2959D3|Hspell:273716|h[Heavy Ordnance]|h|r explodes it does massive damage to the party.\n\n$bullet;When the target of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:257459|h[On the Hook]|h|r, run away.",-1,0,0,4,2654,30431,3,30428,0},
    {30431,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Avoid being in melee range with Chopper Redhook due to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:256867|h[Heavy Hitter]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Face Irontide Cleaver's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:257292|h[Heavy Slash]|h|r away from the party.\n\n$bullet;Run over |cFF2959D3|Hspell:273716|h[Heavy Ordnance]|h|r to prevent them from damaging the party.",-1,0,0,1,2654,0,4,30428,0},
