    {30453,"Section 21",0,2,473115,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2642,0,16,30451,0},
    {30454,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Emberdawn lights the winds aflame as she protects her nest. |cFF2959D3|Hspell:465904|h[Burning Gale]|h|r pushes players and lights |cFF2959D3|Hspell:465957|h[Ignited Embers]|h|r, creating |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469621|h[Flaming Twisters]|h|r that sweep across the garden.",-1,30455,0,0,2655,34509,1,0,0},
    {30455,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:466556|h[Flaming Updraft]|h|r leaves behind a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:465957|h[Ignited Embers]|h|r upon expiration.\n\n\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:465904|h[Burning Gale]|h|r pushes players and causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:465957|h[Ignited Embers]|h|r to create |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469621|h[Flaming Twisters]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2655,30456,2,30454,0},
    {30456,"Healer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:466556|h[Flaming Updraft]|h|r inflicts significant damage to afflicted players.\n\n\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:465904|h[Burning Gale]|h|r pushes players and causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:465957|h[Ignited Embers]|h|r to create |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469621|h[Flaming Twisters]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,2655,30457,3,30454,0},
    {30457,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Emberdawn's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:466064|h[Searing Beak]|h|r inflicts heavy Physical damage followed by significant Fire damage over time.\n\n\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:465904|h[Burning Gale]|h|r pushes players and causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:465957|h[Ignited Embers]|h|r to create |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469621|h[Flaming Twisters]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2655,0,4,30454,0},
    {30459,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$[1,2,205,216Latch spews |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472777|h[Gunk Splatter]|h|r at players while Kalis assails her foes with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472724|h[Shadow Bolt]|h|r.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, Latch attempts to draw players in with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472795|h[Heaving Yank]|h|r while Kalis wails a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472736|h[Debilitating Shriek]|h|r.$]$[8,23Latch spews |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472777|h[Gunk Splatter]|h|r at players while Kalis assails her foes with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:474105|h[Curse of Darkness]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472724|h[Shadow Bolt]|h|r.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, Latch attempts to draw players in with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472795|h[Heaving Yank]|h|r while Kalis wails a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472736|h[Debilitating Shriek]|h|r.$]",-1,30460,0,0,2656,31554,1,0,0},
    {30460,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Latch's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472795|h[Heaving Yank]|h|r interrupts and pulls in the first target it hits.\n\n$bullet;Kalis's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472736|h[Debilitating Shriek]|h|r continues to increase its Shadow damage until interrupted.",3,0,0,2,2656,31552,2,30459,0},
    {30461,"Healer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Kalis's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472736|h[Debilitating Shriek]|h|r continues to increase its Shadow damage until interrupted.\n\n$bullet;Latch's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472795|h[Heaving Yank]|h|r interrupts and pulls in the first target it hits.",-1,0,0,4,2656,30462,4,30459,0},
    {30462,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Latch's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472888|h[Bone Hack]|h|r inflicts significant Physical damage.\n\n$bullet;Latch's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472795|h[Heaving Yank]|h|r interrupts and pulls in the first target it hits.",-1,0,0,1,2656,0,5,30459,0},
    {30463,"Kalis",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,31241,125201,0,2656,31244,7,0,0},
    {30464,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Commander Kroluk crashes down on players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472081|h[Reckless Leap]|h|r and cuts them to pieces with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:467620|h[Rampage]|h|r.\n\n\n\nAt 66% and 33% remaining health, Kroluk lets out a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:468070|h[Rallying Bellow]|h|r to summon a warparty.\n\nKroluk maintains |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1250851|h[Shield Wall]|h|r until his warparty is defeated.",-1,34443,0,0,2657,31014,1,0,0},
    {30465,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:468070|h[Rallying Bellow]|h|r summons a warparty to fight alongside Commander Kroluk.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell: 470963|h[Bladestorm]|h|r inflicts damage to all players within Commander Kroluk's path.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253026|h[Intimidating Shout]|h|r fears players who stand alone.",0,0,0,2,2657,33732,5,30464,0},
    {30467,"Tank",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:468070|h[Rallying Bellow]|h|r summons a warparty to fight alongside Commander Kroluk.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell: 467620|h[Rampage]|h|r inflicts sustained damage to Commander Kroluk's current target.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell: 1253026|h[Intimidating Shout]|h|r fears players standing alone.",0,0,0,1,2657,0,7,30464,0},
    {30468,"[PH]",0,2,470963,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2657,31067,16,31065,0},
    {30469,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The Restless Heart assails players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472556|h[Arrow Rain]|h|r before focusing its fury on a player with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:474528|h[Bolt Gale]|h|r.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, the Restless Heart fires a wind-infused arrow that creates an expanding ring of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:468442|h[Billowing Wind]|h|r.",-1,35168,0,0,2658,31265,1,0,0},
    {30470,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253977|h[Turbulent Arrows]|h|r knock players into the air when touched, removing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216042|h[Squall Leap]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:468429|h[Bullseye Windblast]|h|r creates an expanding ring of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:468442|h[Billowing Wind]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:474528|h[Bolt Gale]|h|r launches a continuous volley of arrows towards a player.",3,0,0,2,2658,35169,3,30469,0},
    {30471,"Healer",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:474528|h[Bolt Gale]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to the targeted player.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253977|h[Turbulent Arrows]|h|r knock players into the air when touched, removing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216042|h[Squall Leap]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:468429|h[Bullseye Windblast]|h|r creates an expanding ring of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:468442|h[Billowing Wind]|h|r.",3,0,0,4,2658,35170,5,30469,0},
    {30472,"Tank",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:472662|h[Tempest Slash]|h|r knocks The Restless Heart's primary target away and briefly increases their Physical damage taken.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253977|h[Turbulent Arrows]|h|r knock players into the air when touched, removing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216042|h[Squall Leap]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:468429|h[Bullseye Windblast]|h|r creates an expanding ring of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:468442|h[Billowing Wind]|h|r.",3,0,0,1,2658,0,7,30469,0},
    {30473,"[PH]",0,2,1253986,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2658,0,17,31270,0},
    {30474,"Section 24",0,2,460603,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,30162,0,0,2639,30116,27,30779,0},
    {30476,"Section 10",0,2,465917,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,1,2653,0,36,30425,0},
    {30477,"Gravi-Grip",0,2,1214872,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,1,2653,30476,35,30425,0},
    {30480,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Geezle siphons massive power from the generator during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:465463|h[Turbo Charge]|h|r, causing the Waterworks to destabilize and collapse. \n\n\n\nGeezle then fries his enemies with an array of voltaic attacks as |cFF2959D3|Hspell:468846|h[Leaping Sparks]|h|r pursue players to their electrocution in the depths of the dam.",-1,31955,0,0,2651,30484,1,0,0},
    {30484,"Section 5",0,2,465456,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,30485,0,0,2651,30729,5,0,0},
    {30485,"Section 6",0,2,466088,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2651,0,6,30484,0},
    {30486,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Gallywix gains energy over time, activating The House of Chrome's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469286|h[Giga Coils]|h|r at max capacity. |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469362|h[Charged Giga Bomb]|h|rs brought to Giga Controls trigger a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469767|h[Giga Bomb Detonation]|h|r. This causes a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1220846|h[Control Meltdown]|h|r which interrupts Gallywix's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469286|h[Giga Coils]|h|r. Upon losing both Giga Controls a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1215209|h[Sabotage Zone]|h|r forms.\n\n\n\nAdditionally, throughout the encounter Gallywix calls in the most overpaid Darkfuse Cronies to aid him.\n\n\n\nAs the battle rages on Gallywix alters and augments his arsenal bringing maniacal mayhem.$[14,15,17$  Upon reaching 50% health Gallywix upgrades his capabilities to eliminates players once and for all. $]",-1,30487,0,0,2646,30490,1,0,0},
    {30487,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$[15,16$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:465952|h[Big Bad Buncha Bombs]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214607|h[Bigger Badder Bomb Blast]|h|r additionally create |cFF2959D3|Hspell:466165|h[1500-Pound \"Dud\"]|h|r.$]\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:466340|h[Scatterblast Canisters]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214607|h[Bigger Badder Bomb Blast]|h|r affect players in Gallywix's frontal direction.\n\n$bullet;Dying Darkfuse Technicians drop Giga Bombs that go |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1223905|h[Giga BOOM!]|h|r after $1223905D. Gallywix's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469327|h[Giga Blast]|h|r detonates these immediately.\n\n$bullet;Gallywix release all |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1220290|h[Trick Shots]|h|r upon reaching $1220290s2 stacks or when changing primary targets.",-1,0,0,1,2646,30488,2,30486,0},
    {30488,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Player affected by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1220761|h[Mechengineer's Canisters]|h|r detonate on consumption or expiration causing a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:474447|h[Canister Detonation]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Dying Darkfuse Technicians drop Giga Bombs that go |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1223905|h[Giga BOOM!]|h|r after $1223905D. Gallywix's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469327|h[Giga Blast]|h|r detonates these immediately.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:469362|h[Charged Giga Bomb]|h|rs brought to Giga Controls trigger a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469767|h[Giga Bomb Detonation]|h|r causing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1220846|h[Control Meltdown]|h|r which interrupts Gallywix's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469286|h[Giga Coils]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:469286|h[Giga Coils]|h|r, |cFF2959D3|Hspell:466338|h[Zagging Zizzler]|h|r, and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214369|h[TOTAL DESTRUCTION!!!]|h|r inflict significant damage.",-1,0,0,4,2646,30489,3,30486,0},
    {30489,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:465952|h[Big Bad Buncha Bombs]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214607|h[Bigger Badder Bomb Blast]|h|r additionally trigger |cFF2959D3|Hspell:466158|h[Sapper's Satchel]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214755|h[Overloaded Rockets]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Dying Darkfuse Technicians drop Giga Bombs that go |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1223905|h[Giga BOOM!]|h|r after $1223905D. Gallywix's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469327|h[Giga Blast]|h|r detonates these immediately.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:469362|h[Charged Giga Bomb]|h|rs brought to Giga Controls trigger a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469767|h[Giga Bomb Detonation]|h|r causing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1220846|h[Control Meltdown]|h|r which interrupts Gallywix's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469286|h[Giga Coils]|h|r.\n\n$[15,16$bullet;Sharpshot Sentry can inflict high damage with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:466834|h[Shock Barrage]|h|r when left uncontrolled.$]",-1,0,0,2,2646,0,4,30486,0},
    {30490,"Stage One: The House of Chrome",0,0,0,3,{"wago"},"\"Take a good look at what gold and goblins can getcha.\"\n\n\n\nCornered in The House of Chrome Gallywix stands ready to blast foes.",0,30555,0,0,2646,30497,5,0,0},
    {30491,"Gallywix",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,30492,125492,0,2646,31028,114,30498,0},
    {30492,"Section 9",0,2,1214607,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,30493,0,1,2646,31477,115,30491,0},
    {30493,"Section 10",0,2,466154,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2646,30494,116,30492,0},
    {30494,"Section 10",0,2,466153,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2646,30495,117,30492,0},
    {30495,"Section 10",0,2,1214755,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,2,2646,30560,118,30492,0},
    {30497,"Stage Two: Mechanical Maniac",0,0,0,2,{"wago"},"\"Supply and demand! Deal with it!\"\n\n\n\nGallywix moves about The House of Chrome calling in Darkfuse cronies.",0,30564,0,0,2646,31558,25,0,0},
    {30498,"Stage One: What an Arsenal!",0,0,0,3,{"wago"},"\"You certainly don't get your likeness carved into the side of a mountain by letting others push you around\"\n\n\n\nGallywix pummels his enemies with his upgraded arsenal.",0,30491,0,0,2646,0,113,0,0},
    {30499,"Section 7",0,2,466197,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,1,2651,0,14,0,0},
    {30500,"Section 13",0,2,466235,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2653,31380,30,30425,0},
    {30501,"Section 7",0,2,466128,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,1,2641,30390,29,31656,0},
    {30502,"Section 14",0,2,466338,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2646,0,122,30492,0},
    {30503,"Section 15",0,2,466342,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2646,0,127,31477,0},
    {30505,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The two heads of Mug'Zee, Mug and Zee, begin the encounter in a friendly contest to see who is in control. Whichever head has $[16 all$]$[14,15,17the most$] players on their side of the arena becomes the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:466376|h[Head Honcho]|h|r, activating a unique set of abilities to unleash upon players.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 40% remaining health, Mug and Zee combine their efforts and attack in unison granting them the use of all of their abilities at once.",-1,30506,0,0,2645,31662,1,0,0},
    {30506,"Tanks",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:466518|h[Molten Gold Knuckles]|h|r inflict heavy damage in front of Mug and apply |cFF2959D3|Hspell:467202|h[Golden Drip]|h|r to players hit.\n\n$bullet;Damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469490|h[Double Whammy Shot]|h|r is mitigated by the closest player hit.",-1,0,0,1,2645,31736,2,30505,0},
    {30507,"Damage Dealers",0,0,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:472631|h[Earthshaker Gaols]|h|r splits damage among all players within the effect, trapping them within earthen walls.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:466480|h[Frostshatter Spears]|h|r inflict lethal damage to the first player or |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472631|h[Earthshaker Gaol]|h|r wall they hit.\n\n$bullet;Touching |cFF2959D3|Hspell:466539|h[Unstable Crawler Mines]|h|r causes them to explode, unleashing an |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1220551|h[Unstable Cluster Bomb]|h|r and causing all players to suffer from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469043|h[Searing Shrapnel]|h|r.",0,0,0,2,2645,31737,4,30505,0},
    {30508,"Healers",0,0,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:468663|h[Elemental Calamity]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469715|h[Uncontrolled Burn]|h|r inflict persistent damage over time each time Mug'zee swaps which head is the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:466376|h[Head Honcho]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Mug'Zee gains |cFF2959D3|Hspell:466385|h[Moxie]|h|r the longer each head is in command.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:466480|h[Frostshatter Spears]|h|r inflict lethal damage to the first player or |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472631|h[Earthshaker Gaol]|h|r wall they hit.",0,0,0,4,2645,0,6,30505,0},
    {30510,"Stage Two:  The Head Honcho",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,30870,0,0,2645,0,87,0,0},
    {30517,"Intermission: Bulletstorm",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"Upon reaching 40% health both heads decide to work together unleashing a series of Static Charges and Bulletstorms before their final, combined, assault begins.",-1,31340,0,0,2645,30510,82,0,0},
    {30520,"Section 16",0,2,1216414,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2653,30718,12,31725,0},
    {30533,"Cleanup Crew",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"Stix calls in his Cleanup Crew to help dispose of unwelcome visitors.",-1,31645,0,0,2642,30378,19,0,0},
    {30536,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Arcanotron Custos controls players with its |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214032|h[Ethereal Shackles]|h|r and by creating pools of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214089|h[Arcane Residue]|h|r. Upon running out of energy, Arcanotron Custos begins its |cFF2959D3|Hspell:474345|h[Refueling Protocol]|h|r, drawing in |cFF2959D3|Hspell:474308|h[Energy Orbs]|h|r to refuel itself.",-1,30537,0,0,2659,31142,1,0,0},
    {30537,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214081|h[Arcane Expulsion]|h|r inflicts a heavy amount of damage and knocks back all players.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214089|h[Arcane Residue]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to players standing in the area.\n\n$bullet; Arcanotron Custos gains |cFF2959D3|Hspell:474407|h[Arcane Empowerment]|h|r if an Energy Orb reaches it.",-1,0,0,2,2659,30538,2,30536,0},
    {30538,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214038|h[Ethereal Shackles]|h|r roots players and inflicts periodic damage.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214089|h[Arcane Residue]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to players standing in the area.\n\n$bullet; Arcanotron Custos gains |cFF2959D3|Hspell:474407|h[Arcane Empowerment]|h|r if an Energy Orb reaches it.",-1,0,0,4,2659,30539,3,30536,0},
    {30539,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:474496|h[Repulsing Slam]|h|r inflicts a heavy amount of damage and knocks back its target.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214089|h[Arcane Residue]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to players standing in the area.\n\n$bullet; Arcanotron Custos gains |cFF2959D3|Hspell:474407|h[Arcane Empowerment]|h|r if an Energy Orb reaches it.",-1,0,0,1,2659,0,4,30536,0},
    {30540,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"At the start of the encounter and $1223847s3% remaining health, Gemellus uses |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1223847|h[Triplicate]|h|r to create clones that drift around the arena. Gemellus and its clones are bound by a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1223670|h[Synaptic Nexus]|h|r and act as one.",-1,35354,0,0,2660,33338,1,0,0},
    {30541,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$[23$bullet; Gemellus maintains a damage absorb shield until its |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253707|h[Neural Link]|h|r is broken.$]\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224299|h[Astral Grasp]|h|r pulls players towards their respective Gemellus.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1223957|h[Cosmic Sting]|h|r inflicts moderate damage and creates |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224100|h[Void Secretions]|h|r upon expiration.",0,0,0,2,2660,35355,4,30540,0},
    {30542,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$[23$bullet; Gemellus maintains a damage absorb shield until its |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253707|h[Neural Link]|h|r is broken.$]\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1223957|h[Cosmic Sting]|h|r inflicts moderate damage and creates |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224100|h[Void Secretions]|h|r upon expiration.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224299|h[Astral Grasp]|h|r pulls players towards their respective Gemellus.",0,0,0,4,2660,35356,7,30540,0},
    {30543,"Tanks",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$[23$bullet; Gemellus maintains a damage absorb shield until its |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253707|h[Neural Link]|h|r is broken.$]\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224299|h[Astral Grasp]|h|r pulls players towards their respective Gemellus.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1223957|h[Cosmic Sting]|h|r inflicts moderate damage and creates |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224100|h[Void Secretions]|h|r upon expiration.",0,0,0,1,2660,0,10,30540,0},
    {30544,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Seranel assaults players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224903|h[Suppression Zones]|h|r that cause |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1225135|h[Feedback]|h|r to players affected by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224801|h[Runic Mark]|h|r.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, Seranel causes an |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1225193|h[Wave of Silence]|h|r silencing and pacifying players outside of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224903|h[Suppression Zones]|h|r.",-1,30545,0,0,2661,33323,1,0,0},
    {30545,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1225193|h[Wave of Silence]|h|r inflicts heavy damage and silences players outside of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224903|h[Suppression Zones]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224801|h[Runic Mark]|h|r inflicts moderate damage to nearby players.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224903|h[Suppression Zone]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1225135|h[Feedback]|h|r silences and pacifies players.",-1,0,0,2,2661,30546,2,30544,0},
    {30546,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1225193|h[Wave of Silence]|h|r inflicts heavy damage and silences players outside of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224903|h[Suppression Zones]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224801|h[Runic Mark]|h|r inflicts moderate damage to nearby players.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224903|h[Suppression Zone]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1225135|h[Feedback]|h|r silences and pacifies players.",-1,0,0,4,2661,30547,3,30544,0},
    {30547,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248689|h[Hastening Ward]|h|r increases Seranel's attack speed and causes his melee attacks to inflict additional Arcane damage.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1225193|h[Wave of Silence]|h|r inflicts heavy damage and silences players outside of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224903|h[Suppression Zones]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224801|h[Runic Mark]|h|r inflicts moderate damage to nearby players.",-1,0,0,1,2661,0,4,30544,0},
    {30548,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Degentrius leads the assault from atop Magisters' Terrace, commanding the platform with overwhelming Void magic. |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214714|h[Void Torrent]|h|r streams carve across the arena as they flow into Degentrius, while |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1215087|h[Unstable Void Essence]|h|rs ricochet around the platform.",-1,30549,0,0,2662,31276,1,0,0},
    {30549,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; If there are no players standing under |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1215087|h[Unstable Void Essence]|h|r  when it impacts, damage will be inflicted to all players.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214714|h[Void Torrent]|h|r  inflicts moderate damage and stuns any players that come into contact with it.",-1,0,0,2,2662,30550,2,30548,0},
    {30550,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1215897|h[Devouring Entropy]|h|r creates Entropy Orbs upon removal.\n\n$bullet; If there are no players standing under |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1215087|h[Unstable Void Essence]|h|r  when it impacts, damage will be inflicted to all players.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214714|h[Void Torrent]|h|r  inflicts moderate damage and stuns any players that come into contact with it.",-1,0,0,4,2662,30551,3,30548,0},
    {30551,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1215941|h[Null Bomb]|h|r will inflict massive damage to all players if it is not triggered by a player.\n\n$bullet; If there are no players standing under |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1215087|h[Unstable Void Essence]|h|r  when it impacts, damage will be inflicted to all players.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214714|h[Void Torrent]|h|r  inflicts moderate damage and stuns any players that come into contact with it.",-1,0,0,1,2662,0,4,30548,0},
