    {30722,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Lord Roccor casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462351|h[Roiling Magma]|h|r on his target, inflicting damage and providing the raw material to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:463674|h[Crystallize]|h|r his obsidian progeny.\n\n\n\nWhen Lord Roccor reaches 95% health and every 20% damage suffered thereafter, he will cast |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462322|h[Eruption]|h|r, filling the room with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462351|h[Roiling Magma]|h|r. Each |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462346|h[Living Magma]|h|r that reaches its destination will increase the power of the elemental created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462320|h[Igneous Crystallization]|h|r.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, Roccor casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462317|h[Volcanic Upheaval]|h|r, inflicting huge damage to all players.",-1,30726,0,0,2663,30706,1,0,0},
    {30726,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462351|h[Roiling Magma]|h|r is cast on Lord Roccor's primary target and inflicts Fire damage to enemies in the area.\n\n$bullet; Stepping on a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462346|h[Living Magma]|h|r will destroy it and inflict damage over time to the player.\n\n$bullet; When crystallized, Obsidian Elementals attack nearby players.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462317|h[Volcanic Upheaval]|h|r inflicts significant damage to all players.",-1,0,0,1,2663,30727,2,30722,0},
    {30727,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Stepping on a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462346|h[Living Magma]|h|r will destroy it and inflict damage over time to the player.\n\n$bullet; When crystallized, Obsidian Elementals attack nearby players.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462317|h[Volcanic Upheaval]|h|r inflicts significant damage to all players.",-1,0,0,2,2663,30728,3,30722,0},
    {30728,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462351|h[Roiling Magma]|h|r is cast on Lord Roccor's primary target and inflicts Fire damage to enemies in the area.\n\n$bullet; Stepping on a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462346|h[Living Magma]|h|r will destroy it and inflict damage over time to the player.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462317|h[Volcanic Upheaval]|h|r inflicts significant damage to all players.",-1,0,0,4,2663,0,4,30722,0},
    {30729,"Section 8",0,2,468276,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,30730,0,32,2651,31781,7,0,0},
    {30730,"Section 9",0,2,468261,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,30731,0,0,2651,30799,8,30729,0},
    {30731,"Section 10",0,2,468661,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2651,0,9,30730,0},
    {30732,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Bael'Gar's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462974|h[Giant Strike]|h|r inflicts enormous damage in a cone in front of him with every swing. Damage is split between players struck.\n\n\n\n|cFF2959D3|Hspell:463890|h[Rockfall]|h|r causes large boulders and small rocks to fall from the ceiling that players must avoid. Players will need to seek cover when Bael'Gar casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:463143|h[Molten Furnace]|h|r. Any boulders that remain when Bael'Gar casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462972|h[Shatter]|h|r will inflict significant additional damage to the entire raid.\n\n\n\nWhenever a boulder is destroyed, several Spawns of Bael'Gar are created. When a Spawn of Bael'Gar is killed, its |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462968|h[Molten Heart]|h|r inflicts damage over time to a random player.",-1,30733,0,0,2664,30736,1,0,0},
    {30733,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Tanks will need to split the damage of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462974|h[Giant Strike]|h|r in order to survive.\n\n$bullet; The large boulders created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:463890|h[Rockfall]|h|r inflict higher damage the nearer players are to the point of impact.\n\n$bullet; Any boulders that remain when Bael'Gar casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462972|h[Shatter]|h|r have the potential to make its damage lethal.\n\n$bullet; When a boulder is destroyed several Spawns of Bael'Gar will be created and attack nearby players.",-1,0,0,1,2664,30734,2,30732,0},
    {30734,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; The large boulders created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:463890|h[Rockfall]|h|r inflict higher damage the nearer players are to the point of impact.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:463143|h[Molten Furnace]|h|r inflicts lethal damage to players that are not behind cover.\n\n$bullet; Any boulders that remain when Bael'Gar casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462972|h[Shatter]|h|r have the potential to make its damage lethal.\n\n$bullet; When a boulder is destroyed several Spawns of Bael'Gar will be created and attack nearby players.",-1,0,0,2,2664,30735,3,30732,0},
    {30735,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Tanks will need to split the damage of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462974|h[Giant Strike]|h|r in order to survive.\n\n$bullet; The large boulders created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:463890|h[Rockfall]|h|r inflict higher damage the nearer players are to the point of impact.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:463143|h[Molten Furnace]|h|r inflicts lethal damage to players that are not behind cover.\n\n$bullet; Any boulders that remain when Bael'Gar casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462972|h[Shatter]|h|r have the potential to make its damage lethal.\n\n$bullet; When Spawns of Bael'Gar are killed they will deal damage over time to a random player with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:462968|h[Molten Heart]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,2664,0,4,30732,0},
    {30736,"Section 5",0,2,462974,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,1,2664,30737,5,0,0},
    {30737,"Section 6",0,2,463890,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,30947,0,32,2664,30738,6,0,0},
