    {30943,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Big M.O.M.M.A. will |cFF2959D3|Hspell:460156|h[Jumpstart]|h|r after all Darkfuse Mechadrones are defeated.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:460156|h[Jumpstart]|h|r inflicts significant damage to all players.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:473220|h[Sonic Boom]|h|r continues until it collides with an obstacle.",-1,0,0,4,2648,0,4,30319,0},
    {30944,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Big M.O.M.M.A. will |cFF2959D3|Hspell:460156|h[Jumpstart]|h|r after all Darkfuse Mechadrones are defeated.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:460156|h[Jumpstart]|h|r leaves behind an area of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:473287|h[Excessive Electrification]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:473220|h[Sonic Boom]|h|r continues until it collides with an obstacle.",-1,0,0,1,2648,30945,2,30319,0},
    {30945,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Big M.O.M.M.A. will |cFF2959D3|Hspell:460156|h[Jumpstart]|h|r after all Darkfuse Mechadrones are defeated.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:460156|h[Jumpstart]|h|r causes Big M.O.M.M.A. to take significantly increased damage.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:473220|h[Sonic Boom]|h|r continues until it collides with an obstacle.",-1,0,0,2,2648,30943,3,30319,0},
