    {30949,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Ticking Time Bombs created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:460867|h[Big Bada BOOM!]|h|r inflict heavy damage to all players if allowed to expire.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:459779|h[Barreling Charge]|h|r causes Bront to run through any objects in his path, including Ticking Time Bombs created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:460867|h[Big Bada BOOM!]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;$[8,23|cFF2959D3|Hspell:473690|h[Kinetic Explosive Gel]|h|r knocks up Ticking Time Bombs nearby when dispelled.$]",-1,0,0,2,2649,0,4,30320,0},
