    {31101,"Overview",0,3,0,1,{"wago"},"Rik Reverb places entrancing amplifiers around the yard during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:473748|h[Amplification]|h|r. Upon reaching full power, the amplifiers go |cFF2959D3|Hspell:466093|h[Haywire]|h|r.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, Rik unleashes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:467991|h[Blaring Drops]|h|r from his sonic resonator and causes each amplifier to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:466722|h[Blowout]|h|r.",-1,31102,0,0,2641,31656,1,0,0},
    {31102,"Tanks",0,3,0,1,{"wago"},"$bullet; Rik |cFF2959D3|Hspell:466128|h[Resonates]|h|r additional power to nearby amplifiers. \n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:464488|h[Sonic Blast]|h|r inflicts Sonic damage in a frontal cone and applies |cFF2959D3|Hspell:464518|h[Tinnitus]|h|r. Sonic damage cannot be blocked or reduced by Armor.\n\n$bullet; Amplifier |cFF2959D3|Hspell:466722|h[Blowouts]|h|r knock players into the air as Rik generates deadly |cFF2959D3|Hspell:467991|h[Blaring Drops]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2641,31103,2,31101,0},
    {31103,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,1,{"wago"},"$bullet; Activating amplifiers drains their energy but applies |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217122|h[Lingering Voltage]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Rik gains a nullifying |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1213817|h[Sound Cloud]|h|r in Stage Two.\n\n$bullet; Amplifier |cFF2959D3|Hspell:466722|h[Blowouts]|h|r  knock players into the air as Rik generates deadly |cFF2959D3|Hspell:467991|h[Blaring Drops]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2641,31104,3,31101,0},
    {31104,"Healers",0,3,0,1,{"wago"},"$bullet; Activating amplifiers drains their energy but applies |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217122|h[Lingering Voltage]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:467044|h[Faulty Zap]|h|r inflicts damage to nearby players. \n\n$bullet; Amplifier |cFF2959D3|Hspell:466722|h[Blowouts]|h|r  knock players into the air as Rik generates deadly |cFF2959D3|Hspell:467991|h[Blaring Drops]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,2641,0,4,31101,0},
