    {31132,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,3,{"wago"},"$bullet;  Kul'tharok rips souls from players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:473959|h[Draw Soul]|h|r. If the souls reach Kul'tharok, he infuses them with necrotic energy, causes|cFF2959D3|Hspell:474013|h[Soul Corruption]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216474|h[Death Spiral]|h|r creates revolving necromancy orb that inflicts Shadow damage to players on contact.",0,0,0,2,2389,31339,3,21515,0},
