    {31220,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Azhiccar bombards players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217436|h[Toxic Regurgitation]|h|r and periodically calls forth an invasion of Frenzied Mites that |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217381|h[Engorge]|h|r themselves on players.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, Azhiccar attempts to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217232|h[Devour]|h|r all players and creatures, healing and becoming stronger with every living creature consumed.",-1,31221,0,0,2675,32688,1,0,0},
    {31221,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217327|h[Invading Shriek]|h|r calls forth Frenzied Mites that fixate on random players and fly between them wildly.\n\n$bullet;Azhiccar uses |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217232|h[Devour]|h|r to draw in living players and Frenzied Mites and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217241|h[Feast]|h|r on them.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217241|h[Feast]|h|r causes Azhiccar to heal and inflict increased damage for every player or creature consumed.",-1,0,0,1,2675,31222,2,31220,0},
    {31222,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217327|h[Invading Shriek]|h|r calls forth Frenzied Mites that fixate on random players and fly between them wildly.\n\n$bullet;Azhiccar uses |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217232|h[Devour]|h|r to draw in living players and Frenzied Mites and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217241|h[Feast]|h|r on them.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217241|h[Feast]|h|r causes Azhiccar to heal and inflict increased damage for every player or creature consumed.",-1,0,0,2,2675,31223,3,31220,0},
    {31223,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217436|h[Toxic Regurgitation]|h|r inflicts Shadow damage to afflicted players.\n\n$bullet;Azhiccar uses |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217232|h[Devour]|h|r to draw in living players and Frenzied Mites and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217241|h[Feast]|h|r on them.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217241|h[Feast]|h|r causes Azhiccar to heal and inflict increased damage for every player or creature consumed.",-1,0,0,4,2675,0,4,31220,0},
    {31224,"Stage One: <PH>",0,2,1217232,3,{"wago"},"$[!8,23,\n\n\n\nOn Mythic difficulty, Frenzied Mites are called when Devour begins.$]",0,31378,0,4128,2675,31406,7,0,0},
    {31227,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Taah'bat begins the encounter mounted on A'wazj, launching attacks  in a coordinated effort.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, Taah'bat dismounts A'wazj and begins |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1219700|h[Arcane Blitz]|h|r. Upon breaking all applications of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1219457|h[Incorporeal]|h|r, both Taah'bat and A'wazj become |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1219731|h[Destabilized]|h|r and return to fight as one.",-1,31228,0,0,2676,31232,1,0,0},
    {31228,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Striking Taah'bat with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1220384|h[Warp Strike]|h|r during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1219700|h[Arcane Blitz]|h|r removes an application of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1219457|h[Incorporeal]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1219482|h[Rift Claws]|h|r inflicts high Arcane damage to the target and causes them to bleed.",-1,0,0,1,2676,31229,2,31227,0},
    {31229,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Striking Taah'bat with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1220384|h[Warp Strike]|h|r during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1219700|h[Arcane Blitz]|h|r removes an application of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1219457|h[Incorporeal]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1219536|h[Binding Javelin]|h|r inflicts stacking damage to affected players until defeated.",-1,0,0,2,2676,31230,3,31227,0},
    {31230,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Striking Taah'bat with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1220384|h[Warp Strike]|h|r during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1219700|h[Arcane Blitz]|h|r removes an application of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1219457|h[Incorporeal]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1220497|h[Arcane Overload]|h|r inflicts Arcane damage to all players.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1219536|h[Binding Javelin]|h|r inflicts stacking damage to affected players until defeated.",-1,0,0,4,2676,0,4,31227,0},
    {31231,"Taah'bat",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,31551,123825,0,2676,31585,7,31584,0},
    {31232,"Section 7",0,2,1219417,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,2,2676,31584,5,0,0},
    {31234,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Soul-Scribe uses |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224793|h[Whispers of Fate]|h|r to create echoes of players' Fates. Soul-Scribe casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1225162|h[Ceremonial Dagger]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1225218|h[Dread of the Unknown]|h|r in an attempt to harm the Fates.  \n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, Soul-Scribe casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1236703|h[Eternal Weave]|h|r.",-1,31235,0,0,2677,31238,1,0,0},
    {31235,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;When a player's Fate is struck by Soul-Scribe's abilities the player bound to that Fate is afflicted with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226444|h[Wounded Fate]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1225218|h[Dread of the Unknown]|h|r inflicts heavy Arcane damage to players and Fates within the detonation.",-1,0,0,1,2677,31236,2,31234,0},
    {31236,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;When a player's Fate is struck by Soul-Scribe's abilities the player bound to that Fate is afflicted with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226444|h[Wounded Fate]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1225218|h[Dread of the Unknown]|h|r inflicts heavy Arcane damage to players and Fates within the detonation.",-1,0,0,2,2677,31237,3,31234,0},
    {31237,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;When a player's Fate is struck by Soul-Scribe's abilities the player bound to that Fate is afflicted with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226444|h[Wounded Fate]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1225218|h[Dread of the Unknown]|h|r inflicts heavy Arcane damage to players and Fates within the detonation.",-1,0,0,4,2677,0,4,31234,0},
