    {31278,"Section 11",0,2,1280113,0,{"wago"},"$[!23\n\n\n\nIn Mythic difficulty, |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1280113|h[Hulking Fragment]|h|r embeds |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1284627|h[Umbral Splinters]|h|r into the target.$]",-1,35306,0,1,2662,34556,10,0,0},
    {31279,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Kystia Manaheart is accompanied by her pet mana wyrm Nibbles, who is controlled by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1230289|h[Illicit Infusion]|h|r. When this infusion is removed, Nibbles breaks free of Kystia's control and reverts back to her light form to assist players in battle with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1230304|h[Light Infusion]|h|r.",-1,31280,0,0,2679,34458,1,0,0},
    {31280,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Kystia turns Nibbles hostile to players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1230289|h[Illicit Infusion]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Avoid Nibbles' |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253811|h[Fel Spray]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Interrupt Kystia's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264095|h[Mirror Images]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2679,31281,2,31279,0},
    {31281,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Kystia turns Nibbles hostile to players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1230289|h[Illicit Infusion]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Avoid Nibbles' |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253811|h[Fel Spray]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Kystia inflicts heavy damage to all players while |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265412|h[Destabilized]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,2679,31282,3,31279,0},
    {31282,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Kystia turns Nibbles hostile to players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1230289|h[Illicit Infusion]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Avoid Nibbles' |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253811|h[Fel Spray]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Interrupt Kystia's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264095|h[Mirror Images]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2679,0,4,31279,0},
    {31285,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Zaen Bladesorrow demonstrates how this town got its name by occassionally casting |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1218347|h[Murder in a Row]|h|r at all players. Dodge his deadly aim by taking cover to avoid heavy damage.",-1,31286,0,0,2680,31525,1,0,0},
    {31286,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; At 100 energy, Zaen casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1218347|h[Murder in a Row]|h|r. Get to cover!\n\n$bullet; Avoid damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:474765|h[Same-Day Delivery]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214357|h[Fire Bomb]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2680,31287,2,31285,0},
    {31287,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; At 100 energy, Zaen casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1218347|h[Murder in a Row]|h|r. Get to cover!\n\n$bullet; Avoid damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:474765|h[Same-Day Delivery]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214357|h[Fire Bomb]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,2680,31288,3,31285,0},
    {31288,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; At 100 energy, Zaen casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1218347|h[Murder in a Row]|h|r. Get to cover!\n\n$bullet; Avoid damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:474765|h[Same-Day Delivery]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214357|h[Fire Bomb]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Zaen inflicts heavy damage to his current target with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222795|h[Envenom]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2680,0,4,31285,0},
    {31289,"Section 6",0,2,474478,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2680,31531,10,0,0},
    {31292,"Section 12",0,2,1215897,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,34557,0,4,2662,31278,8,0,0},
    {31293,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Xathuux the Annihilator's rage increases until he erupts with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:474197|h[Demonic Rage]|h|r and gains |cFF2959D3|Hspell:474231|h[Burning Steps]|h|r.",-1,31294,0,0,2681,31298,1,0,0},
    {31294,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:474231|h[Burning Steps]|h|r leaves damaging pools of fel magic on the ground for a long duration.\n\n\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214637|h[Axe Toss]|h|r targets a random player and applies |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214650  |h[Fel Lightning]|h|r to all players until the axe is destroyed.",-1,0,0,2,2681,31296,2,31293,0},
    {31295,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:473898|h[Legion Strike]|h|r inflicts heavy Physical damage and reduces incoming healing.\n\n\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:474231|h[Burning Steps]|h|r creates damaging pools of fel magic that expand from Xathuux the Annihilator's location and remain on the ground for a long duration.",-1,0,0,1,2681,0,4,31293,0},
    {31296,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:473898|h[Legion Strike]|h|r inflicts heavy Physical damage and reduces incoming healing.\n\n\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214637|h[Axe Toss]|h|r targets a random player and applies |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214650  |h[Fel Lightning]|h|r to all players until the axe is destroyed.",-1,0,0,4,2681,31295,3,31293,0},
    {31297,"Axe Toss",0,2,1214663,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,32026,0,0,2681,31521,7,0,0},
    {31298,"Section 6",0,2,474197,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,31301,0,0,2681,31297,5,0,0},
    {31301,"Section 9",0,2,474234,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,32,2681,0,6,31298,0},
    {31303,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"|cFF2959D3|Hspell:474462|h[Fingers of Gul'dan]|h|r will summon Wild Imps near every target.\n\n\n\nAfter casting |cFF2959D3|Hspell:474462|h[Fingers of Gul'dan]|h|r Lithiel Cinderfury casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214675|h[Demonic Gateway]|h|r to escape and then begins casting |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217345|h[Malefic Wave]|h|r.\n\n\n\n|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217345|h[Malefic Wave]|h|r slowly expands over a large area inflicts heavy damage along with lingering damage over time.\n\n\n\nPlayers traveling through Lithiel's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214675|h[Demonic Gateway]|h|r are immune to the initial impact and lingering Fire vulnerability from passing through |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217345|h[Malefic Wave]|h|r.",-1,31304,0,0,2682,31441,1,0,0},
    {31304,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217345|h[Malefic Wave]|h|r grants |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226469|h[Malefic Empowerment]|h|r to any summoned demons still alive when it passes over them.\n\n\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:474375|h[Chaos Bolt]|h|r inflicts high damage to a random target if not interrupted.",-1,0,0,2,2682,31305,2,31303,0},
    {31305,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:474375|h[Chaos Bolt]|h|r inflicts high damage to a random target if not interrupted.\n\n\n\n$bullet;Furious Vilefiend inflicts heavy damage.",-1,0,0,1,2682,31306,3,31303,0},
    {31306,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217345|h[Malefic Wave]|h|r  applies lingering damage over time when players using Lithiel's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214675|h[Demonic Gateway]|h|r pass through |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217345|h[Malefic Wave]|h|r.\n\n\n\n$bullet;Furious Vilefiend inflicts heavy damage.",-1,0,0,4,2682,0,4,31303,0},
