    {31346,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The Gobfather won't go down without a final fight, scattering Primed Boomcrawlers with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216505|h[Bombfield]|h|r and knocking back players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216812|h[Giga-Rocket Slam]|h|r.\n\n\n\nAt 100 energy it pulls out all the stops, raining down |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216709|h[Death From Above]|h|r.",-1,31347,0,0,2683,31350,1,0,0},
    {31347,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Primed Boomcrawlers explode with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216577|h[Bomb Voyage]|h|r when stepped on.\n\n$bullet;The Gobfather inflicts massive damage with its |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216709|h[Death From Above]|h|r  missiles.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216687|h[Flaming Flames]|h|r inflicts damage to players in front of The Gobfather.",-1,0,0,1,2683,31349,2,31346,0},
    {31348,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Primed Boomcrawlers explode with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216577|h[Bomb Voyage]|h|r when stepped on.\n\n$bullet;The Gobfather inflicts massive damage with its |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216709|h[Death From Above]|h|r  missiles.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216687|h[Flaming Flames]|h|r inflicts damage to players in front of The Gobfather.",-1,0,0,2,2683,0,4,31346,0},
    {31349,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Primed Boomcrawlers explode with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216577|h[Bomb Voyage]|h|r when stepped on.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216656|h[Excessive Pollutants]|h|r continually inflicts damage to all players.\n\n$bullet;The Gobfather inflicts massive damage with its |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216709|h[Death From Above]|h|r  missiles.",-1,0,0,4,2683,31348,3,31346,0},
