    {31366,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Swampface ravages the tank with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:469478|h[Sludge Claws]|h|r and rains a ruinous |cFF2959D3|Hspell:473112|h[Mudslide]|h|r from above.\n\n\n\n|cFF2959D3|Hspell:473070|h[Awaken the Swamp]|h|r causes eruptions from the earth and a chaos of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:473052|h[Rushing Tides]|h|r that sweep players away.",-1,31782,0,0,2650,31079,1,0,0},
    {31368,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:470039|h[Razorchoke Vines]|h|r yank players together when too far apart.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:473112|h[Mudslide]|h|r  inflicts heavy damage in a massive line.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:473052|h[Rushing Tides]|h|r inflict damage and sweep away players caught inside.",0,0,0,2,2650,31784,4,31366,0},
    {31369,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:470039|h[Razorchoke Vines]|h|r yank players together when too far apart.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:473112|h[Mudslide]|h|r  inflicts heavy damage in a massive line.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:473052|h[Rushing Tides]|h|r inflict damage and sweep away players caught inside.",0,0,0,4,2650,0,6,31366,0},
    {31370,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet; Stormrider Vokmar's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:458082|h[Stormrider's Charge]|h|r destroys nearby Voidstone Fragments.\n\n$bullet; Shattering |cFF2959D3|Hspell:445262|h[Void Shell]|h|r allows Stormrider Vokmar's to strike with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:424371|h[Storm's Vengeance]|h|r",0,0,0,2,2568,31371,5,27558,0},
    {31371,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet; Stormrider Vokmar's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:458082|h[Stormrider's Charge]|h|r destroys nearby Voidstone Fragments.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:429487|h[Unleash Corruption]|h|r inflicts moderate Shadow damage to players and creates a pool of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:433067|h[Seeping Corruption]|h|r when removed.\n\n$bullet; Voidstone Awakened inflict increasing damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:429029|h[Corruption Overload]|h|r.",0,0,0,2,2568,31372,6,27558,0},
    {31372,"Tanks",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:445457|h[Oblivion Wave]|h|r inflicts Shadow damage to players in its path.\n\n$bullet; The Monstrosity irradiates all players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:423393|h[Entropy]|h|r while no players are in melee range.",0,0,0,2,2568,0,7,27558,0},
