    {31552,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Latch's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:472795|h[Heaving Yank]|h|r interrupts and pulls in the first target it hits.\n\n$bullet;Kalis's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:474105|h[Curse of Darkness]|h|r causes Dark Entities to fixate upon players.",0,0,0,2,2656,30461,3,30459,0},
    {31554,"Section 18",0,2,1219551,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,2,2656,30463,6,0,0},
    {31555,"Tanks",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Defeated Geargrinder Bikers surrender their bikes, allowing for |cFF2959D3|Hspell:459453|h[Blaze of Glory]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Vexie's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:460116|h[Tune-Up]|h|r and Pit Mechanics' |cFF2959D3|Hspell:460153|h[Repair]|h|r the Geargrinder's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:466615|h[Protective Plating]|h|r.",0,0,0,1,2639,30090,2,30089,0},
