    {31558,"Intermission: Docked and Loaded",0,0,0,2,{"wago"},"Upon reaching 50% health Gallywix drops into the arena |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214226|h[Cratering]|h|r any in his way, gaining |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214229|h[Armageddon-class Plating]|h|r and then casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214369|h[Total Destruction!!!]|h|r until interrupted.",0,31559,0,0,2646,31445,66,0,0},
    {31559,"Section 75",0,2,1214226,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,16,2646,31560,67,31558,0},
    {31560,"Section 76",0,2,1214229,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2646,31561,68,31558,0},
    {31561,"Section 137",0,2,1219319,3,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,8,2646,31562,69,31558,0},
    {31562,"Section 136",0,2,1219278,3,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,4128,2646,31563,70,31558,0},
    {31563,"Section 77",0,2,1214369,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,96,2646,0,71,31558,0},
    {31569,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The Nexus-King readies his mace to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224787|h[Conquer]|h|r armies as images of the Royal Voidwing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1225010|h[Behead]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1225016|h[Besiege]|h|r insurgents at his command. Those who lack zeal are destined for servitude when Salhadaar |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224906|h[Invokes the Oath]|h|r.\n\n\n\nBy regal edict, |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224764|h[Oath-Breakers]|h|r are devoured between cosmic jaws and razed to atoms by the Royal Voidwing's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1228163|h[Dimension Breath]|h|r. Salhadaar governs the battle from atop his steed, rallying elite Shadowguard reinforcements.\n\n\n\nWhen |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1228265|h[King's Hunger]|h|r takes reign, Salhadaar's loyal drake is called upon for ultimate sacrifice. Violet skies blacken and galaxies of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248137|h[Dark Stars]|h|r form at the strike of a gavel as the Nexus-King plunges the world into twilight.",-1,31570,0,0,2690,31573,1,0,0},
    {31570,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Salhadaar executes a combination of deadly attacks during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224776|h[Subjugation Rule]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234529|h[Cosmic Maw]|h|r increases damage taken by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1228163|h[Dimension Breath]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Salhadaar's primary targets of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1225319|h[Galactic Smash]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226024|h[Starkiller Swing]|h|r are |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226417|h[Starshattered]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2690,32623,2,31569,0},
    {31572,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224737|h[Oath-Bound]|h|r players are vulnerable to conversion into |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1224767|h[King's Thrall]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227529|h[Banishment]|h|r, |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1228053|h[Reap]|h|r, and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226362|h[Twilight Scar]|h|r inflict heavy damage over time to affected players.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226024|h[Starkiller Swing]|h|r erupts in a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226042|h[Starkiller Nova]|h|r unless consumed by a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248137|h[Dark Star]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,2690,0,4,31569,0},
    {31573,"Stage One: Oath-Breakers",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"Salhadaar forces players under oath and tests their will against the void.",-1,32227,0,0,2690,31574,5,0,0},
    {31574,"Stage Two: Rider of the Dark",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"Salhadaar orders the draconic images to converge back into one as he takes his rightful seat atop the Royal Voidwing.",-1,32268,0,0,2690,32631,27,0,0},
    {31575,"Stage Three: World in Twilight",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"Salhadaar stands alone as the final champion of the Void Lord's return.",-1,32034,0,0,2690,0,71,0,0},
