    {31594,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217649|h[Arcanomatrix Atomizer]|h|r will |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1219223|h[Atomize]|h|r all beings not made of energy who come into contact with it.\n\n\n\nThe Plexus Sentinel will continue to gain energy while attacking players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1219263|h[Obliteration Arcanocannon]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1219532|h[Eradicating Salvo]|h|r\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 Energy, the Plexus Sentinel begins channelling |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1220489|h[Protocol: Purge]|h|r as it activates the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217649|h[Arcanomatrix Atomizer]|h|r",-1,31981,0,0,2684,31625,1,0,0},
