    {31778,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217083|h[Foot-Blasters]|h|r cause an |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216406|h[Unstable Explosion]|h|r that increases damage taken by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216406|h[Unstable Explosion]|h|r for a short duration.\n\n$bullet;Players designated as |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216508|h[Screw Ups]|h|r periodically drop drills at their location.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:466235|h[Wire Transfer]|h|r inflicts significant damage to players standing within the effect",0,0,0,2,2653,32939,4,30421,0},
    {31779,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:465232|h[Sonic Ba-Boom]|h|r applies a damage over time effect to all players.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217083|h[Foot-Blasters]|h|r cause an |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216406|h[Unstable Explosion]|h|r that increases damage taken by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216406|h[Unstable Explosion]|h|r for a short duration.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1218319|h[Voidsplosion]|h|r inflicts significant damage to all players and absorbs healing taken.",0,0,0,4,2653,30424,7,30421,0},
    {31780,"Tanks",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Each application of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:465917|h[Gravi-Gunk]|h|r increases all damage taken.\n\n$bullet;The damage of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1214872|h[Pyro Party Pack]|h|r is reduced the further the target is from other players.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1217083|h[Foot-Blasters]|h|r cause an |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216406|h[Unstable Explosion]|h|r that increases damage taken by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1216406|h[Unstable Explosion]|h|r for a short duration.",0,0,0,1,2653,30422,2,30421,0},
    {31781,"Section 11",0,2,468846,2,{"wago"},nil,3,0,0,0,2651,30798,11,0,0},
    {31782,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:469478|h[Sludge Claws]|h|r inflict massive damage and cause healing to be absorbed.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:473112|h[Mudslide]|h|r  inflicts heavy damage in a massive line.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:473052|h[Rushing Tides]|h|r inflict damage and sweep away players caught inside.",-1,0,0,1,2650,31783,2,31366,0},
    {31783,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:473112|h[Mudslide]|h|r  inflicts heavy damage in a massive line.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:473052|h[Rushing Tides]|h|r inflict damage and sweep away players caught inside.",3,0,0,2,2650,31368,3,31366,0},
    {31784,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:473112|h[Mudslide]|h|r  inflicts heavy damage in a massive line.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:473052|h[Rushing Tides]|h|r inflict damage and sweep away players caught inside.",3,0,0,4,2650,31369,5,31366,0},
    {31785,"Section 35",0,2,472294,2,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,16,2641,31155,27,31154,0},
    {31786,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Adarus tears open a rift to the void and brands players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222232|h[Devourer's Ire]|h|r. Adarus will focus his assault on the players bearing this mark.\n\n\n\nVelaryn singes any who stand in her path with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1218103|h[Eye Beam]|h|r and lunges towards her prey with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227809|h[The Hunt]|h|r.\n\n\n\nIlyssa cleaves her target's essence with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241833|h[Fracture]|h|r and feasts on their rended soul with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1242259|h[Spirit Bomb]|h|r.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 Fury, the Demon Hunters unleash their true power and enter |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1228381|h[Metamorphosis]|h|r.",-1,31787,0,0,2688,32567,1,0,0},
    {31787,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1218103|h[Eye Beam]|h|r singes Velaryn's current target with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1221490|h[Fel-Singed]|h|r and blasts them away.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241833|h[Fracture]|h|r cleaves their target's soul into fragments which Ilyssa will attempt to consume with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1242259|h[Spirit Bomb]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Adarus will |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227355|h[Voidstep]|h|r to new locations, summoning images which slice open the fabric of the void with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227685|h[Hungering Slash]|h|r and leave behind |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235045|h[Encroaching Oblivion]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2688,31788,2,31786,0},
    {31788,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Adarus continually casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234565|h[Consume]|h|r at the players bearing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222232|h[Devourer's Ire]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241833|h[Fracture]|h|r cleaves their target's soul into fragments which Ilyssa will attempt to consume with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1242259|h[Spirit Bomb]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Adarus will |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227355|h[Voidstep]|h|r to new locations, summoning images which slice open the fabric of the void with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227685|h[Hungering Slash]|h|r and leave behind |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235045|h[Encroaching Oblivion]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2688,31789,3,31786,0},
    {31789,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Adarus continually casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234565|h[Consume]|h|r at the players bearing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222232|h[Devourer's Ire]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241833|h[Fracture]|h|r cleaves their target's soul into fragments which Ilyssa will attempt to consume with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1242259|h[Spirit Bomb]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Adarus will |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227355|h[Voidstep]|h|r to new locations, summoning images which slice open the fabric of the void with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227685|h[Hungering Slash]|h|r and leave behind |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235045|h[Encroaching Oblivion]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,2688,0,4,31786,0},
