    {32156,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Belo'ren guards the Sunwell with both Light and Void magic. His |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1242515|h[Voidlight Convergence]|h|r infuses players with either Light or Void, protecting them from one while leaving them vulnerable to the other.\n\n\n\nWhen his health is depleted, Belo'ren retreats into an ashen egg and begins to cast |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241313|h[Rebirth]|h|r. Players must damage Belo'ren to diminish his |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243320|h[Immortal Flame]|h|r before he is reborn anew.",-1,32157,0,0,2739,33025,1,0,0},
    {32157,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241162|h[Light Feather]|h|r reduces incoming Holy damage. |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241163|h[Void Feather]|h|r reduces incoming Shadow damage.\n\n$bullet; Damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241292|h[Light Dive]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241339|h[Void Dive]|h|r is split evenly between all players hit.",-1,0,0,0,2739,32158,2,32156,0},
    {32158,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241162|h[Light Feather]|h|r reduces incoming Holy damage. |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241163|h[Void Feather]|h|r reduces incoming Shadow damage.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244348|h[Light Burn]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1266404|h[Void Burn]|h|r absorb significant healing and inflict damage over time until fully healed.",-1,0,0,0,2739,32159,3,32156,0},
    {32159,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241162|h[Light Feather]|h|r reduces incoming Holy damage. |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241163|h[Void Feather]|h|r reduces incoming Shadow damage.\n\n$bullet; Failing to hit a player with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1260763|h[Guardian's Edict]|h|r empowers Belo'ren, significantly increasing his damage.",-1,0,0,0,2739,0,4,32156,0},
    {32160,"Stage Two: Ashen Shell",7636699,1,0,1,{"wago"},"As Belo'ren falls he retreats into an ashen egg and kindles the fire of rebirth.",-1,33005,130080,0,2739,0,39,0,1284},
    {32161,"Section 31",0,2,1226417,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,1,2690,0,82,32034,0},
    {32162,"Section 32",0,2,1226417,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,1,2690,0,86,32150,0},
    {32163,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The Dark Naaru counts down the minutes with each harrowing toll of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244412|h[Death's Dirge]|h|r that echoes off the sacred walls. |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253915|h[Heaven's Glaives]|h|r rip and tear through the armies of light as L'ura conducts the infinite power held within |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1282027|h[The Darkwell]|h|r to extinguish all that is holy.\n\n\n\nWhen |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1266622|h[Midnight]|h|r falls and Azeroth descends into darkness, brave |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1266627|h[Torchbearers]|h|r emerge from the shadows to face |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1250898|h[The Dark Archangel]|h|r and fight to see another sunrise.",-1,32164,0,0,2740,32197,1,0,0},
    {32164,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Midnight Crystals undergo |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251807|h[Cosmic Fracture]|h|r if not destroyed in time.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244412|h[Death's Dirge]|h|r displays |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1249609|h[Dark Runes]|h|r that correspond to the melody's notes.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1266627|h[Torchbearers]|h|r emit light to protect nearby allies from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1266622|h[Midnight]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2740,32165,2,32163,0},
    {32165,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1252974|h[Dimming]|h|r Dusk Crystals transform into Dawn Crystals upon reaching full health.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244412|h[Death's Dirge]|h|r displays |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1249609|h[Dark Runes]|h|r that correspond to the melody's notes.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1266627|h[Torchbearers]|h|r emit light to protect nearby allies from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1266622|h[Midnight]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,2740,32166,3,32163,0},
    {32166,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263970|h[Heaven's Lance]|h|r inflicts massive damage as the target is |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265842|h[Impaled]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244412|h[Death's Dirge]|h|r displays |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1249609|h[Dark Runes]|h|r that correspond to the melody's notes.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1266627|h[Torchbearers]|h|r emit light to protect nearby allies from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1266622|h[Midnight]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2740,0,4,32163,0},
    {32167,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Averzian uses |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251361|h[Shadow's Advance]|h|r to claim territory on the battlefield. Territory claimed cannot be retaken, and if Averzian claims three adjacent territories in a row he unleashes the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251583|h[March of the Endless]|h|r.\n\n\n\nCausing an |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1249262|h[Umbral Collapse]|h|r on a territory being taken prevents its capture.",-1,32168,0,0,2733,34566,1,0,0},
    {32168,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Abyssal Voidshapers attempt to use |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1255749|h[Gathering Darkness]|h|r at full power.\n\n$bullet; Shadowguard Stalwarts attempt to empower their allies with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1255702|h[Pitch Bulwark]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2733,32169,2,32167,0},
    {32169,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1249251|h[Dark Upheaval]|h|r inflicts periodic damage to all players.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1249262|h[Umbral Collapse]|h|r inflicts damage to everyone that is reduced by the number of players at the impact location.",-1,0,0,4,2733,32170,3,32167,0},
    {32170,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Averzian gains |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253918|h[Imperator's Glory]|h|r while close to territory he controls.\n\n$bullet; When Averzian strikes his current target he infects them with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265540|h[Blackening Wounds]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2733,0,4,32167,0},
    {32171,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Vorasius periodically strikes the ground with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244012|h[Shadowclaw Slam]|h|r, creating crystals that divide the battlefield. The behemoth then shakes off parasitic creeps that explode in a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1259184|h[Blisterburst]|h|r upon death.\n\n\n\nAs the battle rages, Vorasius sweeps his deadly |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241864|h[Void Breath]|h|r from one side of the battlefield to the other, decimating anything caught in its path.",-1,32172,0,0,2734,33252,1,0,0},
    {32172,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; The explosion of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1259184|h[Blisterburst]|h|r  is powerful enough to damage Void Crystals.\n\n\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244012|h[Shadowclaw Slam]|h|r causes reverberating |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1273067|h[Aftershocks]|h|r from its impact location.",-1,0,0,2,2734,32173,2,32171,0},
    {32173,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; The explosion of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1259184|h[Blisterburst]|h|r  is powerful enough to damage Void Crystals.\n\n\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1260046|h[Primordial Roar]|h|r causes Vorasius to gain more |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1272937|h[Primordial Power]|h|r with each cast.",-1,0,0,4,2734,32174,3,32171,0},
    {32174,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244012|h[Shadowclaw Slam]|h|r inflicts deadly damage to the raid if it fails to hit at least one player.\n\n\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244419|h[Overpowering Pulse]|h|r is triggered when no enemies are near Vorasius.",-1,0,0,1,2734,0,4,32171,0},
    {32175,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The dragon siblings begin battle alternating between flying and grounded combat, swapping after |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1249748|h[Midnight Flames]|h|r at full power. In response, the Lightbound Vanguard offer aid by providing their |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248847|h[Radiant Barrier]|h|r to nearby players.\n\n\n\nEventually, both dragons land, combining their draconic might to annihilate players once and for all.",-1,32176,0,0,2735,34394,1,0,0},
    {32176,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245391|h[Gloom]|h|r applies |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245554|h[Gloomtouched]|h|r upon contact and shrinks the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245420|h[Gloomfield]|h|r formed.\n\n$[15,16$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262623|h[Nullbeam]|h|r creates a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244672|h[Nullzone]|h|r tethering players, causing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244413|h[Nullsnap]|h|r or |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1252157|h[Nullzone Implosion]|h|r when stretching the tether.$]\n\n$[14,17$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262623|h[Nullbeam]|h|r creates a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244672|h[Nullzone]|h|r tethering players, causing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244413|h[Nullsnap]|h|r when stretching the tether.$]\n\n$[14,15,16$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244221|h[Dread Breath]|h|r targets a player but affects all players in front of Vaelgor.$]\n\n$[17$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244917|h[Void Howl]|h|r summons Voidorbs which continually cast |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245175|h[Voidbolt]|h|r.$]\n\n$[14,15,16$bullet;Manifestation of Midnight's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1270497|h[Shadowmark]|h|r detonates upon expiration.$]",-1,0,0,2,2735,32177,2,32175,0},
    {32177,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$[14,17$bullet;Stretching |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244672|h[Nullzone]|h|r's tether triggers |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244413|h[Nullsnap]|h|r, inflicting damage to all players.$]\n\n$[15,16$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244672|h[Nullzone]|h|r's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244413|h[Nullsnap]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1252157|h[Nullzone Implosion]|h|r inflict damage to all players, but |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1252157|h[Nullzone Implosion]|h|r also applies a short duration high intensity damage over time effect.$]\n\n$bullet;The Lightbound Vanguard grant |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248847|h[Radiant Barrier]|h|r to players nearby, reducing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1249748|h[Midnight Flames]|h|r' high damage.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245554|h[Gloomtouched]|h|r players decrease the total damage inflicted by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245391|h[Gloom]|h|r and shrink the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245420|h[Gloomfield]|h|r formed.",-1,0,0,4,2735,32178,3,32175,0},
    {32178,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$[14,15,17$bullet;Both |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262623|h[Nullbeam]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245391|h[Gloom]|h|r orient in the direction of the dragon's primary target, as well as |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244221|h[Dread Breath]|h|r while flying.$]\n\n$[16$bullet;Both |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262623|h[Nullbeam]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245391|h[Gloom]|h|r orient in the direction of the dragon's current target.$]\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245645|h[Rakfang]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1265131|h[Vaelwing]|h|r empower the dragon when cast at the same target.\n\n$bullet;Receiving |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262623|h[Nullbeam]|h|r stacks decrease the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1244672|h[Nullzone]|h|r's pull magnitude for all players.\n\n$[14,15,17$bullet;While flying, |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1280458|h[Grappling Maw]|h|r pulls the dragon's primary target and inflicts increasing damage as their distance increases.$]",-1,0,0,1,2735,0,4,32175,0},
    {32179,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Fallen-King Salhadaar is infused with power from the surrounding machinery, slowly increasing his energy over time. Upon reaching 100 energy, he is overwhelmed by the Void and begins his |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1246175|h[Entropic Unraveling]|h|r. \n\n\n\nPeriodically, the Riftlabs produce orbs of Concentrated Void that are drawn toward Salhadaar. When an orb of Concentrated Void reaches him, he performs a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245960|h[Void Infusion]|h|r.",-1,32180,0,0,2736,35214,1,0,0},
    {32180,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Orbs of Concentrated Void cause a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245960|h[Void Infusion]|h|r when they reach Salhadaar.\n\n$bullet; Salhadaar takes increased damage during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1246175|h[Entropic Unraveling]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Salhadaar creates several Fractured Images that cast |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1254088|h[Shadow Fracture]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2736,32181,2,32179,0},
    {32181,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; When orbs of Concentrated Void are destroyed, they apply |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1250991|h[Dark Radiation]|h|r to all players.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248697|h[Despotic Command]|h|r inflicts periodic damage to nearby players and applies |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248709|h[Oppressive Darkness]|h|r when removed.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1246175|h[Entropic Unraveling]|h|r inflicts heavy periodic damage to all players.",-1,0,0,4,2736,32182,3,32179,0},
    {32182,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Orbs of Concentrated Void cause a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245960|h[Void Infusion]|h|r when they reach Salhadaar.\n\n$bullet; Spikes erupt from the target of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253032|h[Shattering Twilight]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Salhadaar's melee attacks apply |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1271577|h[Destabilizing Strikes]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2736,0,4,32179,0},
    {32183,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The Lightblinded Vanguard attacks players relentlessly as their energy slowly increases.\n\n\n\nWhen a member of the Vanguard reaches 100 energy, they activate an Aura to empower their allies and unleash their most devastating attack.",-1,32184,0,0,2737,34866,1,0,0},
    {32184,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; War Chaplain Senn protects allies within her |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248451|h[Aura of Peace]|h|r, pacifying any players who attack them.\n\n$bullet; Damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248983|h[Execution Sentence]|h|r is split evenly between all players hit.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248674|h[Sacred Shield]|h|r grants immunity to interrupt effects while the shield holds.",-1,0,0,2,2737,32185,2,32183,0},
    {32185,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248721|h[Tyr's Wrath]|h|r absorbs a large amount of healing done to affected players.\n\n$bullet; Damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248983|h[Execution Sentence]|h|r is split evenly between all players hit.\n\n$bullet; General Bellamy silences players struck by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248652|h[Divine Toll]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,2737,32186,3,32183,0},
    {32186,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1246736|h[Judgment]|h|r significantly increases damage taken from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251812|h[Final Verdict]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251859|h[Shield of the Righteous]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Damage from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248983|h[Execution Sentence]|h|r is split evenly between all players hit.\n\n$bullet; Members of the Vanguard with an active Aura greatly empower their nearby allies.",-1,0,0,1,2737,0,4,32183,0},
    {32187,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Alleria Windrunner begins the fight held back by Undying Sentinels from the Void. She periodically strikes out at friend and foe alike with both Void effects and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1233602|h[Silverstrike Arrow]|h|r. \n\n\n\nWhen each of the Undying Sentinels have been destroyed, Alleria crashes into the platform and creates a Rift Simulacrum to assault her enemies with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237837|h[Call of the Void]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237614|h[Ranger Captain's Mark]|h|r.\n\n\n\nWhen the Rift Simulacrum is shattered, Alleria releases her full Void abilities upon all players.",-1,32188,0,0,2738,32196,1,0,0},
    {32188,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1233602|h[Silverstrike Arrow]|h|r will remove any Void effects from targets struck.\n\n$bullet;Void Droplet will splash targets with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241520|h[Corrupting Essence]|h|r when it dies.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1239080|h[Aspect of the End]|h|r reduces healing received until the target moves away from the arrow.",-1,0,0,2,2738,32189,2,32187,0},
    {32189,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1233602|h[Silverstrike Arrow]|h|r will remove any Void effects from targets struck.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1233865|h[Null Corona]|h|r absorbs a large amount of healing and can be moved to another player when dispelled.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1239080|h[Aspect of the End]|h|r reduces healing received until the target moves away from the arrow.",-1,0,0,4,2738,33345,3,32187,0},
    {32190,"Tanks",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Undying Sentinels utilize |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1233778|h[Echoing Darkness]|h|r when no players are in melee combat.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237251|h[Empowering Darkness]|h|r affects Alleria's allies within a large area.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1239080|h[Aspect of the End]|h|r reduces healing received and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1239089|h[Gravity Collapse]|h|r leaves the target weak to Physical attacks.",0,0,0,1,2738,0,5,32187,0},
    {32191,"Stage One",0,2,1251361,2,{"wago"},"$[!16\n\n\n\nOn Mythic difficulty, Averzian summons the Abyssal Malus to join his army.",0,33962,0,4128,2733,33966,24,0,0},
    {32195,"General Amias Bellamy",0,1,0,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,33682,131501,0,2737,33681,28,0,0},
    {32196,"Stage One: The Voidspire",0,0,0,3,{"wago"},nil,0,32457,0,0,2738,32454,6,0,0},
    {32197,"Stage One: Final Tolls",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},"The clock ticks. The sun sets. The candle burns.",-1,33998,0,0,2740,35036,5,0,0},
    {32198,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Reshanor's throat surges with dark, twisted energy, unleashing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237893|h[Veilshatter Roars]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237905|h[Twilight Breaths]|h|r. His unstable presence conjures a raging |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226380|h[Voidstorm]|h|r.\n\n\n\nWhen his energy wanes, Reshanor retreats into Untethered Space to feed on arcane forces - tearing open reality and allowing void creatures to spill forth.",-1,32199,0,0,2762,32941,1,0,0},
    {32199,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237893|h[Veilshatter Roar]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to all players and interrupts those casting.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243941|h[Erratic Rifts]|h|r allow players to follow Reshanor into Untethered Space.\n\n$bullet; Players with high stacks of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237906|h[Void Corruption]|h|r require significant healing.",-1,0,0,4,2762,32200,2,32198,0},
    {32200,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237893|h[Veilshatter Roar]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to all players and interrupts those casting.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243941|h[Erratic Rifts]|h|r allow players to follow Reshanor into Untethered Space.\n\n$bullet; Void creatures are called during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237288|h[Untethered Retreat]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2762,32201,3,32198,0},
    {32201,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237893|h[Veilshatter Roar]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to all players and interrupts those casting.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243941|h[Erratic Rifts]|h|r allow players to follow Reshanor into Untethered Space.\n\n$bullet; Void creatures are called during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237288|h[Untethered Retreat]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2762,0,4,32198,0},
    {32202,nil,0,2,1226380,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,32203,0,0,2762,0,17,0,0},
    {32203,"Section 6",0,2,1226398,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2762,32204,18,32202,0},
    {32204,"Section 7",0,2,1226441,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2762,0,19,32202,0},
    {32205,"Section 30",0,2,1226493,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2688,33035,30,31927,0},
    {32207,"Section 29",0,2,1226384,2,{"wago"},"$[!16\n\nOn Mythic difficulty, the violent consumption of a Starkiller Nova causes the Dark Star to reverse orbit.$]",0,0,0,4096,2690,32036,77,32035,0},
    {32208,"Section 16",0,2,1224822,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,4,2690,0,20,32227,0},
    {32210,"Section 16",0,2,1224822,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,4,2690,0,31,32268,0},
    {32211,"Section 21",0,2,1225444,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,16,2690,32041,74,32035,0},
    {32216,"Section 17",0,2,1225616,0,{"wago"},"$[!16\n\n\n\nOn Mythic difficulties, The |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226827|h[Soulrend Orbs]|h|r can break the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1246530|h[Arcane Sigils]|h|r. $]",-1,33146,0,0,2685,32217,22,0,0},
    {32217,"Section 18",0,2,1240754,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,4,2685,32759,24,0,0},
    {32218,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Soulbinder Naazindhri activates the Binding Chambers throughout the room in order to create waves of Shadowguard. The destructive power of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227276|h[Soulfray Annihilation]|h|r can obliterate her enemies, but may disrupt her chambers' work if caught in its path.",-1,32219,0,0,2685,32043,1,0,0},
    {32219,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241100|h[Mystic Lash]|h|r inflicts significant damage to primary target and increases the damage they take.\n\n$bullet;After completing|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1239988|h[Soulweave Chrysalis]|h|r the Unbound Soul is transformed into a more dangerous Ethereal.",-1,0,0,1,2685,32220,2,32218,0},
    {32220,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227276|h[Soulfray Annihilation]|h|r can destroy all it touches, whether players or Binding Machines.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1225616|h[Soulfire Convergence]|h|r causes the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226827|h[Soulrend Orb ]|h|r to be violently expelled from the target player's body. If it strikes another player, it inflicts negative effects upon them.",-1,0,0,2,2685,32221,3,32218,0},
    {32221,"Healer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227048|h[Soulfray Annihilation]|h|r can destroy all it touches, whether players or Binding Machines.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241100|h[Mystic Lash]|h|r inflicts significant damage to primary target, and increase the damage they take.\n\n$bullet;The Binding Chamber causes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227848|h[Essence Implosion]|h|r while it is broken or opened, inflicting massive damage to all players.",-1,0,0,4,2685,0,4,32218,0},
    {32226,"Section 37",0,2,1227330,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2690,0,26,32228,0},
    {32227,"Nexus-King Salhadaar",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,33463,125691,0,2690,32228,6,31573,0},
    {32228,"The Royal Voidwing",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,32229,126889,0,2690,0,21,31573,0},
