    {32268,"Nexus-King Salhadaar",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,32294,125691,0,2690,32272,28,31574,0},
    {32269,"The Royal Voidwing",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,32333,126889,0,2690,0,69,32011,0},
    {32270,"Nexus-King Salhadaar",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,32332,125691,0,2690,32269,65,32011,0},
    {32271,"Section 16",0,2,1224822,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,4,2690,0,68,32270,0},
    {32272,"The Royal Voidwing",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,33466,126889,0,2690,0,32,31574,0},
    {32273,"Section 46",0,2,1238975,2,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,4096,2690,32014,15,32227,0},
    {32279,"Section 18",0,2,1227373,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,32280,0,32,2747,32483,19,0,0},
    {32280,"Section 19",0,2,1227378,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,32,2747,0,20,32279,0},
    {32283,"Section 1",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Loom'ithar traps enemies within its chamber with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237272|h[Lair Weaving]|h|r and unleashes infused arcane energy with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226395|h[Overinfusion Burst]|h|r. \n\n\n\nUpon reaching 50% health, Loom'ithar tears itself in two and attacks players directly with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227227|h[Writhing Wave]|h|r.",-1,32284,0,0,2686,32296,1,0,0},
    {32284,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227263|h[Piercing Strand]|h|r causes all targets hit to take increased damage from it for a duration.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227226|h[Writhing Wave]|h|r is split between all targets caught in its area.\n\n$bullet; Loom'ithar will give chase to their target while consumed with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1228059|h[Unbound Rage]|h|r",-1,0,0,1,2686,32285,2,32283,0},
    {32285,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Infused Tangles inflict heavy damage if players are caught in the collapsing ring of threads.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226315|h[Infusion Tether]|h|r will inflict damge indefinitely until the effect ends.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226366|h[Living Silk]|h|r inflicts heavy Nature damage and reduces movement speed.",-1,0,0,2,2686,32286,3,32283,0},
    {32286,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226315|h[Infusion Tether]|h|r must be pulled far away from Loom'ithar to end the effect.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226395|h[Overinfusion Burst]|h|r inflicts Arcane damage as it charges and a massive burst when it ends.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226366|h[Living Silk]|h|r inflicts heavy Nature damage and reduces movement speed.",-1,0,0,4,2686,0,4,32283,0},
    {32287,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Dimensius attempts to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1229038|h[Devour]|h|r players almost immediately, and again every time he reaches 100 energy. His |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1229674|h[Growing Hunger]|h|r increases with each cast, pushing the players' |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1228207|h[Collective Gravity]|h|r to its limits.\n\n\n\nWhen Dimensius' health is depleted, he pulls players into the Dark Heart where they must quickly fly with Xal'atath to safety. He releases his conquered rivals to halt players' advance and attempts to obliterate them with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1238765|h[Extinction]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237319|h[Gamma Burst]|h|r.\n\n\n\nAfter a devastating counter-attack from the players and Xal'atath, Dimensius begins to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1231716|h[Extinguish the Stars]|h|r. Upon reaching 100 energy he again attempts to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1233539|h[Devour]|h|r everything around him, pulling his |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1233292|h[Accretion Disk]|h|r ever closer.",-1,32288,0,0,2691,32292,1,0,0},
    {32288,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1230087|h[Massive Smash]|h|r knocks all players away from Dimensius' target.\n\n$bullet;Players who receive too many applications of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1246145|h[Touch of Oblivion]|h|r are killed instantly.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227659|h[Fists of the Voidlord]|h|r damages and knocks away players near Dimensius' target with every melee attack.",-1,0,0,1,2691,32289,2,32287,0},
    {32289,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Living Mass leaves behind |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1228206|h[Excess Mass]|h|r when defeated, which can be used to gain |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1228207|h[Collective Gravity]|h|r and rescue |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243609|h[Airborne]|h|r players.\n\n$bullet;Players can stand in |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243704|h[Antimatter]|h|r to reduce its raidwide damage.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227659|h[Fists of the Voidlord]|h|r damages and knocks away players near Dimensius' target with every melee attack.",-1,0,0,2,2691,32290,3,32287,0},
    {32290,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1229038|h[Devour]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1231716|h[Extinguish the Stars]|h|r inflict heavy damage to all players.\n\n$bullet;Players can stand in |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243704|h[Antimatter]|h|r to reduce its raidwide damage.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227659|h[Fists of the Voidlord]|h|r damages and knocks away players near Dimensius' target with every melee attack.",-1,0,0,4,2691,0,4,32287,0},
    {32291,"Section 5",0,2,1227665,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,1,2691,32336,33,32292,0},
