    {32297,"Section 5",0,2,1226395,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,16,2686,32721,14,32296,0},
    {32301,"Section 9",0,2,1227226,0,{"wago"},"$[!15,16\n\n\n\nOn Heroic and Mythic difficulties, affected players take $1227163s2% increased damage from Writhing Wave.$]",-1,33459,0,1,2686,0,26,32303,0},
    {32303,"Stage Two: The Beast Unbound",0,0,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,32354,0,0,2686,0,19,0,0},
    {32307,"Section 14",0,2,1227782,0,{"wago"},"$[!16 \n\n\n\nOn Mythic difficulty, when Arcane Outrage ends, players erupt with arcane energy inflicting $1243908s1 Arcane damage to themselves and allies within $1243908A1 yards.$]",-1,32531,0,0,2686,32301,24,32303,0},
    {32313,"Section 26",0,2,1246775,2,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,0,2685,0,18,33394,0},
    {32314,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The trio of Lightbloom rutaani work in tandem to sow and nurture a Lightblossom garden. Meittik creates |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234782|h[Fertile Loam]|h|r that is then planted by Lekshi's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234850|h[Lightsower Dash]|h|r. Kezkitt rapidly germinates the flora with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235564|h[Lightblossom Beam]|h|r until they burst in a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235751|h[Lightbloom Overgrowth]|h|r.",-1,34343,0,0,2769,33927,1,0,0},
    {32315,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Ikuzz entangles players in |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1236658|h[Bloodthorn Roots]|h|r to immobilize his prey. At 100 energy, he fixates on a player with a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237090|h[Bloodthirsty Gaze]|h|r and attempts to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237166|h[Incise]|h|r them.",-1,33031,0,0,2770,32727,1,0,0},
    {32316,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Lightwaden Ruia unleashes his druidic power, shapeshifting between Moonkin and Bear forms. At 40% remaining health, he returns to Haranir form and channels |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241067|h[Spirits of the Vale]|h|r, casting all his abilities in a rapid flurry.",-1,33028,0,0,2771,33012,1,0,0},
    {32317,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Ziekket will periodically |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1246372|h[Awaken the Lightbloom]|h|r, sprouting Lightspawn Lashers from the earth and awakening any |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1246379|h[Dormant]|h|r ones.\n\n\n\nSurging with the Light's power, Ziekket projects a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1246607|h[Concentrated Lightbeam]|h|r at players that annihilates flora and fauna alike.",-1,33193,0,0,2772,33186,1,0,0},
    {32325,"Section 54",0,2,1228163,2,{"wago"},"$[!16\n\nOn Mythic difficulty, Dimension Glare is applied to any player hit.$]",0,32589,0,4128,2690,32592,36,32272,0},
    {32332,"Section 56",0,2,1228265,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,32,2690,32488,66,32270,0},
