    {32665,"Rotten Mushroom",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},"This fungi grows for 12 seconds then detonates in a Putrid Burst, covering all players in Toxic Spores.\n\n\n\nUpon contact, the spores transfer, applying Toxic Spores and destroying the fungi.",-1,32661,129345,0,2776,0,16,32659,0},
    {32669,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The Hoardmonger prevents his reserves from being pilfered at all costs, casting |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235072|h[Resourceful Measures]|h|r upon reaching 90%, 60%, and 30% health, empowering one of his abilities.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, he tosses |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234233|h[Spoiled Supplies]|h|r throughout the arena, growing Rotten Mushrooms for 12 seconds. Upon contact, these apply |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234846|h[Toxic Spores]|h|r destroying the fungi, preventing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245593|h[Putrid Burst]|h|r.",-1,32670,0,0,2776,32673,1,0,0},
    {32670,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Rotten Mushrooms apply |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234846|h[Toxic Spores]|h|r upon contact, preventing them from detonating in a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245593|h[Putrid Burst]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234021|h[Earthshatter Slam]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235129|h[Bonespike Slam]|h|r inflict massive damage in a frontal cone.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234681|h[Ravenous Bellow]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235125|h[Hearty Bellow]|h|r inflicts high damage to all players.",-1,0,0,2,2776,32671,2,32669,0},
    {32671,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234681|h[Ravenous Bellow]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235125|h[Hearty Bellow]|h|r inflict high damage to all players.\n\n$bullet; Rotten Mushrooms' |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234846|h[Toxic Spores]|h|r can be removed by Poison-cleansing effects.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234021|h[Earthshatter Slam]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235129|h[Bonespike Slam]|h|r inflict massive damage in a frontal cone.",-1,0,0,4,2776,32672,3,32669,0},
    {32672,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; The Hoardmonger gathers from the nearest resource pile during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235072|h[Resourceful Measures]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Rotten Mushrooms apply |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234846|h[Toxic Spores]|h|r upon contact, preventing them from detonating in a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245593|h[Putrid Burst]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234681|h[Ravenous Bellow]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235125|h[Hearty Bellow]|h|r inflict high damage to all players.",-1,0,0,1,2776,0,4,32669,0},
