    {32690,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The Sentinel of Winter harnesses the power of the surrounding blizzard. This forms |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235623|h[Raging Squalls]|h|r which wander the landscape, and Fractured Shivercores which cast |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235829|h[Winter's Shroud]|h|r until defeated.\n\n\n\nAt 100 energy he coalesces a massive storm and channels |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235656|h[Eternal Winter]|h|r absorbing incoming damage, inflicting heavy damage, and pushing back players until broken.",-1,32691,0,0,2777,34304,1,0,0},
    {32691,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$[23$bullet; Fractured Shivercores create |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234314|h[Snowdrifts]|h|r and trigger |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263590|h[Rimeshatter]|h|r when defeated.$]\n\n$[1,2$bullet; Fractured Shivercores create |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234314|h[Snowdrifts]|h|r when defeated.$]\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235656|h[Eternal Winter]|h|r inflicts heavy damage and pushes players back.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235623|h[Raging Squalls]|h|r wander the landscape and inflict moderate damage.",-1,0,0,2,2777,32692,2,32690,0},
    {32692,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235656|h[Eternal Winter]|h|r inflicts heavy damage and pushes players back.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235548|h[Glacial Torment]|h|r inflicts a large amount of damage, but can be removed by Magic-cleansing effects.\n\n$[23$bullet; Fractured Shivercores create |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234314|h[Snowdrifts]|h|r and trigger |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263590|h[Rimeshatter]|h|r when defeated.$]\n\n$[1,2$bullet; Fractured Shivercores create |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234314|h[Snowdrifts]|h|r when defeated.$]",-1,0,0,4,2777,32693,3,32690,0},
    {32693,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$[23$bullet; Fractured Shivercores create |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234314|h[Snowdrifts]|h|r and trigger |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263590|h[Rimeshatter]|h|r when defeated.$]\n\n$[1,2$bullet; Fractured Shivercores create |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234314|h[Snowdrifts]|h|r when defeated.$]\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235656|h[Eternal Winter]|h|r inflicts heavy damage and pushes players back.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235623|h[Raging Squalls]|h|r wander the landscape and inflict moderate damage.",-1,0,0,1,2777,0,4,32690,0},
