    {32959,"Section 49",0,2,1240891,2,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,4096,2688,32340,35,31791,0},
    {32960,"Section 31",0,2,1241023,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,32,2452,23330,27,23098,0},
    {32963,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Taz'Rah uses |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263593|h[Gather Shadows]|h|r to summon Ethereal Shades that perform |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222098|h[Nether Dash]|h|r, damaging targets in a line in front of them.\n\n\n\nWhile Taz'rah's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222199|h[Dark Rift]|h|r is active, players are drawn towards it.",-1,32964,0,0,2791,32967,1,0,0},
    {32964,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;The effect from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222199|h[Dark Rift]|h|r pulls in all players toward it and inflicts very high damage to those who fall into its center.\n\n\n\n$bullet;Taz'Rah uses |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263593|h[Gather Shadows]|h|r to summon Ethereal Shades that perform |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222098|h[Nether Dash]|h|r, damaging targets in a line in front of them.",-1,0,0,2,2791,32965,2,32963,0},
    {32965,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222098|h[Nether Dash]|h|r strikes all players in a line and inflicts Shadow damage over a long duration.\n\n\n\n$bullet;The effect from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222199|h[Dark Rift]|h|r pulls all nearby enemy targets toward it and inflicts very high damage to any who get pulled into it.",-1,0,0,4,2791,32966,3,32963,0},
    {32966,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222085|h[Cosmic Spike]|h|r inflicts heavy Shadowstrike damage.\n\n\n\n$bullet;The effect from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222199|h[Dark Rift]|h|r pulls in all players toward it and inflicts very high damage to those who fall into its center.",-1,0,0,1,2791,0,4,32963,0},
    {32967,"Dark Rift",0,2,1222199,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,32,2791,32970,5,0,0},
    {32968,"Nether Dash",0,2,1222098,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2791,0,9,34339,0},
    {32969,"Void Strike",0,2,1222085,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,1,2791,0,10,0,0},
    {32970,"Ethereal Shards",0,2,1225107,2,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,4096,2791,34337,6,0,0},
    {32971,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Atroxus uses |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222371|h[Provoke Creeper]|h|r to call forth allies and assaults players with its powerful venoms using |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222721|h[Noxious Breath]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226120|h[Poison Splash]|h|r .",-1,32972,0,0,2792,34379,1,0,0},
    {32972,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222721|h[Noxious Breath]|h|r inflicts high damage in front of Atroxus.\n\n\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222371|h[Provoke Creeper]|h|r calls forth a Toxic Creeper to attack players.\n\n\n\n$bullet;Toxic Creepers created by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222371|h[Provoke Creeper]|h|r fixate on random players.",-1,0,0,2,2792,32973,2,32971,0},
    {32973,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222642|h[Hulking Claw]|h|r inflicts high Nature damage to the primary target.\n\n\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222721|h[Noxious Breath]|h|r inflicts high damage in front of Atroxus.",-1,0,0,4,2792,32974,3,32971,0},
    {32974,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1222642|h[Hulking Claw]|h|r inflicts high Nature damage to the primary target.\n\n\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1282892|h[Sickening Bite]|h|r applies stacking vulnerability to Nature damage.",-1,0,0,1,2792,0,4,32971,0},
    {32975,"Section 5",0,2,1222724,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,32,2792,34340,13,0,0},
    {32976,"Section 5",0,2,1222642,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,513,2792,0,15,0,0},
    {32977,"Section 5",0,2,1226031,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,34341,0,512,2792,32975,10,0,0},
    {32979,"Section 25",0,2,1239988,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2685,32044,6,32043,0},
    {32982,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Charonus truly tests his prey to learn their limits. He attacks players using |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248112|h[Unstable Singularity]|h|r and creates |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263982|h[Gravitic Orbs]|h|r to hunt them down.",-1,32983,0,0,2793,33511,1,0,0},
    {32983,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248112|h[Unstable Singularity]|h|r inflicts Shadow damage and reduces the movement speed of players caught within it.\n\n\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263982|h[Gravitic Orbs]|h|r continually seek out players until collapsed by an |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248112|h[Unstable Singularity]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2793,32984,2,32982,0},
    {32984,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263983|h[Condensed Mass]|h|r inflicts high damage to all players.\n\n\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263982|h[Gravitic Orbs]|h|r continually seek out players until collapsed by an |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248112|h[Unstable Singularity]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,2793,32985,3,32982,0},
    {32985,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248112|h[Unstable Singularity]|h|r inflicts Shadow damage and reduces the movement speed of players caught within it.\n\n\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263982|h[Gravitic Orbs]|h|r continually seek out players until collapsed by an |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1248112|h[Unstable Singularity]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2793,0,4,32982,0},
    {32987,"Section 7",0,2,1248130,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2793,32990,7,0,0},
    {32989,"Section 8",0,2,1227197,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2793,0,9,0,0},
    {32990,"Section 5",0,2,1222755,2,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,4096,2793,32989,8,0,0},
    {32991,"Section 70",0,2,1241188,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,16,2691,32713,40,32735,0},
    {32993,"Section 50",0,2,1227685,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,32958,0,0,2688,0,12,32504,0},
    {32994,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Chimaerus wrenches its enemies into the Rift during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262305|h[Alndust Upheaval]|h|r where they must contend with aberrant Manifestations shielded by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245727|h[Alnshroud]|h|r. Manifestations that lose their shroud emerge into Reality and move towards the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1252863|h[Insatiable]|h|r Chimaerus.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, Chimaerus takes to the skies with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245486|h[Corrupted Devastation]|h|r while summoning Manifestations below.",-1,32995,0,0,2795,34507,1,0,0},
    {32995,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262305|h[Alndust Upheaval]|h|r allows players to see into the Aln and attack Manifestations.\n\n$bullet; Coalesced Manifestations afflict the raid with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1250953|h[Rift Sickness]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Manifestations in Reality move toward |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1252863|h[Insatiable]|h|r Chimaerus.\n\n$bullet; Colossal Horrors unleash a series of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262020|h[Colossal Strikes]|h|r against their current target.",-1,0,0,1,2795,32996,2,32994,0},
    {32996,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262305|h[Alndust Upheaval]|h|r allows players to see into the Aln and attack Manifestations.\n\n$bullet; Coalesced Manifestations afflict the raid with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1250953|h[Rift Sickness]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Manifestations in Reality move toward |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1252863|h[Insatiable]|h|r Chimaerus.",-1,0,0,2,2795,32997,3,32994,0},
    {32997,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Coalesced Manifestations afflict the raid with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1250953|h[Rift Sickness]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262305|h[Alndust Upheaval]|h|r allows players to see into the Aln and attack Manifestations.\n\n$bullet; Players within the Rift who are affected by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1245698|h[Alnsight]|h|r cannot interact with allies.",-1,0,0,4,2795,0,4,32994,0},
