    {33028,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1240210|h[Pulverizing Strikes]|h|r launches a cone of Physical damage at each target.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1240098|h[Lightfall]|h|r inflicts high damage to players within each impact.",-1,0,0,2,2771,33029,2,32316,0},
    {33029,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1241058|h[Grievous Thrash]|h|r is only removed when the afflicted target reaches full health.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1240210|h[Pulverizing Strikes]|h|r launches a cone of Physical damage at each target.",-1,0,0,4,2771,33030,3,32316,0},
    {33030,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; In Moonkin form, Ruia's melee attacks are replaced with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1239821|h[Warden's Wrath]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1240210|h[Pulverizing Strikes]|h|r launches a cone of Physical damage at each target.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1240098|h[Lightfall]|h|r inflicts high damage to players within each impact.",-1,0,0,1,2771,0,4,32316,0},
    {33031,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1236658|h[Bloodthorn Roots]|h|r immobilize players until the roots are destroyed.\n\n$bullet; Players targeted by |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237090|h[Bloodthirsty Gaze]|h|r will be |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237166|h[Incised]|h|r if Ikuzz reaches their location.",-1,0,0,2,2770,33032,2,32315,0},
    {33032,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1236658|h[Bloodthorn Roots]|h|r immobilize players until the roots are destroyed.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1236709|h[Thorncaller Roar]|h|r channels Nature damage on all players.\n\n$bullet; Players take a high amount of damage when |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237166|h[Incised]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,2770,33033,3,32315,0},
