    {33165,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The Loa of War spares no mortal as the final trial, assailing players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1242860|h[Echoing Maul]|h|r and pushing them with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1255385|h[Forceful Roar]|h|r.\n\n\n\nAt 100 energy, Nalorakk casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243002|h[Fury of the War God]|h|r, slamming Zul'jarra across the arena and incapacitating her with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243063|h[Concussive Shock]|h|r. Nalorakk commands Echoes of Nalorakk to charge the defenseless Zul'jarra, casting |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243408|h[Echoing Fury]|h|r when colliding with the first target they encounter.",-1,33166,0,0,2778,35137,1,0,0},
    {33166,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243002|h[Fury of the War God]|h|r sends Echoes of Nalorakk to attack Zul'jarra, stopping only to cast |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243408|h[Echoing Fury]|h|r on the first target they encounter.\n\n$bullet; Each Echo of Nalorakk casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1242860|h[Echoing Maul]|h|r when Nalorakk casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1242860|h[Echoing Maul]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Nalorakk's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1255385|h[Forceful Roar]|h|r pushes all players away.",-1,0,0,2,2778,33167,2,33165,0},
    {33167,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243585|h[Overwhelming Onslaught]|h|r inflicts significant damage even while protected from Zul'jarra's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1261776|h[Defensive Stance]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Each Echo of Nalorakk casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1242860|h[Echoing Maul]|h|r when Nalorakk casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1242860|h[Echoing Maul]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; Nalorakk's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1255385|h[Forceful Roar]|h|r pushes all players away.",-1,0,0,4,2778,33168,3,33165,0},
    {33168,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Zul'jarra's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1261776|h[Defensive Stance]|h|r greatly reduces Nalorakk's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243585|h[Overwhelming Onslaught]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243002|h[Fury of the War God]|h|r sends Echoes of Nalorakk to attack Zul'jarra, stopping only to cast |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243408|h[Echoing Fury]|h|r on the first target they encounter.\n\n$bullet; Each Echo of Nalorakk casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1242860|h[Echoing Maul]|h|r when Nalorakk casts |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1242860|h[Echoing Maul]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,2778,0,4,33165,0},
    {33171,"Section 10",0,2,1243002,3,{"wago"},"$[!8,23\n\n \n\nIn Mythic difficulty, players struck by an Echo are also afflicted with Spectral Slash.$]",0,33177,0,4128,2778,33173,9,0,0},
