    {33345,"Tanks",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Undying Sentinels utilize |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1239279|h[Echoing Darkness]|h|r when no players are in melee combat.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237251|h[Empowering Darkness]|h|r affects Alleria's allies within a large area.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1239080|h[Aspect of the End]|h|r reduces healing received and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1239089|h[Gravity Collapse]|h|r leaves the target weak to Physical attacks.",0,0,0,1,2738,32190,4,32187,0},
    {33348,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"The cunning duo of Muro'jin and Nekraxx fight as one, assailing players with an array of combined tactics.\n\n\n\nMuro'jin withers players down with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1260643|h[Barrage]|h|r while Nekraxx flings a salvo of feathers with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243900|h[Fetid Quillstorm]|h|r.\n\n\n\nAs Muro'jin scatters |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1260731|h[Freezing Traps]|h|r across the arena, Nekraxx barrels forward with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1249479|h[Carrion Swoop]|h|r.",-1,33349,0,0,2810,33932,1,0,0},
    {33349,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Muro'jin attempts to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1249789|h[Revive Pet]|h|r upon Nekraxx's defeat, and Nekraxx enters |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1249948|h[Bestial Wrath]|h|r upon Muro'jin's defeat.\n\n$bullet;Muro'jin's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1260731|h[Freezing Traps]|h|r encase players in ice upon contact. Players encased in ice can intercept Nekraxx's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1249479|h[Carrion Swoop]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Muro'jin's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1260643|h[Barrage]|h|r follows the targeted player and affects all players in a frontal cone.",-1,0,0,2,2810,33350,2,33348,0},
    {33350,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Nekraxx's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1246666|h[Infected Pinions]|h|r inflicts significant damage to all players.\n\n$bullet;Muro'jin's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1260731|h[Freezing Traps]|h|r encase players in ice upon contact. Players encased in ice can intercept Nekraxx's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1249479|h[Carrion Swoop]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Muro'jin's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1260643|h[Barrage]|h|r follows the targeted player and affects all players in a frontal cone.",-1,0,0,4,2810,33351,3,33348,0},
    {33351,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Muro'jin's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1266480|h[Flanking Spear]|h|r both repositions behind his current target and applies |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1266488|h[Open Wound]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Muro'jin's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1260731|h[Freezing Traps]|h|r encase players in ice upon contact. Players encased in ice can intercept Nekraxx's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1249479|h[Carrion Swoop]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Nekraxx's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1249479|h[Carrion Swoop]|h|r affects all players in its path, inflicting damage and knocking them upwards.",-1,0,0,1,2810,0,4,33348,0},
    {33360,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Vordaza blasts players with necrotic energy while manipulating spirits with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251204|h[Wrest Phantoms]|h|r to perform her bidding.\n\n\n\nAs the fight progresses, Vordaza invokes a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1250708|h[Necrotic Convergence]|h|r, concentrating soul energy into volatile masses until interrupted.",-1,33361,0,0,2811,33702,1,0,0},
    {33361,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Vordaza summons Unstable Phantoms with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251204|h[Wrest Phantoms]|h|r that chase players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251775|h[Final Pursuit]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Unstable Phantoms afflict all players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251813|h[Lingering Dread]|h|r when defeated.\n\n$bullet;While |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251598|h[Deathshroud]|h|r holds, Vordaza is unable to be interrupted.",-1,0,0,2,2811,33362,2,33360,0},
    {33362,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Vordaza summons Unstable Phantoms with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251204|h[Wrest Phantoms]|h|r that chase players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251775|h[Final Pursuit]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Unstable Phantoms afflict all players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251813|h[Lingering Dread]|h|r when defeated.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251554|h[Drain Soul]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to Vordaza's current target and absorbs healing received.",-1,0,0,4,2811,33363,3,33360,0},
    {33363,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Vordaza summons Unstable Phantoms with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251204|h[Wrest Phantoms]|h|r that chase players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251775|h[Final Pursuit]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Unstable Phantoms afflict all players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251813|h[Lingering Dread]|h|r when defeated.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251554|h[Drain Soul]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to Vordaza's current target and absorbs healing received.",-1,0,0,1,2811,0,4,33360,0},
    {33372,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Rak'tul batters players with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251023|h[Spiritbreaker]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1252676|h[Crush Souls]|h|r, forming totems that |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1252777|h[Soulbind]|h|r his foes.\n\n\n\nAs the fight progresses, Rak'tul unleashes a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253788|h[Soulrending Roar]|h|r, casting players' souls into the Restless Masses and afflicting them with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253844|h[Withering Soul]|h|r until they return to the realm of the living.",-1,33373,0,0,2812,33913,1,0,0},
    {33373,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Totems spawn at each |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1252676|h[Crush Souls]|h|r target's location and cast |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1252777|h[Soulbind]|h|r at a player.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253788|h[Soulrending Roar]|h|r applies |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253844|h[Withering Soul]|h|r until players return to the realm of the living.\n\n$bullet;Interrupting |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1254010|h[Eternal Suffering]|h|r grants |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1255629|h[Spectral Residue]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2812,33374,2,33372,0},
    {33374,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Totems spawn at each |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1252676|h[Crush Souls]|h|r target's location and cast |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1252777|h[Soulbind]|h|r at a player.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253788|h[Soulrending Roar]|h|r applies |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253844|h[Withering Soul]|h|r until players return to the realm of the living.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1252864|h[Deathgorged Vessel]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to all players.",-1,0,0,4,2812,33375,3,33372,0},
    {33375,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Totems spawn at each |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1252676|h[Crush Souls]|h|r target's location and cast |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1252777|h[Soulbind]|h|r at a player.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253788|h[Soulrending Roar]|h|r applies |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253844|h[Withering Soul]|h|r until players return to the realm of the living.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251023|h[Spiritbreaker]|h|r inflicts heavy damage to Rak'tul's primary target, launching them into the air.",-1,0,0,1,2812,0,4,33372,0},
    {33384,"Section 37",0,2,1246709,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2739,0,38,33025,0},
