    {33389,"Section 69",0,2,1237695,2,{"wago"},"$[!15,16\n\n\n\nIn Heroic and Mythic difficulty, |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237695|h[Stardust Nova]|h|r also leaves behind a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1237696|h[Debris Field]|h|r.$]",0,33591,0,8,2691,33592,82,32745,0},
    {33390,"Section 71",0,2,1237696,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,0,2691,0,87,33592,0},
    {33391,"Section 83",0,2,1232987,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,33408,0,16,2691,33409,43,32735,0},
    {33393,"Section 26",0,2,1227848,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,4,2685,0,15,32043,0},
    {33394,"Section 26",0,2,1246530,2,{"wago"},nil,0,32313,0,4096,2685,33038,17,0,0},
    {33395,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Kasreth's Corespark Engine ebbs and flows with arcane energies, forming |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251626|h[Leyline Arrays]|h|r between the conduits around the room. The Corewright is a mastermind of circuitry, overwhelming a player with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251767|h[Reflux Charge]|h|r. At 100 energy, Kasreth picks up a corespark and overcharges it in the engine, unleashing a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1257509|h[Corespark Detonation]|h|r at the impact location.",-1,33396,0,0,2813,34752,1,0,0},
    {33396,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251767|h[Reflux Charge]|h|r inflicts damage until overloaded.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251183|h[Leyline Arrays]|h|r link randomly between conduits around the room and inflict heavy damage when crossing.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264040|h[Flux Collapse]|h|r launches a continuous flow of arcane towards a player.",-1,0,0,2,2813,33397,2,33395,0},
    {33397,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251767|h[Reflux Charge]|h|r inflicts damage until overloaded.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251183|h[Leyline Arrays]|h|r link randomly between conduits around the room and inflict heavy damage when crossing.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264040|h[Flux Collapse]|h|r launches a continuous flow of arcane towards a player.",-1,0,0,4,2813,33398,3,33395,0},
    {33398,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251767|h[Reflux Charge]|h|r inflicts damage until overloaded.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1251183|h[Leyline Arrays]|h|r link randomly between conduits around the room and inflict heavy damage when crossing.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264040|h[Flux Collapse]|h|r launches a continuous flow of arcane towards a player.",-1,0,0,1,2813,0,4,33395,0},
    {33399,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Scarred by her struggle with Lothraxion, Fractured Images continue to assault the Corewarden, erupting in bursts of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1247976|h[Lightscar Flare]|h|r. Nysarra calls upon the remnants of her shattered command to defend and suppress players while she slips through the shadows with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1249014|h[Eclipsing Step]|h|r and empowers her twin nullblades to unleash |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1247937|h[Umbral Lash]|h|r.",-1,33400,0,0,2814,34346,1,0,0},
    {33400,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Corewarden Nysarra calls to her subordinates to assist during battle.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1249014|h[Eclipsing Step]|h|r carves into nearby players in addition to the targeted victim.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1247976|h[Lightscar Flare]|h|r stuns as the Fractured Image strikes its target and the resulting wound surges with Holy energy, providing power to those standing within it.",-1,0,0,2,2814,33401,2,33399,0},
    {33401,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Corewarden Nysarra calls to her subordinates to assist during battle.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1249014|h[Eclipsing Step]|h|r carves into nearby players in addition to the targeted victim.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1247976|h[Lightscar Flare]|h|r stuns as the Fractured Image strikes its target and the resulting wound surges with Holy energy, providing power to those standing within it.",-1,0,0,4,2814,33402,3,33399,0},
    {33402,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Corewarden Nysarra calls to her subordinates to assist during battle.\n\n$bullet;The power of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1247937|h[Umbral Lash]|h|r cleaves nearby players and applies |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1252828|h[Void Gash]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1247976|h[Lightscar Flare]|h|r stuns as the Fractured Image strikes its target and the resulting wound surges with Holy energy, providing power to those standing within it.",-1,0,0,1,2814,0,4,33399,0},
    {33403,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Fractured Images of Lothraxion linger with every |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253848|h[Brilliant Dispersion]|h|r, haunting the battlefield. These images |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1255531|h[Flicker]|h|r and slice at nearby enemies with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1266713|h[Mirrored Rend]|h|r. When he reaches full power, Lothraxion flickers into hiding amongst his images and attempts to overload the core with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1257613|h[Divine Guile]|h|r.",-1,33404,0,0,2815,34712,1,0,0},
    {33404,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253848|h[Brilliant Dispersion]|h|r inflicts damage to all nearby players.\n\n$bullet; Fractured Images unleash |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1266713|h[Mirrored Rend]|h|r when standing too close.\n\n$bullet; Lothraxion hides among his distorted images during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1257613|h[Divine Guile]|h|r until he is interrupted.",-1,0,0,2,2815,33405,2,33403,0},
    {33405,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253848|h[Brilliant Dispersion]|h|r targets several players and inflicts damage to all nearby players when reaching its targeted destination.\n\n$bullet; Fractured Images unleash |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1266713|h[Mirrored Rend]|h|r when standing too close.\n\n$bullet; Lothraxian hides among his distorted images during |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1257613|h[Divine Guile]|h|r until he is interrupted.",-1,0,0,4,2815,33406,3,33403,0},
