    {33678,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Fractillus calls forth |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226089|h[Crystal Nexuses]|h|r that amplify the power of the |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1233657|h[Nether Prism]|h|r. If six nexuses are allowed to amplify a single prism's beam, Fractillus will be empowered with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1233917|h[Crystaline Overcharge]|h|r.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, Fractillus will use its |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1227376|h[Shattering Backhand]|h|r to knock several players away, shattering any |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1226089|h[Crystal Nexus]|h|r in their path.",-1,32121,0,0,2747,33677,1,0,0},
