    {34055,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Thorm'belan unleashes the power of the Light to assault the players. Periodically lobbing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1257825|h[Scintillating Shards]|h|r while also pulling players in towards itself with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1258639|h[Shredding Tendrils]|h|r.",-1,34056,0,0,2829,34059,1,0,0},
    {34056,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1257825|h[Scintillating Shard]|h|r causes all players to become stunned if it is not intercepted.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1258639|h[Shredding Tendrils]|h|r pulls players towards Thorm'belan and inflicts damage until players move far enough away from Thorm'belan.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1257320|h[Radiant Mote]|h|r damages and disorients nearby players when it expires.",-1,0,0,1,2829,34057,2,34055,0},
