    {34246,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Forgemaster Garfrost |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1261299|h[Throws Saronite]|h|r at players, then follows up with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1261546|h[Orebreaker]|h|r. Occasionally, he lets loose a mighty |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1261847|h[Cryostomp]|h|r, increasing |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1261806|h[Siphoning Chill's]|h|r danger.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, Garfrost activates a |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262029|h[Glacial Overload]|h|r from his closest forge.",-1,34247,0,0,608,34250,1,0,0},
    {34247,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Garfrost |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1261299|h[Throws Saronite]|h|r at targeted players.\n\n$bullet;Saronite ore offers protection from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262029|h[Glacial Overload]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,608,34248,2,34246,0},
    {34248,"Healer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1261847|h[Cryostomp]|h|r increases the danger of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1261806|h[Siphoning Chill]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Saronite ore offers protection from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262029|h[Glacial Overload]|h|r.",-1,0,0,4,608,34249,3,34246,0},
    {34249,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1261546|h[Orebreaker]|h|r does not stun its target if it strikes saronite ore.\n\n$bullet;Saronite ore offers protection from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262029|h[Glacial Overload]|h|r.",-1,0,0,1,608,0,4,34246,0},
