    {34313,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Scourgelord Tyrannus opens his assault with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276648|h[Bone Infusion]|h|r while his dragon, Rimefang, attacks from the air with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262745|h[Rime Blast]|h|r. While building his power, Scourgelord Tyrannus unleashes |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263756|h[Death's Grasp]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262582|h[Scourgelord's Brand]|h|r.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, he raises undead minions with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263406|h[Army of the Dead]|h|r.",-1,35183,0,0,610,34317,1,0,0},
    {34314,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Scourgelord Tyrannus's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263406|h[Army of the Dead]|h|r summons a swarm of minions.\n\n$bullet;Rimefang's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262745|h[Rime Blast]|h|r freezes any |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276357|h[Bone Piles]|h|r or |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276391|h[Infused Bone Piles]|h|r it impacts.\n\n$bullet;Scourgelord Tyrannus's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276648|h[Bone Infusion]|h|r empowers some |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276357|h[Bone Piles]|h|r.",0,0,0,2,610,35184,3,34313,0},
    {34315,"Healer",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276648|h[Bone Infusion]|h|r, |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262745|h[Rime Blast]|h|r, and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262739|h[Frost Spit]|h|r inflict significant damage to players.\n\n$bullet;Rimefang's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262745|h[Rime Blast]|h|r freezes any |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276357|h[Bone Piles]|h|r or |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276391|h[Infused Bone Piles]|h|r it impacts.\n\n$bullet;Scourgelord Tyrannus's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263406|h[Army of the Dead]|h|r summons minions that inflict significant damage to players.",0,0,0,4,610,35185,5,34313,0},
    {34316,"Tank",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262582|h[Scourgelord's Brand]|h|r increases the damage of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263671|h[Scourgelord's Reckoning]|h|r.\n\n$bullet;Scourgelord Tyrannus's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263406|h[Army of the Dead]|h|r summons a swarm of minions.\n\n$bullet;Scourgelord Tyrannus's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276648|h[Bone Infusion]|h|r empowers some |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276357|h[Bone Piles]|h|r.",0,0,0,1,610,0,7,34313,0},
    {34317,"Scourgelord Tyrannus",0,1,0,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,35180,137505,0,610,34329,8,0,0},
