    {34343,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; Lightblossoms gain an increasing amount of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235729|h[Light-Gorged]|h|r unless the rays of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235564|h[Lightblossom Beam]|h|r are blocked.\n\n$bullet; Damage taken is shared between the trio with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1253028|h[Thicket's Trinity]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2769,34906,2,32314,0},
    {34344,"Healers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235751|h[Lightbloom Overgrowth]|h|r inflicts higher damage based on applications of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235729|h[Light-Gorged]|h|r.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235640|h[Thornblade]|h|r causes random players to bleed for high damage.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276586|h[Bedrock Surge]|h|r inflicts periodic damage to all players.",0,0,0,4,2769,34345,4,32314,0},
    {34345,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234753|h[Bedrock Slam]|h|r creates patches of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1234782|h[Fertile Loam]|h|r near the location of the target.\n\n$bullet; Lightblossoms gain an increasing amount of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235729|h[Light-Gorged]|h|r unless the rays of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1235564|h[Lightblossom Beam]|h|r are blocked.",-1,0,0,1,2769,0,5,32314,0},
    {34346,"Section 14",0,2,1253965,1,{"wago"},nil,-1,34494,0,0,2814,35237,5,0,0},
    {34349,"Section 11",0,2,1222795,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,34350,0,513,2680,0,12,0,0},
    {34350,"Section 12",0,2,474515,0,{"wago"},nil,-1,0,0,513,2680,0,13,34349,0},
    {34357,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Krick and his construct, Ick, battle players simultaneously. |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264259|h[Shades of Krick]|h|r channel |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264186|h[Shadowbind]|h|r while Ick attacks with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264336|h[Plague Expulsion]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264287|h[Blight Smash]|h|r.\n\n\n\nUpon reaching 100 energy, Krick yells, \"|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264363|h[Get 'Em, Ick!]|h|r,\" commanding his monstrous minion to attack specific players.",-1,34358,0,0,609,35179,1,0,0},
    {34358,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264259|h[Shades of Krick]|h|r explode for significant damage if not defeated quickly.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264186|h[Shadowbind]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1278893|h[Death Bolt]|h|r inflict significant harm unless stopped.\n\n$bullet;Krick's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264363|h[Get 'Em, Ick!]|h|r compels Ick to fixate a player, ignoring others at all costs.",-1,0,0,2,609,34359,2,34357,0},
    {34359,"Healer",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264027|h[Shade Shift]|h|r inflicts significant damage to all players.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264259|h[Shades of Krick]|h|r channel |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264186|h[Shadowbind]|h|r, inflicting intense periodic damage.\n\n$bullet;Krick's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264363|h[Get 'Em, Ick!]|h|r compels Ick to fixate a player, ignoring others at all costs.",-1,0,0,4,609,34360,3,34357,0},
    {34360,"Tank",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Ick's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264287|h[Blight Smash]|h|r inflicts significant damage to his primary target.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264186|h[Shadowbind]|h|r and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1278893|h[Death Bolt]|h|r inflict significant harm unless stopped.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1264259|h[Shades of Krick]|h|r explode for significant damage if not defeated quickly.",-1,0,0,1,609,0,4,34357,0},
