    {34705,"Mythic Keystones",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;A Mythic Keystone is a special item used to begin a Mythic Keystone Dungeon.\n\n$bullet;Each Keystone is attuned to a specific dungeon and has a Mythic Level.\n\n$bullet;The Mythic Level of a Keystone determines dungeon difficulty and which affixes are active.\n\n$bullet;A character can only have one Keystone at a time.",-1,0,0,0,2869,34707,2,34737,0},
    {34706,"Upgrading a Mythic Keystone",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Completing a Mythic Keystone dungeon within the time limit upgrades that Keystone's Mythic Level.\n\n$bullet;If less than 20% of the timer remains, the Keystone upgrades by 1 Mythic Level.\n\n$bullet;If 20% to 40% of the timer remains, the Keystone upgrades by 2 Mythic Levels.\n\n$bullet;If more than 40% of the timer remains, the Keystone upgrades by 3 Mythic Levels.",-1,0,0,0,2869,34749,8,34737,0},
    {34707,"Obtaining a Mythic Keystone",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Completing a Mythic dungeon grants a Mythic Keystone.\n\n$bullet;Completing another player's Mythic Keystone dungeon grants a Mythic Keystone at the end of the dungeon.\n\n$bullet;After the weekly reset, opening the Great Vault grants a Mythic Keystone if a Mythic Keystone dungeon was completed in the prior week.",-1,0,0,0,2869,34708,3,34737,0},
    {34708,"Downgrading a Mythic Keystone",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Failing to complete the dungeon within the time limit lowers that Keystone's Mythic Level by 1.\n\n$bullet;Resetting the dungeon instance after the Keystone has been used lowers that Keystone's Mythic Level by 1.\n\n$bullet;Lindormi in major cities can lower a Keystone by 1 Mythic Level on request.",-1,0,0,0,2869,34709,4,34737,0},
    {34709,"Starting a Mythic Keystone",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Enter the dungeon the Mythic Keystone is attuned to on Mythic difficulty.\n\n$bullet;At the entrance, insert the Mythic Keystone into the Font of Power and activate it to start the dungeon.",-1,0,0,0,2869,34710,5,34737,0},
    {34710,"Replacing a Mythic Keystone",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;When a Mythic Keystone dungeon is completed within the time limit, Lindormi can exchange a character's Keystone for one attuned to a different dungeon. To be eligible for exchange, the completed dungeon's Mythic Level must be equal to or higher than the Keystone being exchanged.",-1,0,0,0,2869,34711,6,34737,0},
    {34711,"Completing a Mythic Keystone",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;All bosses must be defeated.\n\n$bullet;The enemy forces requirement must be met by defeating non-boss enemies.",-1,0,0,0,2869,34706,7,34737,0},
    {34712,"Section 10",0,2,1257613,1,{"wago"},"$[!23\n\n\n\nIn Mythic difficulty, interrupting an incorrect Fractured Image causes Core Exposure.$]",-1,34713,0,32,2815,33973,5,0,0},
    {34713,"Section 12",0,2,1271511,3,{"wago"},nil,0,0,0,4096,2815,0,6,34712,0},
