    {34749,"Resilient Keystones",0,0,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Starting at Mythic Level 12, completing all current season Keystone dungeons within the time limit sets a character's Resilient Level to that Mythic Level for the rest of the season.\n\n$bullet;If all current season Keystone dungeons are later completed within the time limit at a higher Mythic Level, the character's Resilient Level increases to that higher level.\n\n$bullet;A Resilient Keystone does not drop below its Resilient Level when a dungeon is not completed within the time limit. A Keystone's Mythic Level can still be lowered by speaking to Lindormi.",-1,0,0,0,2869,0,9,34737,0},
