    {34883,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Lu'ashal assails foes in a holy frenzy, raining energy from the skies with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243963|h[Radiant Sunder]|h|r  to shatter the ground that leave |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243988|h[Blinding Fissures]|h|r behind. During |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1258427|h[Radiant Flare]|h|r, she unleashes waves of |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1258426|h[Radiant Embers]|h|r that travel across the battlefield.",-1,34884,0,0,2827,34891,1,0,0},
    {34884,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276436|h[Dawncrazed Halo]|h|r inflicts moderate damage in an area around afflicted players.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1258427|h[Radiant Flare]|h|r inflicts substantial damage and casues |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1258426|h[Radiant Embers]|h|r to erupt from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243988|h[Blinding Fissures]|h|r .",-1,0,0,4,2827,34885,2,34883,0},
    {34885,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276373|h[Dawnfire Breath]|h|r inflicts heavy Radiant damage in a cone at the primary target.\n\n$bullet; |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1258427|h[Radiant Flare]|h|r inflicts substantial damage and casues |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1258426|h[Radiant Embers]|h|r to erupt from |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1243988|h[Blinding Fissures]|h|r .",-1,0,0,1,2827,34886,3,34883,0},
