    {34925,"Overview",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"Predaxas thrashes about the Gorging Pit ejecting his late lunch at foes with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276193|h[Regurgitation]|h|r and crushing vermin with |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276320|h[Seismic Slam]|h|r.",-1,34926,0,0,2828,34994,1,0,0},
    {34926,"Tanks",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276193|h[Regurgitation]|h|r ejects Predaxas' previous meals which attack players.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276320|h[Seismic Slam]|h|r knocks back players and Predaxas' previous meals, causing additional effects.",-1,0,0,1,2828,34927,2,34925,0},
    {34927,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276320|h[Seismic Slam]|h|r knocks back players and Predaxas' previous meals, causing additional effects.\n\n$bullet;Voidticks react to |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276320|h[Seismic Slam]|h|r triggering |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276884|h[Voidscatter]|h|r.",-1,0,0,2,2828,34928,3,34925,0},
    {34928,"Healers",0,3,0,0,{"wago"},"$bullet;Reguritated Bloodclaws periodically gain |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1277711|h[Bestial Rage]|h|r inflicting increased damage.\n\n$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276320|h[Seismic Slam]|h|r knocks back players and Predaxas' previous meals, causing additional effects.",-1,0,0,4,2828,0,4,34925,0},
