    {35183,"Damage Dealers",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;Scourgelord Tyrannus's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263406|h[Army of the Dead]|h|r summons a swarm of minions.\n\n$bullet;Rimefang's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262745|h[Rime Blast]|h|r freezes any |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276357|h[Bone Piles]|h|r it impacts.\n\n$bullet;Scourgelord Tyrannus's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263756|h[Death's Grasp]|h|r and Rimefang's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276948|h[Ice Barrage]|h|r inflict significant damage at targeted locations.",3,0,0,2,610,34314,2,34313,0},
    {35184,"Healer",0,3,0,2,{"wago"},"$bullet;|cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276648|h[Bone Infusion]|h|r, |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262745|h[Rime Blast]|h|r, and |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262739|h[Frost Spit]|h|r inflict significant damage to players.\n\n$bullet;Rimefang's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1262745|h[Rime Blast]|h|r freezes any |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1276357|h[Bone Piles]|h|r it impacts.\n\n$bullet;Scourgelord Tyrannus's |cFF2959D3|Hspell:1263406|h[Army of the Dead]|h|r summons minions that inflict significant damage to players.",3,0,0,4,610,34315,4,34313,0},
